\id MAT - KadiwГ©u NT -Brazil 1999 (DBL -2013) 
\h MATEUS 
\toc1 NotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi Ane IdГӯ Mateus 
\toc2 Mateus 
\toc3 Mt 
\mt1 NOTAЗӨANAЗӨAXI ANE IDГҚ MATEUS 
\ip Jesus eledi enidite Mateus niЙЎМ¶ijo maleekoka iolatedicoace niЙЎМ¶ijoa dooze ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi modiotibece. Jesus maleedaЙЎМ¶a eniditeta, Mateus libakedi me dibatibigege dinyeelo anoyajigota ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi, idaaЙЎМ¶ida me judeu. Odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me neleЙЎМ¶edi eletidi judeutedi. Mateus eledi oyatigi me Levi. (Awiniteloco miditaЙЎМ¶a Mateus 9.9; Marcos 2.14). 
\ip Mateus me idГӯ naЙЎМ¶adi notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi didikotibige noiigi judeu me ikeetiogi mewi Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶icoa ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЗӨonewikatitoЙЎМ¶odi. Elioditibece me yalaЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane lotaЙЎМ¶a miditaЙЎМ¶a liwai oxiiЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi ane yalaЙЎМ¶ate Jesus, midiwataЙЎМ¶a notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axiidi ane iditedini MoisГ©s, maditaЙЎМ¶a lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi enaco, codaa midiwataЙЎМ¶a notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axiidi anoidГӯ niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. 
\ip Mateus iditedini liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco Jesus aneneЙЎМ¶egi ida ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate. LiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco Jesus ane yalaЙЎМ¶ata: 
\io2 (1) Ane leeditibige me ee lewiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baanaЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali, codaa niЙЎМ¶ica ane yajigotediogi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. 
\io2 (2) NiЙЎМ¶ica ane iiЙЎМ¶ete Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece mowo niЙЎМ¶ijo me imonya moyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece nibodicetedi anele aneetece Jesus, codaa me iiЙЎМ¶e moicilatidi eelotaginadi. 
\io2 (3) Natematiko Jesus anida ane iciaceeketetege me ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶axi. 
\io2 (4) LiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco Jesus anoyalaЙЎМ¶ata gela loiigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. 
\io2 (5) LiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco Jesus anoyalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶icoa owidijedi nokododi, codaa niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee nige dopitedijo. 
\ip Mateus eledi yalaЙЎМ¶ata lanikegi Jesus, codaa me loenataka anoikee anijoa. Eledi yalaЙЎМ¶ata anodaaЙЎМ¶ee neloЙЎМ¶ododipi noЙЎМ¶oyakadi moyeloadi, codaa eledi yatemati niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace. 
\c 1  
\s1 Ica jotigide laamipi Jesus Cristo 
\r (Lucas 3.23-38) 
\p  
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶idi noiigi joaniЙЎМ¶idiaa jotigide laamipi Jesus Cristo. Jesus ida aneetetege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi, ane licoЙЎМ¶egi AbraГЈo. 
\q1  
\v 2 AbraГЈo jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Isaque, 
\q1 Isaque jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi JacГі. 
\q1 JacГі jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi JudГЎ ijaa nioxoadipi JudГЎ. 
\q1  
\v 3 JudГЎ ijoa itoataale lionigipi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, onijoteci liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Peres ijaaЙЎМ¶eledi Zera, ajaa eliodo Tamar. 
\q1 Peres jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Esrom, 
\q1 Esrom jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi ArГЈo. 
\q1  
\v 4 ArГЈo jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Aminadabe, 
\q1 Aminadabe jiЙЎМ¶ijaa ane eliodi Nasam. 
\q1 Nasam jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Salmom. 
\q1  
\v 5 Salmom jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Boaz, Boaz eliodo liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Raabe. 
\q1 Boaz jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi JessГ©. 
\q1  
\v 6 JessГ© jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Davi, Davi anijo me inionigi-eliodi. 
\b  
\q1 Davi eliodi SalomГЈo, eliodo SalomГЈo naЙЎМ¶ajo anijo me lodawa Urias. 
\q1  
\v 7 SalomГЈo jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi RoboГЈo, 
\q1 RoboГЈo jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Abias, 
\q1 Abias jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Asa. 
\q1  
\v 8 Asa jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi JosafГЎ, 
\q1 JosafГЎ jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi JorГЈo, 
\q1 JorГЈo jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Uzias. 
\q1  
\v 9 Uzias jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi JotГЈo, 
\q1 JotГЈo jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Acaz, 
\q1 Acaz jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Ezequias. 
\q1  
\v 10 Ezequias jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi ManassГ©s, 
\q1 ManassГ©s jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Amom, 
\q1 Amom jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Josias. 
\q1  
\v 11 Josias jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Jeconias ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo nioxoadipi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo malee yewiЙЎМ¶a Josias, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo laxakawepodi loiigi Israel joЙЎМ¶oyadeegi loiigi Israel digoida niiЙЎМ¶otedi BabilГҙnia midiaaЙЎМ¶i me niwilogojedipi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 12 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi noЙЎМ¶oyadeegiticogi BabilГҙnia, 
\q1 odaa Jeconias jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Salatiel, 
\q1 Salatiel jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Zorobabel. 
\q1  
\v 13 Zorobabel jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi AbiГәde, 
\q1 AbiГәde jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Eliaquim, 
\q1 Eliaquim jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Azor. 
\q1  
\v 14 Azor jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Sadoque, 
\q1 Sadoque jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Aquim, 
\q1 Aquim jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi EliГәde. 
\q1  
\v 15 EliГәde jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi Eleazar, 
\q1 Eleazar jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi MatГЈ, 
\q1 MatГЈ jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi JacГі. 
\q1  
\v 16 JacГі jiЙЎМ¶ijaa eliodi JosГ©, 
\q1 JosГ© jiЙЎМ¶ijaa lodawa Maria. 
\q1 Maria jaЙЎМ¶ajaa eliodo Jesus, ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Cristo. 
\p  
\v 17 JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee jiЙЎМ¶ijoa catooze noiigi ixomaЙЎМ¶atijo anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi AbraГЈo neЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶icota Davi, odaa idaaЙЎМ¶ee ijoa catooze noiigi ixomaЙЎМ¶atijo anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi neЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶icota Jeconias anoyadeegiticogi BabilГҙnia. IdaaЙЎМ¶ee ijoa catooze noiigi ixomaЙЎМ¶atijo anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi Jeconias neЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶icota JosГ©, niЙЎМ¶ijo lodawa Maria eliodo Jesus. 
\s1 Lanikegi Jesus 
\r (Lucas 2.1-7) 
\p  
\v 18 JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee neЙЎМ¶enitedini Jesus. Maria, ane eliodo Jesus, eka doletibige me lodawa ica JosГ©. Pida anaЙЎМ¶a lodawa niЙЎМ¶ipileЙЎМ¶e, codaa Maria aniЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a nadi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa. Pida Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eo me ipileЙЎМ¶e.  
\v 19 JosГ©, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane doletibige me lodawa Maria, ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, codaa mele. Ja domaЙЎМ¶a lowoogo me ika Maria, pida adomaЙЎМ¶a yemaa me ibolikatidi Maria lodoe niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me domaЙЎМ¶a lowoogo me ika Maria me diЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica oko.  
\v 20 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a lowoogo me daЙЎМ¶adiaa lodawa Maria, odaa ja dige. Igee ica niaanjo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me dinikeeta. Odaa oneeta, вҖңJosГ©, anida anenitege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi, jinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a adoiita me ЙЎМ¶adodawa Maria. IgaataЙЎМ¶a Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneo nigaanigi catiwedi Maria le.  
\v 21 Odaa Maria dinigajetece nigaanigawaanigi, odaa awii me liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Jesus, leeЙЎМ¶odi jiЙЎМ¶ijaa napitaЙЎМ¶adi loiigi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 22 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ica niciagi eo me icotece niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yalaЙЎМ¶ata aneeteta ЗӨoniotagodi, mee,  
\v 23 вҖңDigawini! Ani awicije anicota me ipileЙЎМ¶e, pida aniЙЎМ¶ica me nadi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idi lionigi, odaa joЙЎМ¶owo me liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖҳEmanuelвҖҷ.вҖқ вҖңEmanuelвҖқ niЙЎМ¶ina anejinaЙЎМ¶a iniwa вҖңAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mokotaЙЎМ¶aвҖқ. 
\p  
\v 24 NaЙЎМ¶a nioodi JosГ©, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eo niЙЎМ¶ijo niaanjo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iiЙЎМ¶eta meo. Odaa JosГ© ja lodawa Maria.  
\v 25 Pida aniЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a loomatewa Maria neЙЎМ¶epaa dinigajetece odoejegi lionigi. Odaa JosГ© jeЙЎМ¶eo me liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Jesus. 
\c 2  
\s1 Icoa icoЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anoicoЙЎМ¶oticogi ane icoЙЎМ¶otigi nigoi 
\p  
\v 1 Jesus lanikadi aca nigotaЙЎМ¶a BelГ©m ane nipodigi JudГ©ia, niЙЎМ¶ijo me inionigi-eliodi Herodes. NiЙЎМ¶ijoa nokododi icoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane libakedi moiЙЎМ¶oaditalo yotetitedi oicoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigoi, igotibeci nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m.  
\v 2 Odaa ja nigikanaЙЎМ¶a, modi, вҖңIgame diЙЎМ¶etigi ica nigaanigawaanigi ane icota me ninionigi-eliodi judeutedi? JowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a neЙЎМ¶enitini, igaataЙЎМ¶a jinataЙЎМ¶a ajo notedi digoida nigoi. Odaa janagaЙЎМ¶a me joЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶ata.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 3 NaЙЎМ¶a wajipatalo Herodes lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, odaa eliodi me doЙЎМ¶owikomata, codaa eliodi okotigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m eledi noЙЎМ¶owikomataaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 4 Odaa ja yatecoЙЎМ¶otee niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi, ijaa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s. Odaa Herodes ja nigetiniwace ica ane lanikadi icoa Cristo, niЙЎМ¶ijoa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane niiЙЎМ¶e meote me ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶atace.  
\v 5 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, modita, вҖңLanikadi BelГ©m nipodigi JudГ©ia, leeЙЎМ¶odi mee anigepidiЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko, 
\q1  
\v 6 вҖҳAkaami BelГ©m nipodigi JudГ©ia, 
\q1 akamaЙЎМ¶akaami akaami ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶e liwigotigi eletidi nigotadi JudГ©ia. 
\q1 IgaataЙЎМ¶a digoina makaamitaЙЎМ¶a lanikadi niЙЎМ¶ica ane icota me lacilo, 
\q1 ane dowediteloco yoiigi Israel micataЙЎМ¶a nowienoЙЎМ¶odi waxacocoliвҖҷ.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 7 Odaa Herodes jeЙЎМ¶eniditiogi ica anokegipi anoicoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigoi igo dakapetege me diЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi. Odaa ja nigetiniwace niЙЎМ¶ica noko noЙЎМ¶onadi naЙЎМ¶aca yotedi ane nodi.  
\v 8 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja imonyatibigiwaji migotibeci nigotaЙЎМ¶a BelГ©m, meetiogi, вҖңEmiitiwaji, odaa oleetibige mowooЙЎМ¶oti ane diЙЎМ¶etigi niЙЎМ¶ica nigaanigawaanigi. Nigakati, odaa awii yeemidi, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jakadi maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ejigo joЙЎМ¶eteta.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 9 NoЙЎМ¶owajipatalo lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ini inionigi-eliodi, odaa joЙЎМ¶opitibeci niЙЎМ¶ijoa anokaЙЎМ¶a. EЙЎМ¶idaa diiticogi me wiajeeЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶onadi ajaaЙЎМ¶ajo naЙЎМ¶ajo yotedi anonadi diЙЎМ¶etege nigoi. Odaa naЙЎМ¶ajo yotedi jiЙЎМ¶igo lodoe niЙЎМ¶ijoa anokaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja nicoti ditibigimedi niЙЎМ¶ijo diimicawaanigi aneitice nigaanigawaanigi.  
\v 10 NoЙЎМ¶onadi naЙЎМ¶ajo yotedi ane idei ditibigimedi niЙЎМ¶ijo diimicawaanigi, odaa eliodi me ninitibigiwaji. \fig |src="CN01629b.tif" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Mateus 2.8-10" \fig* 
\v 11 Odaa noЙЎМ¶odakatiwece niЙЎМ¶ijo diimicawaanigi, joЙЎМ¶onadi nigaanigawaanigi manitaЙЎМ¶a Maria ane eliodo nigaanigawaanigi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi lodoe niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigawaanigi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odoЙЎМ¶eteta. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi joЙЎМ¶oyomoke aca lowoodaЙЎМ¶axi anonadeegi, onoЙЎМ¶a icoa liboonaЙЎМ¶a anonadeegita nigaanigawaanigi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyajigo icoa liboonaЙЎМ¶a, oolo, ica namoko ЙЎМ¶odatobi ane liditege lanigi niЙЎМ¶ina moyalegi, idaa ica pomaada ane liditece lanigi codaa dakake loojedi.  
\v 12 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a niotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja nigeeЙЎМ¶a, odaa oigee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ibodicaxi me daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶idiaa igotinece minitaЙЎМ¶a Herodes. Odaa joЙЎМ¶odioteci eledi naigi mopiticogi niiЙЎМ¶otedi. 
\s1 JosГ©, Maria ijaa lionicawaanigi ialeticogi Egito 
\p  
\v 13 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi noЙЎМ¶opitibeci niЙЎМ¶ijo anokegipi, JosГ© ja igee ica niaanjo ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me dinikeeta, odaa meeta, вҖңAdabititini, abaata nigaanigawaanigi, aniaa eliodo, ialeticogi niiЙЎМ¶o Egito! IdiaaЙЎМ¶oni nigepaa jao ЙЎМ¶adeemidi nige yakadi madopilitijo, igaataЙЎМ¶a Herodes doletibige me yeloadi niЙЎМ¶idi nigaanigawaanigi.вҖқ  
\v 14 Odaa JosГ© jiЙЎМ¶itibigi, ja nibatine nigaanigawaanigi ajaa eliodo, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo enoale JosГ© jiЙЎМ¶igo Egito.  
\v 15 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶i Egito neЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶icota me yeleo Herodes, odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa mewi me icotece ane lotaЙЎМ¶a ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ganigepidiЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko ane iditedini, вҖңOdaa jiniditalo ionigi me noditicogi Egito.вҖқ 
\s1 Herodes diiЙЎМ¶enatakatiogi monigodi nigaanigipawaanigi 
\p  
\v 16 NaЙЎМ¶a nadi Herodes moinaale niЙЎМ¶ijo anokegipi anoicoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigoi, odaa eliodi me deliЙЎМ¶ide. Odaa ja diiЙЎМ¶enatakatiogi monigodi iditawece nigaanigipawaanigi anidiwa itoataale nicaaЙЎМ¶ape, ane niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi BelГ©m, codaa me minoataЙЎМ¶a inoa nipodaЙЎМ¶a ane ipegitege nigotaЙЎМ¶a. Eo niЙЎМ¶ida loenatagi leeЙЎМ¶odi yowooЙЎМ¶odi neЙЎМ¶eote itoataale nicaaЙЎМ¶ape naЙЎМ¶ajo yotedi naЙЎМ¶a dinikeetiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anokegipi.  
\v 17 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee naЙЎМ¶a icotece niЙЎМ¶ijoa Jeremias lotaЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee, 
\q1  
\v 18 вҖңManitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a RamГЎ jajipaaЙЎМ¶ata layaageЙЎМ¶egi oko me nacaagaЙЎМ¶ateloco, 
\q1 eliodi me agecaЙЎМ¶alodipi. 
\q1 JaЙЎМ¶ajaa Raquel ane dacaagetibece leeЙЎМ¶odi lionigipi. 
\q1 Dacaagetibece, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me yocaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e leeЙЎМ¶odi iditawece ja nigo.вҖқ 
\s1 JosГ© ja dopi me icoЙЎМ¶oticogi Egito 
\p  
\v 19 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Herodes naЙЎМ¶a yeleo, odaa JosГ© ja dige digoida Egito. Igee ica niaanjo ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me dinikeeta.  
\v 20 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ica aanjo jeЙЎМ¶eeta, вҖңOnitibige, anibaatine nigaanigawaanigi aniaa eliodo, odaaЙЎМ¶opiliticogi nipodigi Israel, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane domoЙЎМ¶oyeloadi niЙЎМ¶ini nigaanigawaanigi aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica, ja nigo.вҖқ  
\v 21 Odaa JosГ© jiЙЎМ¶itibigi, nibatine nigaanigawaanigi, ajaa eliodo, odaa ja dopiticogi nipodigi Israel.  
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶icoticogi, odaa ja dibodiceta Arquelau, lionigi Herodes, me niЙЎМ¶iniaa diiЙЎМ¶enataka waxodi limedi eliodi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi JosГ© me doita midiaaЙЎМ¶i. Odaa JosГ© ja dige, igee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote leemidi. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo nipodigi GalilГ©ia.  
\v 23 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶i mani nigotaЙЎМ¶a NazarГ©. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee micotece lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ica jotigide, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee, вҖңOyatedigi me Nazareeno.вҖқ 
\c 3  
\s1 Latematigo JoГЈo Batista 
\r (Marcos 1.1-8; Lucas 3.1-18; JoГЈo 1.19-28) 
\p  
\v 1 NaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶atedice icoa nicaaЙЎМ¶ape, ijo ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi JoГЈo Batista jiЙЎМ¶igo nipodigi JudГ©ia ane diЙЎМ¶icata niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi. Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eetiogi niЙЎМ¶idi oko anodiita,  
\v 2 вҖңAdinilaanitece ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶ecotiwaji! IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica noko ja nipegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶ica jotigide IsaГӯas ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko, yalaЙЎМ¶ata JoГЈo, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee, 
\q1 вҖңIda oko ane igedi me dotaЙЎМ¶a miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane diЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi, anee, 
\q1 вҖҳOenitece ligi ЗӨoniotagodi me ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo! 
\q1 Codaa awiitiwaji naigi ane dixoke nigepaa enotedijoвҖҷ.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 4 JoГЈo dinixotinigi nowoodi gameelo lamodi onibila, codaa ibake goenaЙЎМ¶adi ewacogo, liweenigi ЙЎМ¶onipidi inaa napigo.  
\v 5 Eliodi oko igotibeci mowajipatalo lotaЙЎМ¶a JoГЈo, niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, codaa me nipodigi JudГ©ia, codaa midiwatawece nipodaЙЎМ¶a ane ipegitege akiidi JordГЈo.  
\v 6 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo oko joЙЎМ¶oyatemati libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco odinilaatece, odaa JoГЈo nilegetiniwace midi akiidi JordГЈo (moikee noЙЎМ¶oika mowo ane beyagi). 
\p  
\v 7 JoГЈo nadi me eliodi niЙЎМ¶ijo fariseutedi ijaa saduceutedi anigotibeci midataЙЎМ¶a me dinilegetibigiwaji. NaЙЎМ¶a nadi, odaa jeЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji ЙЎМ¶adiciagi niЙЎМ¶inoa laketedi ane diniweneene! Aleetibigetiwaji daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiwokoni niЙЎМ¶ica noko nige iloikatidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco?  
\v 8 Pida oleetibige mawii anele mikeeni mewi naЙЎМ¶adinilaanitece ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.  
\v 9 JinaЙЎМ¶aleetibige daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiwokoni niЙЎМ¶ina menitibecetiwaji, вҖҳIda anejinaЙЎМ¶atege licoЙЎМ¶egi AbraГЈo.вҖҷ IgaataЙЎМ¶a ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yakadi meote niЙЎМ¶idiwa wetiadi me lionigipi AbraГЈo.  
\v 10 Ja nipegi niЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶otedi niЙЎМ¶inoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Jiciaceeketege naЙЎМ¶ana niale anidiwa onateciЙЎМ¶idiwa nokododi, odaa ja nakagidi napalite litodi. Inoatawece niЙЎМ¶inoa niale ane daЙЎМ¶a yajigo ela anele, onakagidi, odaa oyokoletiogi minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi.  
\v 11 ЗӨadilegenitiwaji jatitaЙЎМ¶awa ninyoЙЎМ¶odi me jikee madinilaanitece ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Pida ina oko anenagi nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi ane naЙЎМ¶axatiloco. NiЙЎМ¶ini oko nige ЙЎМ¶adilegenitiwaji, odaa ibake AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a noledi me ЙЎМ¶adapitaЙЎМ¶ati. DaЙЎМ¶axa me notoedi, aiciagi, codaa daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi, caticedi ee, odaa oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jakadi me joyaЙЎМ¶adi liwelatedi.  
\v 12 Ja igo me iolatedice niЙЎМ¶ina oko anele me yawalacetege niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane beyagi. Liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko anani nibeneela libaaЙЎМ¶adi, baanaЙЎМ¶a dinenyaЙЎМ¶adi me iolatice idiwatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa leyeema lapadi. Odaa ja yotete nileyeema manitaЙЎМ¶a lotetenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa lapadi baЙЎМ¶a yalegi minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe.вҖқ 
\s1 JoГЈo naЙЎМ¶a ilege Jesus 
\r (Marcos 1.9-11; Lucas 3.21-22) 
\p  
\v 13 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa nokododi, Jesus ja noditedicogi nipodigi GalilГ©ia. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo akiidi JordГЈo maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a dinilege midataЙЎМ¶a JoГЈo.  
\v 14 Pida JoГЈo ayakadi mele codaa adomaЙЎМ¶a yemaa me ilege Jesus. Odaa mee, вҖңAkaami anagi meetaЙЎМ¶a maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a adinilegeni. Pida jeЙЎМ¶epaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a leeditibige madilegeni.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 15 Pida mee Jesus, вҖңAwii ane jemaa, adiwikodeni adilegeni! Odaa ja jaoЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yemaa.вҖқ Odaa JoГЈo ja niwoditema. 
\p  
\v 16 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi JoГЈo ja ilege Jesus, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi Jesus naЙЎМ¶a daxoditedita ninyoЙЎМ¶odi, naЙЎМ¶a iwitedibigimece ditibigimedi, odaa ja nadi me domoke ditibigimedi, codaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a naditetege Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me dinikatelogo dinanatigi yotibi, odaa ja nicotelogo.  
\v 17 Odaa digawini! NiЙЎМ¶ijo oko joЙЎМ¶owajipata ica nigegi digoida ditibigimedi, anee, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idoa Ionigi yemaanigi. Eliodi me idinitibeci leeЙЎМ¶odi IdaaЙЎМ¶idoa.вҖқ 
\c 4  
\s1 ЗӨodaxakawa icaaniЙЎМ¶igotalo Jesus 
\r (Marcos 1.12-13; Lucas 4.1-13) 
\p  
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yadeegitedicogi Jesus miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane yadilo ane diЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶icaaniЙЎМ¶igotalo ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa me dinetalo Jesus.  
\v 2 Jesus ayemaa mica ane yeligo niЙЎМ¶ijoa cwareenta nokododi, odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja nigicile.  
\v 3 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa, niЙЎМ¶icotalo Jesus, odaa meetalo, вҖңNigewi makaami Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, awii naЙЎМ¶ani wetiЙЎМ¶a me paon.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 4 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meeteta, вҖңLotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji diniditeloco, вҖҳMe diЙЎМ¶inokina niweenigi meo me yewiЙЎМ¶a oko. Pida leeditibige mowajipatalo codaa mowo inoatawece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane lotaЙЎМ¶a.вҖҷвҖқ 
\p  
\v 5 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa ja yadeegitedicogi Jesus digoida nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, nigotaЙЎМ¶a anida aneetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa ja yadeegitedibigimece ditibigimedi liЙЎМ¶eladi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ica liwai ane daЙЎМ¶axa me leegitibigimece.  
\v 6 Odaa ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa meetalo Jesus, вҖңNigewi makaami Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, adinaxokitinece digoida natinedi, igaataЙЎМ¶a lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mee, 
\q1 вҖҳAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niiЙЎМ¶e niaanjotedi modoweditaЙЎМ¶aloco. 
\q1 OilokaditaЙЎМ¶awa me diЙЎМ¶icata ЙЎМ¶ataciledi, 
\q1 codaa me daЙЎМ¶a etaciloteda ЙЎМ¶adoЙЎМ¶onaka midiwataЙЎМ¶a wetiadi.вҖҷвҖқ 
\p  
\v 7 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, вҖңPida maditaЙЎМ¶a lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji diniditeloco, mee, 
\q1 вҖҳJinaЙЎМ¶a adineenitalo ЗӨaniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji!вҖҷвҖқ 
\p  
\v 8 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa ja yadeegitedicogi Jesus ditibigimedi naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶axa me leegitibigimece, odaa ja ikeetalo iditawece noiigitigi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, codaa me niliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o.  
\v 9 Odaa ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa meetalo, вҖңJajigotaЙЎМ¶awa inatawece noiigi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o me iiЙЎМ¶eni, nige amakitedini ЙЎМ¶adokotidi moЙЎМ¶eetetiwa.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 10 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meeteta, вҖңEmii, opili, SatanГЎs! IgaataЙЎМ¶a diniditeloco lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, 
\q1 вҖҳOЙЎМ¶eetetalo ЗӨaniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, 
\q1 codaa ikani miniokiniwateda me ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶eni.вҖҷвҖқ 
\m  
\v 11 Odaa ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa ja ika Jesus, odaa aanjotedi jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci, odoweditelogo. 
\s1 Jesus jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi libakedi midi nipodigi GalilГ©ia 
\r (Marcos 1.14-15; Lucas 4.14-15) 
\p  
\v 12 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a dibodicete JoГЈo Batista moniwilo, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo nipodigi GalilГ©ia.  
\v 13 AЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶itedice nigotaЙЎМ¶a NazarГ©, pida igo idiaa liЙЎМ¶eladi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Cafarnaum, ane ipegitege weiigi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi GalilГ©ia, nipodigi Zebulom aniaa Naftali.  
\v 14 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa meo micotece lotaЙЎМ¶a IsaГӯas, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee, 
\q1  
\v 15 вҖңMiditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi Zebulom aniaa Naftali, 
\q1 naigi anigo weiigi nipodaЙЎМ¶a aneite daato akiidi JordГЈo, 
\q1 nipodigi GalilГ©ia ane liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi. 
\q1  
\v 16 MidiwataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idiwa nipodaЙЎМ¶a, 
\q1 niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi aneiteloco miditaЙЎМ¶a nexocaЙЎМ¶a onadi aca lokokena loniciweЙЎМ¶ena. 
\q1 Odaa naЙЎМ¶ani lokokena naloteloco iditawece oko aneiteloco niЙЎМ¶idiwa nipodaЙЎМ¶a 
\q1 ane liciagi nipodigi aneite niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 17 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece latematiko, mee, вҖңAdinilaanitece ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, igaataЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶ipegiteloco niЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ina oko.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus eniditediogi cwaatolo nomiigomigipi modiotece 
\r (Marcos 1.16-20; Lucas 5.1-11) 
\p  
\v 18 Jesus igotetece liniogotibece niweiigi GalilГ©ia, odaa ja nadi itoataale ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi dinioxomigi, ijo ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi SimГЈo (ane eledi oyatigi me Pedro) ijaa AndrГ©. Odibatalo noЙЎМ¶ojedi moyaa, oyokoletedinibece leelatiidi midi weiigi me nomiigomigipi.  
\v 19 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңAnagi, aniwitici! ЗӨadiiЙЎМ¶axinitiwaji anemiita oko madeegitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina mabaata noЙЎМ¶ojedi madeegitiogi oko.вҖқ \fig |src="CN01681B.TIF" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Mateus 4.18-19" \fig* 
\v 20 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi, joЙЎМ¶oikatedice leelatiidi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odiotece Jesus. 
\p  
\v 21 Jesus igoawaanigi odoe, odaa ja naditediogi eletidi itoataale ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi dinioxomigi, ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Tiago ijaa JoГЈo, lionigipi Zebedeu. IdiaaЙЎМ¶i catinedi niwatece ijaaЙЎМ¶eniodi, onapade icoa leelatiidi. Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eniditediogi modiotece.  
\v 22 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi jidiaa oyaladi Zebedeu, niЙЎМ¶ijo eniodi, ajaaЙЎМ¶ajo liwatece, odaa joЙЎМ¶odiotece Jesus. 
\s1 Jesus yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece latematiko codaa icilatidi eliodi eelotaginadi 
\r (Lucas 6.17-19) 
\p  
\v 23 Jesus igotedeloco idiwatawece nipodaЙЎМ¶a GalilГ©ia. DiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atedibece minoataЙЎМ¶a liiakanaЙЎМ¶axiidi judeutedi. YeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece ЙЎМ¶obodicetedi anele micota me iiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶enali. Codaa nicilatiditedi ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa eelotaginadi, codaa me ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo ane nawikodeeЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 24 Nibodicetedi aneetece Jesus ilaagiteloco iditawece nipodigi SГӯria. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi monadeegitalo Jesus ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa eelotaginadi. Odaa icilatidi inoatawece ane latopaco neelotika, codaa me niЙЎМ¶inoa ane ЙЎМ¶odileenaЙЎМ¶a, inoa anodakatiogi niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, codaa nicilatiditedi yetoledi, codaa me alejaadotedi ane daЙЎМ¶adiaa ditineЙЎМ¶e. Jesus nicilatidi ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo anenagitibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 25 Eliodi oko anodiotece. Idi ica noiigi anoicoЙЎМ¶oticogi nipodigi GalilГ©ia, idi anoicoЙЎМ¶oticogi micoataЙЎМ¶a icoa deez nigotadi anei oko anodotaЙЎМ¶atigi nioladi greegotedi, idi anoicoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, codaa me nipodigi JudГ©ia, codaa midiwataЙЎМ¶a nipodaЙЎМ¶a daato akiidi JordГЈo. 
\c 5  
\s1 Jesus niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi ane yatecoЙЎМ¶o minitaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo lojotaЙЎМ¶adi 
\p  
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a naditetege Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi anenagitibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja dalaЙЎМ¶atetedibigimece ica lojotaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa ja nicotedini. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo oko anodiotece joЙЎМ¶odipegitalo.  
\v 2 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atediniwace. 
\s1 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane ninitibigiwaji 
\r (Lucas 6.20-23) 
\p  
\v 3 Odaa mee, 
\q1 вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina oko anoyowooЙЎМ¶odi me diЙЎМ¶ica ane leeЙЎМ¶odi daЙЎМ¶a dinanetibigiwaji lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, 
\q1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icota me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶idi oko, 
\q1 joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi oko midioka limedi me ninitibigiwaji. 
\q1  
\v 4 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane agecaЙЎМ¶alodipi niЙЎМ¶ina natigide, 
\q1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icota me yocaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶idi oko, 
\q1 joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi oko midioka limedi me ninitibigiwaji. 
\q1  
\v 5 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane diniwikodetibece lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, 
\q1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote me nebi inatawece iiЙЎМ¶o, 
\q1 joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi oko midioka limedi me ninitibigiwaji. 
\q1  
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane doletibige ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, 
\q1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icota meote meletibigiwaji, 
\q1 leeЙЎМ¶odi me liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane nigodi nigigi, 
\q1 codaa me ecibi. 
\q1 Odaa nigoyakadi anoyeligo, 
\q1 codaa anowacipe, 
\q1 odaa jeЙЎМ¶eletibigiwaji. 
\q1 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi oko midioka limedi me ninitibigiwaji. 
\q1  
\v 7 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko anoiwikode eledi oko, 
\q1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niwikodetediniwace, 
\q1 joaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi oko midioka limedi me ninitibigiwaji. 
\q1  
\v 8 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane yapidi laaleЙЎМ¶enali, 
\q1 icota monadi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. 
\q1 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi oko midioka limedi me ninitibigiwaji. 
\q1  
\v 9 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane ilakidetaciwage niЙЎМ¶ina oko anijo me nidelaЙЎМ¶a, 
\q1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eetediogi me lionigipi. 
\q1 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi oko midioka limedi me ninitibigiwaji. 
\q1  
\v 10 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko anoiatetibece leeЙЎМ¶odi mowo ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, 
\q1 icota AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali codaa me yaxawatediogi. 
\q1 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi oko midioka limedi me ninitibigiwaji. 
\p  
\v 11 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko nigodotaЙЎМ¶atibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji, nige etiЙЎМ¶adiatenitibece codaa nige odiwitakatibigaЙЎМ¶ajitiwaji, modi mawii ane beyagi, leeЙЎМ¶odi me aniwiticitiwaji, odaa icota maniniitibecitiwaji.  
\v 12 Enice aniniitibecitiwaji, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yotetetedaЙЎМ¶adomi digoida ditibigimedi niЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ajegi ane daЙЎМ¶axa mele. IgaataЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee moiatetibeci niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide. (Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigotediogi naЙЎМ¶ajegi anele.) 
\s1 ЗӨadiciagitiwaji yoci anaa lokokena 
\r (Marcos 9.50; Lucas 14.34-35) 
\p  
\v 13 NiЙЎМ¶ida makamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji ЙЎМ¶adiciagi yoci liwigotigi inatawece oko. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina yoci nige aniaditema loniciwaЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶a ika me beyagi niweenigi, odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi daЙЎМ¶a agelaЙЎМ¶atiti loniciwaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica ane jaoЙЎМ¶a, alati, odaa oko joЙЎМ¶onipodi. (Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶enitiwaji ЙЎМ¶adiciagi yoci, leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶ikanitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina ane beyagi daЙЎМ¶a ibeyacaЙЎМ¶adi oko lewiЙЎМ¶a.)  
\v 14 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiciagi naЙЎМ¶ana lokokena ane naloteloco inatawece oko, igaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ica anaЙЎМ¶atitini, leeЙЎМ¶odi mikeeni catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adewiЙЎМ¶a ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Codaa aЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me yaЙЎМ¶aditini nigotaЙЎМ¶a anodabiteЙЎМ¶eti ditibigimedi wetiЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 15 AЙЎМ¶ica ane yalegi noledaЙЎМ¶axi, oditaЙЎМ¶a yapoЙЎМ¶oditinigi anigetaЙЎМ¶ada naЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi. Pida naЙЎМ¶ana noledaЙЎМ¶axi oipeke ditibigimedi, mowo me naloteloco iditawece ane idei catiwedi diimigi.  
\v 16 JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee ikani ЙЎМ¶anilokokenatiwaji me Гӯdi, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oyakadi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko monadi ЙЎМ¶abakedi anele anawiitetiwaji, awii modoЙЎМ¶etetibigimece ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi. 
\s1 NiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi aneetece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s 
\p  
\v 17 JinaЙЎМ¶aleetibige daЙЎМ¶a janagi me jaaЙЎМ¶adi lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, ijaa liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko. Ee ajanagi daЙЎМ¶a jaaЙЎМ¶adi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, pida janagi me jotete codaa me jao me yeloЙЎМ¶o niЙЎМ¶ica anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece.  
\v 18 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. NigepaaЙЎМ¶icota me daa ditibigimedi, codaa me iiЙЎМ¶o, aЙЎМ¶ica ane noЙЎМ¶a gaantokaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶inoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. AЙЎМ¶ica gaantokaaЙЎМ¶idi anonoЙЎМ¶a nigepaa owidijegi noko nige ma niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o.  
\v 19 Enice niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶a yotete okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶ecawaanigi ane deЙЎМ¶ewi me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi, codaa nige iiЙЎМ¶axi eledi oko me deЙЎМ¶eyiwaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ini oko lionigawaanigi liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ina oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iiЙЎМ¶e. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane yotete ijoatawece niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, codaa maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶axi eledi oko me yotete idiwatawece niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, niЙЎМ¶ini oko baaniЙЎМ¶iniaa daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶idi oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iiЙЎМ¶e.  
\v 20 IgaataЙЎМ¶a ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji icota AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali, codaa akaamitiwaji jiЙЎМ¶ida anenitege nige daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶adeЙЎМ¶enakitiwaji caticedi niЙЎМ¶inoa fariseutedi inaa niЙЎМ¶ina niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s. 
\s1 Ayakadi daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odelatema ЙЎМ¶onioxoa 
\p  
\v 21 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji jaЙЎМ¶ajipaata niЙЎМ¶ijo MoisГ©s aneeta, aneetiogi jotigide ЙЎМ¶adaamipi, вҖҳJineЙЎМ¶eloati eledi oko! IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane daije oyadeegiticogi minitaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶oniwinoЙЎМ¶odi.вҖҷ  
\v 22 Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane yelatema nioxoa me diЙЎМ¶ica leeЙЎМ¶odi, niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oniwinoЙЎМ¶odi iwi niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶igota. Nigica aneeta nioxoa, вҖҳAkaami yetole!вҖҷ JoaniЙЎМ¶iniaa oyadeegiticogi miditaЙЎМ¶a seteenta lacilodi noiigi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo aneeta nioxoa me daЙЎМ¶axa me beyagi, aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica aneetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa doidetibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶etedicogi niЙЎМ¶ini oko minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe.  
\v 23 Enice nige emii AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi madeegitalo noЙЎМ¶eedi ditibigimedi nameeja AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa analakitibige ЙЎМ¶anioxoa mijo me dinotigimadetaЙЎМ¶agi.  
\v 24 IdiaaЙЎМ¶anitice ЙЎМ¶aboonigi lodoe nameeja. Odaa ecoЙЎМ¶otace oleetibige me ЙЎМ¶adilakiitege ЙЎМ¶anioxoa, nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi nige naЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adilakiitege, odaa jaЙЎМ¶ajicitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶aboonigitalo. 
\p  
\v 25 Nigica ane lowoogo me ЙЎМ¶adadeegita ЙЎМ¶oniwinoЙЎМ¶odi me yeloЙЎМ¶odi mida ЙЎМ¶adoenatagi ane beyagi, adinilakidenitege maleediЙЎМ¶icoota ЙЎМ¶oniwinoЙЎМ¶odi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a doidetibige daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adadeegiticogi minitaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶oniwinoЙЎМ¶odi, odaa ЙЎМ¶oniwinoЙЎМ¶odi ja ЙЎМ¶adajicitiogi iodaЙЎМ¶awadi. Odaa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi etiЙЎМ¶adixomitiwece niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi.  
\v 26 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. AЙЎМ¶anotiticogitiwaji niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi nigepaaЙЎМ¶ediani icoatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa ЙЎМ¶anaaleweta niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa. 
\s1 NiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi ane yalaЙЎМ¶ata noЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi 
\p  
\v 27 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji joЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti niЙЎМ¶ijo aneeta MoisГ©s niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, neЙЎМ¶ee, вҖҳJinaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adoomatewa iwaalo wadonaЙЎМ¶a.вҖҷ  
\v 28 Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane iwita iwaalo ane daЙЎМ¶a lodawa, odaa nige yowo me loomatewa, odaa catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena ja doЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶ataka.  
\v 29 Enice ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶eli nigeo mowoo ane beyagi catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena, odaa anoЙЎМ¶aatice ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶e, alati! IgaataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mele maniatitema ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶e, pida aЙЎМ¶oyokoletiogi iditawece ЙЎМ¶adolaadi minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe.  
\v 30 ЗӨabaaЙЎМ¶adi nigeo mawii ane beyagi, akagiti, odaa alati. IgaataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mele maniatitema onidateci ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶adi, pida aЙЎМ¶oyokoletiogi iditawece ЙЎМ¶adolaadi minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe. 
\s1 NiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi aneetece nalataЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi 
\r (Mateus 19.9; Marcos 10.11-12; Lucas 16.18) 
\p  
\v 31 Moditibece niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, вҖҳNiЙЎМ¶ina ane yaladi naЙЎМ¶ana lodawa, odaa leeditibige me yajigota notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi me ikee naЙЎМ¶a yaladi lodawa.вҖҷ  
\v 32 Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, inoatawece ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anoiiЙЎМ¶e lodawa mopi, odaa naЙЎМ¶ani iwaalo nige wadotace, odaa niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa nalatoЙЎМ¶odi jeЙЎМ¶eo me doЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶ataka naЙЎМ¶ani iwaalo. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ini gela lodawa naЙЎМ¶ani iwaalo jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶ataka. Idoka yakadi malati ЙЎМ¶adodawa nige ЙЎМ¶adoЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶ati. 
\s1 NiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco aneetece me leeditibige me jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina anejinaЙЎМ¶a me jaoЙЎМ¶a 
\p  
\v 33 Codaa owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji anoditiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide ЙЎМ¶odaamipi, noЙЎМ¶oditiogi, вҖҳJinaЙЎМ¶a inetee niЙЎМ¶ina naЙЎМ¶awii anigida ЙЎМ¶agegi, pida awii niЙЎМ¶ica ane enitalo ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mawii.вҖҷ  
\v 34 Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, nigawii ЙЎМ¶agegi, jinaЙЎМ¶abakeni liboonaЙЎМ¶adi anigetiЙЎМ¶idi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a eledi oko liboonaЙЎМ¶adi. JinaЙЎМ¶a aboonaЙЎМ¶ateeni ditibigimedi mawii ЙЎМ¶agegi, igaataЙЎМ¶a ditibigimedi jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶i me diiЙЎМ¶enataka AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 35 Codaa jinaЙЎМ¶abakeni liboonaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, igaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o liciagi naЙЎМ¶ana baanco aneite AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me nipeneЙЎМ¶etedini loЙЎМ¶onaka. Codaa jinaЙЎМ¶abakeni liboonaЙЎМ¶adi JerusalГ©m, igaataЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ani nigotaЙЎМ¶a nebi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, minionigi-eliodi.  
\v 36 Codaa jinaЙЎМ¶abakeni niboonaЙЎМ¶adi makamaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adacilo mawii ЙЎМ¶agegi, igaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶animaweneЙЎМ¶egitece ЙЎМ¶adacilo molii me diЙЎМ¶ica otiЙЎМ¶idatece ЙЎМ¶adamodi me yapacaЙЎМ¶a migetaЙЎМ¶a nabidi.  
\v 37 Pida nigawii ЙЎМ¶agegi, onexaaЙЎМ¶eni, вҖҳJaoвҖҷ, oЙЎМ¶oa domige eni, вҖҳAjaoвҖҷ, igaataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶awii eledi ЙЎМ¶agegi, niЙЎМ¶ida eledi ЙЎМ¶agegi ja icoЙЎМ¶oticogi mijotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo ane beyagi, ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa. 
\s1 AЙЎМ¶ele daЙЎМ¶a joleeЙЎМ¶atibige me jojeteeЙЎМ¶a 
\r (Lucas 6.29-30) 
\p  
\v 38 OwooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide moditibece, вҖҳAnoЙЎМ¶aa ligecooЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ina ane napoace ligecooЙЎМ¶e eledi oko. Codaa aninokeni lowe niЙЎМ¶ina ane ninoke lowe eledi oko.вҖҷ  
\v 39 Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji jinoЙЎМ¶oojeteeta niЙЎМ¶ina aneo ane beyagitaЙЎМ¶adomi. Nigica ane yabaketigi ЙЎМ¶adajice, odaa ajici eledi ЙЎМ¶adajice maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yabake.  
\v 40 Nigica ane ЙЎМ¶adadeegiticogi minitaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶oniwinoЙЎМ¶odi me doletibige me dinigaanyetece ЙЎМ¶anoecaЙЎМ¶axi, odaa ikanitece maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yadeegi ЙЎМ¶anibalito.  
\v 41 Nigica iodaЙЎМ¶awa ane iiЙЎМ¶etaЙЎМ¶awa moyaЙЎМ¶ati loyaЙЎМ¶aka onadateci ciloomito, odaa adeegitema nigepaa itoa ciloomito.  
\v 42 Ediani niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane dipokotibece, codaa jinaЙЎМ¶aciiletema niЙЎМ¶ina ane dadilaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶awa. 
\s1 Leeditibige memaani ЙЎМ¶adaxakawepodi 
\r (Lucas 6.27-28, 32-36) 
\p  
\v 43 OwooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide moditibece, вҖҳLeeditibige memaani ЙЎМ¶adoiigi, odaa ЙЎМ¶adeleЙЎМ¶edi niЙЎМ¶ina anakaami leleЙЎМ¶edi.вҖҷ  
\v 44 Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji leeditibige memaani ЙЎМ¶aneloЙЎМ¶ododipi. Codaa oeni motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni niЙЎМ¶ina anetiЙЎМ¶adixoomitiwaji. Codaa otaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mipokitalo meote aneletema niЙЎМ¶ina aneo ane beyagitaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji codaa niЙЎМ¶ina anetiЙЎМ¶adiatenitibece.  
\v 45 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶ikeenitiwaji mewi makaami lionigipi ЗӨadiodi ane ideite digoida ditibigimedi. IniaaЙЎМ¶iniwa daЙЎМ¶axa meletedoЙЎМ¶odomi, igaataЙЎМ¶a eote naЙЎМ¶ani aligeЙЎМ¶e ane nebi me naloteloco oko anele, codaa me niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane beyagi. Codaa niwakateetedigi ebici niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 46 IgaataЙЎМ¶a nige inoka emaani niЙЎМ¶ina ane ЙЎМ¶ademaanitiwaji, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ayajigotedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ajegi, igaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina anodibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi, jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi analeetibige doЙЎМ¶owidi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, pida idiaaЙЎМ¶idi oyemaa lokaaЙЎМ¶etedi.  
\v 47 Nige anicenitiwaji codaa nige ikeenitiogi ЙЎМ¶ademaanaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi idiokidi ЙЎМ¶adoiigi, odaa aЙЎМ¶awiitetiwaji anele caticedi niЙЎМ¶idi eledi oko anowo, igaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane doЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶oditeda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji owo liciagi.  
\v 48 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji leeditibige mawii aneletema inatawece oko liciagi ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi, igaataЙЎМ¶a idioka limedi meletetema inatawece oko.вҖқ 
\c 6  
\s1 Jesus ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶axi anodaaЙЎМ¶ejinaЙЎМ¶a me jaxawanaЙЎМ¶a eledi oko 
\p  
\v 1 Jesus eЙЎМ¶idaa diitigi me dotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa mee, вҖңAdinowetitiwaji! NiЙЎМ¶ina nigaxawanitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anida lemaЙЎМ¶amatiigi, jinaЙЎМ¶awii lodoe eledi oko, moleetibige metiЙЎМ¶adiweniЙЎМ¶ideni. IgaataЙЎМ¶a nigawiitiwaji me lodoe eledi oko, odaa ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi ayajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ajegi.  
\v 2 Enice niЙЎМ¶ina maxawani okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica oko anida lemaЙЎМ¶amatiigi, jinaЙЎМ¶a adineleЙЎМ¶enitiogi inatawece oko micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko anokowo meletibigiwaji minoataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa niiakanaЙЎМ¶axiidi, codaa me ladicotiidi nigotaЙЎМ¶a. NiЙЎМ¶idi oko inoka odoletibige moiweniЙЎМ¶ide. EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi, niЙЎМ¶idi oko jiЙЎМ¶idokida moiweniЙЎМ¶ide, odaa aЙЎМ¶odibatege naЙЎМ¶ajegi ane domaЙЎМ¶a yajigotediogi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 3 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina maxawani okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica oko anida lemaЙЎМ¶amatiigi, awii makamokakaami mowooЙЎМ¶oti!  
\v 4 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee aЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina maxawani niЙЎМ¶ina oko anida lemaЙЎМ¶amatiigi. Iniokiniwateda ЗӨadiodi me yowooЙЎМ¶odi! IgaataЙЎМ¶a baЙЎМ¶a nadi inoatawece. Odaa yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ajegi lodoe eledi oko. 
\s1 NiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi anodaaЙЎМ¶ejinaЙЎМ¶a me jotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji 
\r (Lucas 11.2-4) 
\p  
\v 5 NiЙЎМ¶ina motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, jinaЙЎМ¶awii liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anokeo mele, ane lemaanigi me dabiditiniwace niЙЎМ¶ina moyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji catiwedi liЙЎМ¶eladi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, inaa loЙЎМ¶omoce ladicotiidi, owotibige minatawece oko onadi odaa oiweniЙЎМ¶ide. EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi, aЙЎМ¶odibatege anigetiЙЎМ¶ica naЙЎМ¶ajegi miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, inoka odibatege liweniЙЎМ¶idenaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi niЙЎМ¶ina oko.  
\v 6 Pida niЙЎМ¶ida makaami, nigotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, akaatiwece ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi, anibatooni ЙЎМ¶adapoagi, odaa otaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЗӨadiodi, leeЙЎМ¶odi iniwa okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ane onitice. JiЙЎМ¶iniaa ЗӨadiodi ane ЙЎМ¶adati okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ane onitice odaa yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ajegi lodoe eledi oko. 
\p  
\v 7 NiЙЎМ¶ina motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, jinoЙЎМ¶opilaЙЎМ¶atitibigeloco ЙЎМ¶agegi ane diЙЎМ¶icata ane niitigi, anee niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane doЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶oditeda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a odiletibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶a wajipatediogi niЙЎМ¶ina meliodi me notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 8 JinoЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶awii liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЗӨadiodi ja yowooЙЎМ¶odi anopootibige, maleediЙЎМ¶icatibige diЙЎМ¶ipokitalo.  
\v 9 Enice nigotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji etida alitigi ЙЎМ¶agegi, 
\b  
\q1 вҖҳЗӨodiodi anadeoni digoida ditibigimedi, 
\q1 jemaanaЙЎМ¶a minatawece oko oiweniЙЎМ¶ide ЗӨaboonaЙЎМ¶adi. 
\q1  
\v 10 IiЙЎМ¶eni laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ina oko. 
\q1 JemaanaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko mowo digoina iiЙЎМ¶o niЙЎМ¶ica anemaani, 
\q1 digo anee midi anowo anemaani digoida ditibigimedi. 
\q1  
\v 11 ЗӨodedianiЙЎМ¶itece ЙЎМ¶oweenigi ane jopooЙЎМ¶atibige niЙЎМ¶ina noko. 
\q1  
\v 12 IxomaЙЎМ¶ateenitedice ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, 
\q1 digo anejinaЙЎМ¶a me jixomaЙЎМ¶ateenaЙЎМ¶atedice libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco eledi oko anowotoЙЎМ¶odomi. 
\q1  
\v 13 JiniЙЎМ¶ikani niЙЎМ¶ina ane beyagi daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odice oditeЙЎМ¶eo me jaoЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi. 
\q1 Pida ЙЎМ¶odatamaЙЎМ¶ateenitege ane beyagi, 
\q1 niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa. 
\q1 IgaataЙЎМ¶a jaЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶akaami ane iiЙЎМ¶eni laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ina oko. 
\q1 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaami eliodi ЙЎМ¶adoniciwaЙЎМ¶a, 
\q1 codaa inatawece oko odoЙЎМ¶etetaЙЎМ¶awa. 
\q1 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee nigepaa ganigicatibige. 
\q1 JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee (AmГ©m).вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 14 IgaataЙЎМ¶a nige ixomaЙЎМ¶ateenitedicetiwaji libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco eledi oko anowotaЙЎМ¶adomi, odaa ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.  
\v 15 Pida nige daЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶ateenitedice libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco eledi oko anowotaЙЎМ¶adomi, odaa ЗӨadiodi aixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. 
\s1 Jesus diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atetece ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me jikanakawaanigi me jiniodaЙЎМ¶a me jotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji 
\p  
\v 16 Ele midatibece me daЙЎМ¶a jiniodaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina me joleeЙЎМ¶atibige meneЙЎМ¶egi jipecaЙЎМ¶atege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Nige ikanawaanigi manioditiwaji motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, jinaЙЎМ¶awii micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶akaami agecaЙЎМ¶alo, anee niЙЎМ¶ina anokowo meletibigiwaji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a anapiladaЙЎМ¶a owotibige eledi oko moyowooЙЎМ¶odi moikanawaanigi me niodaЙЎМ¶a. EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. NiЙЎМ¶idi oko aЙЎМ¶odinigaanyetetece laЙЎМ¶ajedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, inoka odinigaanyetece liweniЙЎМ¶idenaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko.  
\v 17-18 Pida akamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji, niЙЎМ¶ina me daЙЎМ¶aniodi, anapiladi, codaa iteci ЙЎМ¶adamodi, odaa aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko mikanawaanigi maniodi. Pida iniokiniwateda ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi codaa ane ideite okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ane oni baЙЎМ¶a yowooЙЎМ¶odi. Odaa ЗӨadiodi ane nadi anawii okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ane oni, yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ajegi lodoe niЙЎМ¶ina oko anigida noko. 
\s1 NiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco ane yalaЙЎМ¶atalo icoa ЙЎМ¶oniliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi ane daЙЎМ¶a daateda 
\r (Lucas 12.33-34) 
\p  
\v 19 JinaЙЎМ¶a ateciЙЎМ¶i ЙЎМ¶aniliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, igaataЙЎМ¶a inoa ipilaЙЎМ¶awaana inaa ligowiiЙЎМ¶a anoyaaЙЎМ¶adi ane ЙЎМ¶oniliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi, codaa inoa olicaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a moyojiketi nibaloote diimigi, odaa ja dakatiobece me nolicaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 20 Pida ateciЙЎМ¶i ЙЎМ¶aniliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi digoida ditibigimedi ane diЙЎМ¶icoa ipilaЙЎМ¶awaana inaa ligowiiЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶oyaaЙЎМ¶adi ane ЙЎМ¶anepilidi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a olicaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶oyakadi me dakatiobece daЙЎМ¶a nolicaЙЎМ¶a. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶icoa ЙЎМ¶oniliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi digoida ditibigimedi aliciaco niЙЎМ¶inoa ane jakataЙЎМ¶ate digoina iiЙЎМ¶o.  
\v 21 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ida moko ЙЎМ¶odemaanigi midiokaanaЙЎМ¶a limedi me idejonaЙЎМ¶a aneite ЙЎМ¶oniliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi. 
\s1 Aca nilokokena ЙЎМ¶odolaadi 
\r (Lucas 11.34-36) 
\p  
\v 22 Nigoleetibige inokina ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa ЙЎМ¶adiciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anele ligecooЙЎМ¶eli. MicataЙЎМ¶a nilokokena AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶a dakatiwece ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶eli, odaa idei catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena me ikeetaЙЎМ¶awa ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 23 Pida nige doЙЎМ¶oleetibige mawii ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa baЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane beyagi ligecooЙЎМ¶eli. MicataЙЎМ¶a nilokokena AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daaditaЙЎМ¶a yakadi me dakatiwece ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena me ikeetaЙЎМ¶awa ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa nexogotiwe ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ica nexocaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa me nexocaЙЎМ¶a, odaa aЙЎМ¶akati doЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti niЙЎМ¶ica ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. 
\s1 Ica ane leeditibige me joleeЙЎМ¶atibige 
\r (Lucas 16.13; 12.22-31) 
\p  
\v 24 AЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me dibatema iniwataale necalaixedi, igaataЙЎМ¶a oniniteci yemaa, iniЙЎМ¶eledi baЙЎМ¶a leleЙЎМ¶edi, odaa yoe libakedi niЙЎМ¶ini anepaЙЎМ¶a yemaa. Pida niЙЎМ¶ini eledi baadaЙЎМ¶a deemitetibige. AЙЎМ¶akatitiwaji mabaatema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, oditaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oleetibige mowidi ЙЎМ¶aninyeelo.  
\v 25 Enice ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji jinaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶owikomataatibige ЙЎМ¶aweenigi, codaa anopootibige me ЙЎМ¶adewiki, codaa jinaЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶owikomataatibige ЙЎМ¶adowoodaЙЎМ¶agi ane leeditibige madinixomitinigi, igaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶atema diЙЎМ¶idokida me idinixomaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 26 Digawini niЙЎМ¶inoa ilaaЙЎМ¶axodi ane wayotiwaji digoina! AЙЎМ¶enanaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, codaa aЙЎМ¶icoa lawodigijedi doЙЎМ¶onopilaЙЎМ¶aditedio, codaa aЙЎМ¶oyatecoЙЎМ¶otee liweenaЙЎМ¶a. Pida ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a ika maniaditibige liweenigi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji baЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mida ЙЎМ¶aniwalГіtema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji caticedi niЙЎМ¶inoa ilaaЙЎМ¶axodi.  
\v 27 AЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me iigitice lewiЙЎМ¶a otiЙЎМ¶idatece noko leeЙЎМ¶odi me igecaЙЎМ¶aleЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ica ane yopotibige me yewiЙЎМ¶a. 
\p  
\v 28 Igaamee ina me ЙЎМ¶adigecaЙЎМ¶aleЙЎМ¶enitiwaji ЙЎМ¶adowoodaЙЎМ¶agi? Digawini anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me iliteloco nipodigi niЙЎМ¶inoa niale lawoЙЎМ¶o. NiЙЎМ¶idiwa niale lawoЙЎМ¶o anibaaЙЎМ¶a, codaa aЙЎМ¶icoa lowoodi loenataka modinixotinigilo.  
\v 29 Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶inoa niale lawoЙЎМ¶o daЙЎМ¶axa me libinienaЙЎМ¶a caticedi niЙЎМ¶icoa lowoodi inionigi-eliodi SalomГЈo anowidi niliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi codaa dinixotinigilo nowoodi ane daЙЎМ¶axa me libinienaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 30 Digawini niЙЎМ¶ina nadegogo aninaa, icota me yadilo, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyalegi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote nadegogo me libinienigi micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a dinixotinigilo niЙЎМ¶inoa nowoodi ane daЙЎМ¶axa me libinienaЙЎМ¶a. Enice nigeote nadegogo me libinienigi, odaa ajawienatakanaЙЎМ¶a maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adinixomeЙЎМ¶enitetiwaji idaaЙЎМ¶ida me deЙЎМ¶eliodi ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi. 
\p  
\v 31 Enice jinaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶owikomataatiwaji, jineЙЎМ¶eni, вҖҳIgamige jakataЙЎМ¶a ane jelicaЙЎМ¶a?вҖҷ codaa jineЙЎМ¶eni, вҖҳIgamige jakataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odowoodaЙЎМ¶agi?вҖҷ  
\v 32 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane doЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶oditeda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baЙЎМ¶a odoЙЎМ¶owikomatatibige anoyeligo, codaa me lowoodaЙЎМ¶agi. ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi yowooЙЎМ¶odi mopootibigetiwaji maniodi, codaa anadinixomitinigi.  
\v 33 Pida odoejegi oleetibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko, codaa oleetibige minatawece oko owo ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji inatawece anopootibige.  
\v 34 Enice jinaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adigecaЙЎМ¶aleЙЎМ¶eni niЙЎМ¶ica anopootibige natiinigoi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a anoЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti niЙЎМ¶ica ane diЙЎМ¶ica natiinigoi. JaЙЎМ¶abo niЙЎМ¶inoa ane dakaketaЙЎМ¶adomi niЙЎМ¶ina noko, odaa aЙЎМ¶ele daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adigecaЙЎМ¶aleЙЎМ¶eni niЙЎМ¶ica ane dakaketaЙЎМ¶adomi natiinigoi.вҖқ 
\c 7  
\s1 Leeditibige me daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶olaagedi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a anee 
\r (Lucas 6.37-38, 41-42) 
\p  
\v 1 Jesus eЙЎМ¶idaa diitigi me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a, odaa mee, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶awini anee lewiЙЎМ¶a eledi oko oditaЙЎМ¶a adinanimiЙЎМ¶ita, adaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶akaami laagetedipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 2 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶adiwini digo aneni me ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶oatita eledi oko. AnodaaЙЎМ¶emiita eledi oko, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji idaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a igotedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji. 
\p  
\v 3 Igame leeЙЎМ¶odi mawini libatiicawaanigi ЙЎМ¶anioxoa, ane micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a laЙЎМ¶amicaЙЎМ¶ajecawaanigi ЙЎМ¶anioxoa, pida akamaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶abatiigi aЙЎМ¶anati, ane micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a iwoЙЎМ¶o liwai catiwedi ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶elitiwaji?  
\v 4 Ica mabo ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena menita ЙЎМ¶anioxoa, вҖҳInoЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶adomi ЙЎМ¶adaЙЎМ¶amicaЙЎМ¶ajegiвҖҷ, pida idi iwoЙЎМ¶o liwai catiwedi ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶e?  
\v 5 ЗӨadiciagi niЙЎМ¶ina anokeo mele! Odoejegi leeditibige manoЙЎМ¶aa iwoЙЎМ¶o liwai ane idei catiwedi ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶e, amanagawini anatiteloco manoЙЎМ¶aa laЙЎМ¶amicaЙЎМ¶ajecawaanigi ЙЎМ¶anioxoa. 
\p  
\v 6 JinaЙЎМ¶ajicitiogi niЙЎМ¶idi oko abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane iomaЙЎМ¶aditetema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idi oko liciagi necexodi ane diojo, odaa doidetibige deЙЎМ¶etiЙЎМ¶adowacitiwaji. Codaa jineЙЎМ¶enitiogi niЙЎМ¶idi oko niЙЎМ¶inoa notaЙЎМ¶a anele AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedaЙЎМ¶awa, igaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa notaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yeloЙЎМ¶odi liciagi naЙЎМ¶ana wetiЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶axa me dakake loojedi. Codaa niЙЎМ¶idi oko abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a liciagi nigidagiwadi. Nige okolenitiogi nigidagiwadi naЙЎМ¶ani wetiЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶onipoditibige naЙЎМ¶ani wetiЙЎМ¶a ane dakake loojedi. 
\s1 JakataЙЎМ¶a me jipokaЙЎМ¶atalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ica ane jopooЙЎМ¶atibige 
\r (Lucas 11.9-13) 
\p  
\v 7 Ipokitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ica anopootibige, odaa jaЙЎМ¶abaategetiwaji. Oleetibige miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina anele anepaa yemaa me yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, odaa jaЙЎМ¶akatitiwaji. Atokeni epoagi, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja yomoke.  
\v 8 IgaataЙЎМ¶a inatawece oko anodipokotalo, odibatege lipoketegi, codaa inatawece oko anodoletibige anigidi, oyakadi. Codaa yomoketetema epoagi niЙЎМ¶ina ane yatoke.  
\v 9 ЗӨadionigi nige dipokotaЙЎМ¶awa paon, domige ajicita wetiЙЎМ¶a?  
\v 10 Ina me dipokotaЙЎМ¶awa noЙЎМ¶ojegi, domige ajicita lakeedi?  
\v 11 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaami anakaami abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, pida owooЙЎМ¶oti majicita ЙЎМ¶adionigipi niЙЎМ¶ina anele. ApiЙЎМ¶ikoa ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ina anele niЙЎМ¶ina oko modipokotalo.  
\v 12 Awiitema eledi oko niЙЎМ¶ica anemaanitiwaji modigotaЙЎМ¶awa. IgaataЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a MoisГ©s niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a idГӯ niЙЎМ¶ijoa lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco, codaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. 
\s1 Icoa itiwataale naicoli 
\r (Lucas 13.24) 
\p  
\v 13 AdinoniciwaЙЎМ¶ati makaatiwece mida epoacawaanigi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ida eledi epoagi nelegi codaa me niЙЎМ¶ijo naigi aЙЎМ¶ica laЙЎМ¶aliigi me jiwaЙЎМ¶atece dowiceta miditaЙЎМ¶a ica aneitice niЙЎМ¶ina oko me diЙЎМ¶ica liniogo me nawikodeeЙЎМ¶a. Codaa eliodi oko anodioteci niЙЎМ¶ijo naigi.  
\v 14 Pida niЙЎМ¶ida epoacawaanigi ijaa niЙЎМ¶ijo naicawaanigi ane dakake me jiwaЙЎМ¶atece, baЙЎМ¶a dowiceticogi miditaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica aneitice niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane newiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa baadeЙЎМ¶eliodi oko anodioteci niЙЎМ¶ijo naicawaanigi. 
\s1 Ica awitakegipi anokowo miniЙЎМ¶ina anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji 
\r (Lucas 6.43-44) 
\p  
\v 15 Anidakitiogi niЙЎМ¶ina anodi moyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida niwitakaЙЎМ¶a. NiЙЎМ¶idi oko anokowo moyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko oinaale niЙЎМ¶ina oko. Liciagi diwilecoЙЎМ¶oni me doide, odinixotinigi lamodi waxacoco moinaale waxacoco. Odaa niЙЎМ¶idi oko liciagi waxacoco.  
\v 16 Pida icota mowooЙЎМ¶oti anidi leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa loenataka, anodaaЙЎМ¶ee mowooЙЎМ¶oti ane latopagi niale leeЙЎМ¶otedi elali. IgaataЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ana omiigonaЙЎМ¶a ayajigo uuva, codaa niЙЎМ¶inoa lalepiЙЎМ¶igoli aЙЎМ¶oyajigo fiigo.  
\v 17 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee naЙЎМ¶ana niale anele yajigo elali anele, codaa naЙЎМ¶ana niale ane deЙЎМ¶ele yajigo elali ane beyagi.  
\v 18 NaЙЎМ¶ana niale anele ayakadi daЙЎМ¶a yajigo elali ane beyagi. Codaa naЙЎМ¶ana niale ane beyagi ayakadi daЙЎМ¶a yajigo elali anele.  
\v 19 NaЙЎМ¶ana niale ane daЙЎМ¶a yajigo elali anele, oyakagidi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyokoletiogi noledi.  
\v 20 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa me jakataЙЎМ¶a me jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ana niale leeЙЎМ¶otedi elali ane yajigo. JiЙЎМ¶idaa maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jakataЙЎМ¶a me jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idiwa awitakaЙЎМ¶a anodi moyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa loenataka. 
\s1 NiЙЎМ¶ica oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane dibatetege 
\r (Lucas 13.25-27) 
\p  
\v 21 Eliodi oko idoka etidadatigi, вҖҳIniotagodi, Iniotagodi!вҖҷ Pida aЙЎМ¶iditawece odakatiwece digoida ditibigimedi aneitedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me diiЙЎМ¶enataka. Pida inokina niЙЎМ¶ina anowo Eiodi ane yemaa, idiokidi baЙЎМ¶a dakatiobece digoida ditibigimedi aneitedice Eiodi.  
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶ica noko nige iwi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anigotediogi inatawece oko, odaa eliodi oko moditiwa, вҖҳIniotagodi, Iniotagodi! Eliodi me jibakenaЙЎМ¶a ЗӨaboonaЙЎМ¶adi codaa jeloЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶atedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa me jibakenaЙЎМ¶a ЗӨaboonaЙЎМ¶adi me jiticodaЙЎМ¶atedice niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, codaa me jibakenaЙЎМ¶a ЗӨaboonaЙЎМ¶adi me jaoЙЎМ¶ate ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi.вҖҷ  
\v 23 Pida ejitiogi lodoe eledi oko, вҖҳAЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adowooЙЎМ¶oti. Adetecenitice, jaЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji anawii ane beyagi!вҖҷ 
\s1 Icoa itoa latopaco lipodaЙЎМ¶alatedi diimigi 
\r (Lucas 6.47-49) 
\p  
\v 24 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane wajipatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a odaa eyiwaЙЎМ¶adi, niЙЎМ¶ini liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa anida lixakedi odaa dabiteЙЎМ¶eteloco liЙЎМ¶eladi ditibigimedi wetiЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 25 NaЙЎМ¶a dinikatini ebici nelegi, odaa neЙЎМ¶enagi abooЙЎМ¶o-ninyoЙЎМ¶odi, codaa niwocotaЙЎМ¶a ane yoniciwadi jiЙЎМ¶icota niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi, pida aЙЎМ¶enitini. LeeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa dabiteЙЎМ¶etini liЙЎМ¶eladi ditibigimedi wetiЙЎМ¶a, anepeЙЎМ¶ele me diimigi lipodaЙЎМ¶aladi.  
\v 26 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane wajipatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a pida aЙЎМ¶eyiwaЙЎМ¶adi, baЙЎМ¶a liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane diЙЎМ¶ica lixakedi ane dabiteЙЎМ¶etini liЙЎМ¶eladi midi dotiwadi.  
\v 27 NaЙЎМ¶a dinikatini ebici nelegi, odaa neЙЎМ¶enagi abooЙЎМ¶o-ninyoЙЎМ¶odi, codaa niwocotaЙЎМ¶a ane yoniciwadi jiЙЎМ¶icota niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi, odaa ja dojitini, codaa aЙЎМ¶ica ane yeyaЙЎМ¶atice.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus ibake naЙЎМ¶atetigi me dotaЙЎМ¶a 
\p  
\v 28 NaЙЎМ¶a nigotedini Jesus me dotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ica lapo-nelegi joЙЎМ¶oyopo leeЙЎМ¶odi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 29 LeeЙЎМ¶odi adiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a liciagi niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, pida Jesus baЙЎМ¶a ibake epaa naЙЎМ¶atetigi me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a. 
\c 8  
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa dawace-lolaadi 
\r (Marcos 1.40-45; Lucas 5.12-16) 
\p  
\v 1 NaЙЎМ¶a daxoditedini Jesus me icoЙЎМ¶otedibigimece ica lojotaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa ica noiigi-nelegi joЙЎМ¶odiotece.  
\v 2 Odaa ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa dawace-lolaadi jiЙЎМ¶icotalo, odaa ja yamaЙЎМ¶atedi lokotidi lodoe Jesus me iweniЙЎМ¶ide, meetalo, вҖңIniotagodi, jowooЙЎМ¶odi mida ЙЎМ¶adoniciwaЙЎМ¶a madicilatiti, nigemaani.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 3 Odaa Jesus ja ixoketedice libaaЙЎМ¶adi, naЙЎМ¶a ipeketedeloco niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eeteta, вҖңEe jemaa me ЙЎМ¶adicili niЙЎМ¶ina natigide!вҖқ Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi niЙЎМ¶ijo dawace-lolaadi ja icГӯ.  
\v 4 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eete, вҖңDigawini, jiniЙЎМ¶ica aneloЙЎМ¶otita niЙЎМ¶ida anejigotaЙЎМ¶awa. Pida emii, adinikeenita sacerdoti naЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adicili. Codaa aboonitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶aboonigi ane liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi MoisГ©s, awiitibige me ikeenitiogi iditawece oko naЙЎМ¶a akaami ele. Odaa yakadi mopiliticogi miditaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adoiigiwepodi.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica liotagi nigoloneegi romaanotedi 
\r (Lucas 7.1-10) 
\p  
\v 5 Jesus igo nigotaЙЎМ¶a Cafarnaum. NaЙЎМ¶a dakatediwece nigotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ica goloneegi ane iiЙЎМ¶e onaniteci taalia iodaЙЎМ¶awadi, igo midoataЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja dipokotalo me yaxawa.  
\v 6 Odaa meetalo Jesus, вҖңIniotagodi, ini iotagi lioneeЙЎМ¶a digoida iЙЎМ¶eladi eliodi me deelotika. Ayakadi oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a me ditineЙЎМ¶e, eliodi me dawikode.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 7 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңEjigo jicilatidi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 8 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo goloneegi meetalo, вҖңAleeditibige deЙЎМ¶emii akaatiwece iЙЎМ¶eladi, Iniotagodi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa makaami ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi, caticedi ee. Pida onexaaЙЎМ¶awii ЙЎМ¶agegi me icГӯ, odaa inioneeЙЎМ¶a ja icГӯ.  
\v 9 IgaataЙЎМ¶a inoa eletidi iodaЙЎМ¶awadi ane leegitibigimece naЙЎМ¶atetigi ane etidiiЙЎМ¶e. Pida ee aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ida inaЙЎМ¶atetigi maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jiiЙЎМ¶e onaniteci taalia iodaЙЎМ¶awadi. Jakadi mejita okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶idiwa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi, вҖҳEmii!вҖҷ Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo. Iniaa eledi nigejita, вҖҳAnagi!вҖҷ Odaa jeЙЎМ¶enagi. Codaa nigejita niЙЎМ¶ina iotagi, вҖҳAwii niЙЎМ¶ida ane jiiЙЎМ¶etaЙЎМ¶awa!вҖҷ Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eo. Odaa akaami ida ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atetigi me iiЙЎМ¶eni iotagi me ele, odaa ja icГӯ.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 10 NiЙЎМ¶ica Jesus naЙЎМ¶a wajipateta niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo goloneegi, odaa eliodi me yopo niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa. Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi anodiotece, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa eliodi meyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. AniЙЎМ¶ica jinadi oko oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a minataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odoiigi Israel ane nakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, digo midataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me nakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 11 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji eliodi eledi oko, ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi, icota me icoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigoi codaa me ЙЎМ¶ocidi, odaa nicooЙЎМ¶owepodi AbraГЈo, Isaque, JacГі miditaЙЎМ¶a nalokegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yoe digoida ditibigimedi, lalokegi loiigi.  
\v 12 Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aikatediobece eliodi oko loiigi judeutedi me dakatiobece miditaЙЎМ¶a lalokegi. Aikatedio me dakatiobece niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶a yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baЙЎМ¶a yokoletedicogi miditaЙЎМ¶a nexocaЙЎМ¶a anei me noenaЙЎМ¶ateloco, codaa moyacigice lowe leeЙЎМ¶odi me nawikodeeЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 13 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eeteta niЙЎМ¶ijo goloneegi, вҖңEmii opiliticogi ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi, ЙЎМ¶aotagi ja icГӯ leeЙЎМ¶odi manakatoni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yakadi me icilatidi.вҖқ Odaa aniaaЙЎМ¶ani naЙЎМ¶aca lakata Jesus neЙЎМ¶ee, odaa niЙЎМ¶ica liotagi niЙЎМ¶ijo goloneegi ja icГӯ. 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi eliodi eelotaginadi 
\r (Marcos 1.29-34; Lucas 4.38-41) 
\p  
\v 14 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igo liЙЎМ¶eladi Pedro. NaЙЎМ¶a dakatedio, ja naditedeloco loxiiЙЎМ¶ate Pedro miwotini, dapicoЙЎМ¶o-lolaadi.  
\v 15 Odaa ja ipeketedeloco libaaЙЎМ¶adi naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo, odaa ja icГӯ. NaЙЎМ¶a dabiditini, odaa ja doolaЙЎМ¶a yoe liweenigi Jesus. 
\p  
\v 16 NaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶ocidi, joЙЎМ¶onadeegitalo eliodi oko anodakatiogi niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, codaa me eelotaginadi. Odaa Jesus onexaaЙЎМ¶eetediogi mopitibeci niЙЎМ¶icoa niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, odaa ijoatawece noditedice miditaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idi oko. Odaa ja nicilatiditediniwace iditawece eelotaginadi.  
\v 17 JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee neЙЎМ¶eote micotece niЙЎМ¶ica aneeta IsaГӯas, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, neЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңYadeegi ЙЎМ¶odeelotagi, codaa noЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odabocaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus yajoi oko anoyemaa modiotece 
\r (Lucas 9.57-62) 
\p  
\v 18 NaЙЎМ¶a nadi Jesus ica noiigi-nelegi moyawiile, odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece me diЙЎМ¶etitacicoace daato niЙЎМ¶ica weiigi.  
\v 19 MaleedaЙЎМ¶a noditicoaci, odaa onijoteci niЙЎМ¶ijo ane diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s igo midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eetalo, вҖңNiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, ja idigo me jiotaЙЎМ¶adici okanicodaaЙЎМ¶icata ane aaticogi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 20 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eeteta, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶inoa eti inoa libecoli, codaa ilaaЙЎМ¶axodi inoa epaa libatoli. Pida Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, baadiЙЎМ¶ica yotokaЙЎМ¶adi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 21 Ica eledi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane diotibece Jesus jeЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңIniotagodi, jemaa me jiotaЙЎМ¶adici. Pida ecoЙЎМ¶otace jalita eiodi nige yeleo amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a inaligitini.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 22 Pida Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eeteta, вҖңAniwitici! IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko liciagi Г©meЙЎМ¶egi leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶oyemaa moniotici, odaa dioki epaa onaligitedini Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus yamaketedini ica niwocotaЙЎМ¶a 
\r (Marcos 4.35-41; Lucas 8.22-25) 
\p  
\v 23 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus ja waxoditedinigi ajo niwatece ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi.  
\v 24 CodaaЙЎМ¶ida naЙЎМ¶a enagi ica niwocotaЙЎМ¶a aneo me itedibige ebekadi nelecoli. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa ebekadi ja domaЙЎМ¶a oyapoЙЎМ¶oditi niwatece. Pida idiaa Jesus diote.  
\v 25 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶odipegitalo, oyojietelogo, moditalo, вҖңЗӨoniotagodi, ЙЎМ¶odaxawaneЙЎМ¶egi! Ade jaaЙЎМ¶a!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 26 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңIgaamee ina madoiitiwaji? Amewi manakatonitetiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ NaЙЎМ¶a dabiditedini, odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶e niocodi inaa ebekadi me notokotiniwace. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niocodi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa ebekadi ja notokotiniwace.  
\v 27 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece eliodi moyopo, odaa ja dinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e modi, вҖңAmiidoa icoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa? Aneote niocodi idiaa ebekadi moyiwaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ina ane liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi!вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi itoataale ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anodakatiogi niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a 
\r (Marcos 5.1-20; Lucas 8.26-39) 
\p  
\v 28 Jesus jiЙЎМ¶icotedicogi daato niweiigi GalilГ©ia, nipodigi aca Gadara. Odaa joЙЎМ¶odakapetege icoa itoataale ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane dakatiogi niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, ja niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi midiwa lawimaЙЎМ¶ajetedi-wetiadi, ane onaligite judeutedi nГ©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaa oicoЙЎМ¶otiwece niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi. NiЙЎМ¶idiwa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi loidenaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me doide, aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me dioteci niЙЎМ¶ijo naigi.  
\v 29 NoЙЎМ¶onaditege Jesus, odaa ja napaawaЙЎМ¶a, modi, вҖңIgaamee managi ЙЎМ¶odigiwoceЙЎМ¶egi, anakaami Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji? Domige naЙЎМ¶anagi me ЙЎМ¶odiloikatiteЙЎМ¶egi maleediЙЎМ¶icota noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 30 Onidiwa icoa nigidagiwadi ane noxicoЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶a aona leegitalo.  
\v 31 Odaa niЙЎМ¶icoa niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anodakatiogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa itoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi moditalo Jesus, вҖңNige ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶eneЙЎМ¶egi me ЙЎМ¶ododiticogi niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, pida ЙЎМ¶odikaneЙЎМ¶egi me jakaЙЎМ¶atiogilo niЙЎМ¶idiwa nigidagiwadi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 32 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңEnice emiitiwaji!вҖқ Odaa niЙЎМ¶icoa niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ja noditicoaci midiwataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odakatiogilo niЙЎМ¶ijoa nigidagiwadi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa nigidagiwadi ja daleditedigi, odaa jeЙЎМ¶enitinece ica lilokaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa ja daxaboketiniwace, joЙЎМ¶oceЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a miditaЙЎМ¶a weiigi. 
\p  
\v 33 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anodoweditelogo niЙЎМ¶ijoa nigidagiwadi ja daleditibige odeleticogi nigotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyatemati niЙЎМ¶ica ane ninyaagi niЙЎМ¶ijoa nigidagiwadi, codaa anee niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi naЙЎМ¶a noditicoaci niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anodakatiogi.  
\v 34 Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi naЙЎМ¶ajo nigotaЙЎМ¶a jeЙЎМ¶enagitibeci odakapetege Jesus. NoЙЎМ¶onadi Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶odipokotalo me noditedicogi niiЙЎМ¶o. 
\c 9  
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica alejaado ane daЙЎМ¶adiaa ditineЙЎМ¶e 
\r (Marcos 2.1-12; Lucas 5.17-26) 
\p  
\v 1 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a waxoditedinigi niwatece migo daato weiigi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶icotedicogi manitaЙЎМ¶a epaa nigotaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 2 Odaa icoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi joЙЎМ¶oyadeegitalo ica alejaado ane daЙЎМ¶adiaa ditineЙЎМ¶e ane iwoteloco aca liЙЎМ¶elate. NaЙЎМ¶a nadi Jesus moyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yakadi me icilatidi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eeteta niЙЎМ¶ijo alejaado, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶adoii, ionigi! Ja inapitaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 3 Odaa icoa onateciЙЎМ¶idiwa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s dinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etiwage modi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa beyagi me dotaЙЎМ¶atedibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a iniokiniwateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yakadi me ligegi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 4 Jesus yowooЙЎМ¶oditediwe lowoogo, odaa meetediogi, вҖңIgaameetiwaji mowoo ane beyagi?  
\v 5 Amiida ica ane dakake mejatigi igegita idi alejaado? Domige eneЙЎМ¶egi dakake deЙЎМ¶ejita, вҖҳJa ЙЎМ¶adapitaЙЎМ¶atitece ijoatawece ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶ecoвҖҷ, oЙЎМ¶oa domige ina deЙЎМ¶ejita, вҖҳAdabititini, odaa awaligi!вҖҷ?  
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶ida me Ee jikeetaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji me Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, ida yoniciwaЙЎМ¶a me inapitaЙЎМ¶adi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco oko.вҖқ Odaa meete niЙЎМ¶ijo alejaado, вҖңAdabititini, odaa anibaatine naЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶elate, odaa emii digoida ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 7 NiЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa naЙЎМ¶a dabiditini, odaa joЙЎМ¶opiticogi liЙЎМ¶eladi.  
\v 8 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi noЙЎМ¶onadi niЙЎМ¶ijo niciagi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odoЙЎМ¶etetalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, leeЙЎМ¶odi me yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko loniciwaЙЎМ¶a monicilatiditiniwace eelotaginadi. 
\s1 Jesus enidite Mateus me diotece 
\r (Marcos 2.13-17; Lucas 5.27-32) 
\p  
\v 9 Jesus ja noditedicogi niЙЎМ¶ica aneite, eЙЎМ¶idaa diitedicogi mewaligi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶icote ica diimicawaanigi balaacogo aneitice me nicoti ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Mateus. Mateus inaaЙЎМ¶ina ane dibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi. Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eeteta, вҖңAnagi, aniwitici!вҖқ Odaa Mateus ja dabiditini, ja diotece.  
\v 10 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igo liЙЎМ¶eladi Mateus, odaa ja nicotedi maditaЙЎМ¶a aca nameeja. NaЙЎМ¶a niodaЙЎМ¶a menoale, jiЙЎМ¶icotiobece eliodi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo eliodi eledi oko, judeutedi anoyakadi me abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. Odaa ja nicotiniwace miniwataЙЎМ¶a Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niodaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 11 Icoa fariseutedi onadi Jesus me ligiiwepodi niЙЎМ¶idi oko anoyakadi me abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶onigetiniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus, moditiogi, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶aniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi me ligiiwepodi idiwa anodibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi, idiaaЙЎМ¶idi idi eledi oko aninoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco?вҖқ \fig |src="cn01694B.tif" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Mateus 9.10-11" \fig* 
\p  
\v 12 Jesus wajipatediogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi monigetiniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina oko icileЙЎМ¶egi ayopotibige dotowegi, pida inokina niЙЎМ¶ina ane deelotika baЙЎМ¶a yopotibige dotowegi.  
\v 13 Oleetibige mowooЙЎМ¶oti ane diitigi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, anee, вҖҳAjemaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko monajigotiwa eijedi monigodi leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Pida baЙЎМ¶a jemaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko mowo aneletema eledi oko.вҖҷ IgaataЙЎМ¶a ajanagi jiniditiogi niЙЎМ¶ina anoyakadi meletibigiwaji. Pida janagi jiniditiogi niЙЎМ¶inoa abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a modopitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, igaataЙЎМ¶a oyopotibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me napitaЙЎМ¶aditediniwace micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane deelotika odaa yopotibige dotowegi me icilatidi.вҖқ 
\s1 Ica moikanawaanigi me niodaЙЎМ¶a moikee magecaЙЎМ¶alodipi leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco 
\r (Marcos 2.18-22; Lucas 5.33-39) 
\p  
\v 14 Icoa nioЙЎМ¶ododi JoГЈo Batista igotibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo, вҖңOko, idiaaЙЎМ¶idiwa fariseutedi baЙЎМ¶a jikanakawaanigi me jiniodaЙЎМ¶a, jikeenaЙЎМ¶a moko agecaЙЎМ¶alodipi leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶obeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Igaamee idi ЙЎМ¶anioЙЎМ¶ododipi me doЙЎМ¶oikanawaanigi me niodaЙЎМ¶a?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 15 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a igidi, meetediogi, вҖңDomige agecaЙЎМ¶alodipi ina nodenigipi migotibeci lalokegi nadoneЙЎМ¶egi ina mini miditaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo ane wado? AЙЎМ¶agecaЙЎМ¶alodipi! Pida icota noko monoЙЎМ¶atice niЙЎМ¶ijo ane wado miditaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ica noko jaЙЎМ¶agecaЙЎМ¶alodipi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oikanawaanigi me niodaЙЎМ¶a. 
\p  
\v 16 AЙЎМ¶ica ane napadeta nowoodaЙЎМ¶agi oxiiЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina lapadenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶adi gela anepaЙЎМ¶alee yexogo, igaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idi lapadijegi gela nige dinixigi, odaa ja daa niЙЎМ¶idi nowoodaЙЎМ¶agi oxiiЙЎМ¶odi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ica laakajegi ja daЙЎМ¶axa me nelegi.  
\v 17 Codaa aЙЎМ¶ica ane yadotinigi viinyo gela naЙЎМ¶ana laЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi ewacogo baanaЙЎМ¶a opake. Nigeo iatinigi viinyo gela, odaa naЙЎМ¶ada laЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi opake datope, odaa viinyo jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a aniadi. Pida oyatinigi viinyo naЙЎМ¶aca laЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi gela, odaa naЙЎМ¶ada laЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi abeyagi, codaa me viinyo eledi aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶aniadi.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi aca iwaalo acaaЙЎМ¶aca nigaanawaana 
\r (Marcos 5.21-43; Lucas 8.40-56) 
\p  
\v 18 Jesus eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me notaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etediniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibeci JoГЈo, niЙЎМ¶icotalo ica lacilo judeutedi, odaa ja yamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi lodoe Jesus, meetalo, вҖңIona ja leedi me yeleo. Anagi ipekeniteloco ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶atedi amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a icГӯ.вҖқ  
\v 19 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igo lixigaЙЎМ¶awa, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece eledi igotibeci odiotece. 
\p  
\v 20 EЙЎМ¶idaa diiticogi migotibeci, odaa aca iwaalo ja nowidila Jesus. JoneЙЎМ¶eote dooze nicaaЙЎМ¶ape mawodina. NaЙЎМ¶a iwidatece Jesus, odaa dibatece nijayogo liniogo.  
\v 21 NaЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo eo niЙЎМ¶ida anee, leeЙЎМ¶odi mee me dowooko, вҖңOnexaa jiba-aatece nijayogo liniogo, odaa ja idici.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 22 NaЙЎМ¶a nilokotedijo Jesus, odaa ja nadi naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo. Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eete, вҖңIona, jinaЙЎМ¶adoii! Ja ЙЎМ¶adicili, leeЙЎМ¶odi me iwaЙЎМ¶ati AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yakadi me ЙЎМ¶adicilatiti.вҖқ NaЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo naЙЎМ¶a dibateloco nijayogo Jesus, odaa ja icГӯ. 
\p  
\v 23 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igo liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo judeutedi. NiЙЎМ¶icotedio, odaa ja naditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyatetigi natenaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi lajo Г©meЙЎМ¶egi monaligitini, idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ica oko ane nacaagaЙЎМ¶ateloco.  
\v 24 Odaa meetediogi, вҖңEmii anotiticoacetiwaji! NaЙЎМ¶adi nigaanawaana ayeleo, pida diote.вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oilajitedibece.  
\v 25 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a noditicoaci niЙЎМ¶ijo oko. Odaa Jesus ja dakatediwece ane liotaЙЎМ¶adi naЙЎМ¶ajo nigaanawaana ane yeleo. NaЙЎМ¶a dibatedigi libaaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa ja nicooЙЎМ¶etedi.  
\v 26 Odaa noЙЎМ¶odibodiceta niЙЎМ¶ida Jesus aneote jiЙЎМ¶ilaagiteloco iditawece nipodigi. 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi itoataale etoinadi 
\p  
\v 27 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a noditedice niЙЎМ¶ijo aneite. Odaa eЙЎМ¶idaa diitedigi migo, icoa itoataale etoinadi joЙЎМ¶oigaalatece, codaa napaawaЙЎМ¶ateloco, moditalo, вҖңAkaami anida anenitege licoЙЎМ¶egi inionigi-eliodi Davi, ЙЎМ¶odiwikodeneЙЎМ¶egi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 28 NaЙЎМ¶a icotedicogi Jesus ica diimigi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa etoinadi joЙЎМ¶oigaalatiwece. NaЙЎМ¶a dakatiobece, odaa joЙЎМ¶ototalo. Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңDomige iwaЙЎМ¶atakani ica me jakadi me ЙЎМ¶adicilatititiwaji?вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңEjiwaЙЎМ¶atakanaЙЎМ¶a, ЗӨoniotagodi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 29 Odaa Jesus ja dibatedeloco ligecooЙЎМ¶eli, odaa meetediogi, вҖңEnice niЙЎМ¶ina natigide ja ЙЎМ¶adicilitiwaji, leeЙЎМ¶odi me iwaЙЎМ¶atakani!вҖқ  
\v 30 Odaa ja yatetibigiwaji, jeЙЎМ¶ele ligecooЙЎМ¶eli. Odaa Jesus ja najoitediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a ica anatematiita niЙЎМ¶ida ane ejigotaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji!вҖқ  
\v 31 Pida noЙЎМ¶opitibeci, joЙЎМ¶oyatematitiogi iditawece niЙЎМ¶idi oko niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi niЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi me Jesus nicilatiditediniwace. 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica ewaloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶a 
\p  
\v 32 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶opitibeci niЙЎМ¶ijoa itoataale ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, odaa ica eledi oko joЙЎМ¶onadeegitalo Jesus ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane dakatiogi niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi aneo me ewaloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 33 NeЙЎМ¶eote Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi me noditice mijotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, odaa ja dotaЙЎМ¶a. Ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi eliodi moyopo, odaa modi, вҖңAЙЎМ¶ica me jinataЙЎМ¶a digoina ЙЎМ¶oniiЙЎМ¶o Israel ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane yakadi meo ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi liciagi niЙЎМ¶ida aneote niЙЎМ¶idoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 34 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi modi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶ijaa yajigotalo loniciwaЙЎМ¶a me iticoitedice niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus iwikodetediogi ica noiigi 
\p  
\v 35 Odaa Jesus igotetece idiwatawece nigotadi codaa me nigotadawaanaЙЎМ¶a, diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a midiwa niiakanaЙЎМ¶axiidi, yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece nibodicetedi anele, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me doletedibige me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko, codaa icilatidi inoatawece ane latopaco neelotika, codaa me niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane diЙЎМ¶ica loniciwaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 36 NaЙЎМ¶a nadi Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi, odaa ja iwikodetediogi, leeЙЎМ¶odi me nawikodeeЙЎМ¶a, aЙЎМ¶ica ane yaxawatiogi, iciaceeketetege niЙЎМ¶inoa waxacocoli ane diЙЎМ¶ica nowienoЙЎМ¶odi.  
\v 37 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idi oko liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina nixoЙЎМ¶otagi nelegi baanaЙЎМ¶a leeditibige monopilaЙЎМ¶aditio. Pida ane nibaaЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶eliodi.  
\v 38 Odaa ipokitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me niwakatee eletidi nibakecajoli moyaxawa eledi oko monakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodipokota niЙЎМ¶ini ane nebi nixoЙЎМ¶otagi nelegi me niwakatee eletidi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi monopilaЙЎМ¶aditedio lawodigijedi.вҖқ 
\c 10  
\s1 Icoa dooze liiЙЎМ¶exedi ЗӨoniotagodi 
\r (Marcos 3.13-19; Lucas 6.12-16) 
\p  
\v 1 Jesus eniditediogi dooze ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi modiotibece. Odaa ja yajigotediogi loniciwaЙЎМ¶a moiticoitedice niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anodakatiogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko, codaa moicilatidi okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ane latopagi neelotagi codaa me nibeyacaЙЎМ¶ajegi.  
\v 2-4 Digawini ane liboonaЙЎМ¶atedi niЙЎМ¶ijo dooze anodiotibece Jesus: odoejegi SimГЈo, aneledi oyatigi me Pedro, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo nioxoa ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi AndrГ©; Tiago ijaa JoГЈo dinioxomigipi ane lionigipi Zebedeu; Filipe, Bartolomeu, TomГ© ijaa Mateus anijo me dibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi; Tiago lionigi Alfeu, Tadeu, ijaa eledi SimГЈo ane domaЙЎМ¶a lowoogo me iticoiticoace romaanotedi me noditicoaci nipodaЙЎМ¶a judeutedi; ijaa Judas Iscariotes aneyaa Jesus mijotaЙЎМ¶a neloЙЎМ¶ododipi. 
\s1 Jesus iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijoa dooze liiЙЎМ¶exedi mowo ica libakedi 
\r (Marcos 6.7-13; Lucas 9.1-6) 
\p  
\v 5 Jesus iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijoa dooze ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, odaa ja najoitediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңJineЙЎМ¶emiitiwaji liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi, codaa jinaЙЎМ¶akaatiwece nigotadi samaritaanotedi.  
\v 6 Pida oleetibige oko miditaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odoiigi Israel, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane aniatagigipi, ane liciagi niЙЎМ¶inoa waxacocoli aneyamaЙЎМ¶aticoace, odaa jaЙЎМ¶aniadi.  
\v 7 Emiitiwaji atematikani, eni, вҖҳNiЙЎМ¶ina natigide AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko.вҖҷ  
\v 8 Icilatititiwaji eelotaginadi, codaa awii Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a me newiЙЎМ¶atace. Codaa awii niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane dawace-loolatedi me nicilaЙЎМ¶a. Iticoitedice niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anodakatiogi oko. Inoatawece niЙЎМ¶inoa anabaategetiwaji aЙЎМ¶ica loojedi, odaa jinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a abanoonaЙЎМ¶ani mawii niЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶abakeditiwaji.  
\v 9 Codaa jinaЙЎМ¶awii adeegi dinyeelo catinedi ЙЎМ¶aninyeelaЙЎМ¶axi.  
\v 10 Codaa jinaЙЎМ¶adeegi ЙЎМ¶aniboco maniwiaje, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anigetaЙЎМ¶ani eledi ЙЎМ¶anoecaЙЎМ¶axi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a eletidi ЙЎМ¶awelatedi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶agiilaЙЎМ¶adi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a ewi niЙЎМ¶ina modi, ane diba leeditibige me dibatege ane yopotibige me yewiЙЎМ¶a. 
\p  
\v 11 Nigakaatiwecetiwaji anigani nigotaЙЎМ¶a domige nigotakawaana, odaa oleetibige liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anodeemitetibige, odaa idiaaЙЎМ¶onitetiwaji nigepaa limedi manotiticogi naЙЎМ¶ani nigotaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 12 Nigakaatiwecetiwaji diimigi, odaa anicenitiniwace niЙЎМ¶ica oko niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi.  
\v 13 Nigele modibataЙЎМ¶agitiwaji niЙЎМ¶idi oko ane liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ica diimigi, odaa ipokitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ibinietediogi. Pida nige deЙЎМ¶ele modibataЙЎМ¶agi, odaa jiniЙЎМ¶ipokitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ibinietediogi.  
\v 14 Codaa nige deЙЎМ¶ele modibataЙЎМ¶agi anigini diimigi, domige anigani nigotaЙЎМ¶a, codaa nige doЙЎМ¶oyemaa mowajipatalo ЙЎМ¶adatematiko, odaa niganotiticogi niЙЎМ¶ini diimigi, domige naЙЎМ¶ani nigotaЙЎМ¶a, iticiЙЎМ¶i ЙЎМ¶awelatedi me ikeeni me daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica anenitege.  
\v 15 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶idi oko leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, odaa daЙЎМ¶axa me beyagi niЙЎМ¶ica anigotediogi niЙЎМ¶idi oko caticedi me liciagi anigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi Sodoma ajaa Gomorra niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lakataЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi. 
\s1 Icoa lawikodico niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus 
\r (Marcos 13.9-13; Lucas 21.12-17) 
\p  
\v 16 Digawinitiwaji! ЗӨadiiЙЎМ¶eni micoataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa waxacocoli memii liwigotigi oko ane liciagi diwilecoЙЎМ¶oni. Enice ecoЙЎМ¶otace owookoni nigepaa nige awii ane ЙЎМ¶abakedi. Nigawii, odaa abakeni ЙЎМ¶adacilo, me daЙЎМ¶a beyagi ЙЎМ¶adowoogo.  
\v 17 Anidakitiogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko. IgaataЙЎМ¶a etiЙЎМ¶adiwilotiwaji codaa etiЙЎМ¶adadeegiticogi midiwataЙЎМ¶a lacilodi moiwi anodigotaЙЎМ¶awa, codaa icota metiЙЎМ¶adalakenitibige catiwedi liiakanaЙЎМ¶axiidi judeutedi, oyatitaЙЎМ¶awa lalakenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atedi.  
\v 18 LeeЙЎМ¶odi maniwitici, odaa etiЙЎМ¶adadeegiticogitiwaji midiwataЙЎМ¶a lacilodi ane niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me midiwataЙЎМ¶a inionaЙЎМ¶a-eloodoli, odaa joЙЎМ¶oiwi anigotaЙЎМ¶awa, codaa odiiЙЎМ¶enatakataЙЎМ¶awa metiЙЎМ¶adiloikatiti. Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eniticitiwaji midiwataЙЎМ¶a lacilodi ane niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me miditaЙЎМ¶a ane daЙЎМ¶a judeutedi.  
\v 19 NigetiЙЎМ¶adadeegiticogi lodoe ЙЎМ¶oniwinoЙЎМ¶odi, jinaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adigecaЙЎМ¶aleЙЎМ¶eni ane alitigi ЙЎМ¶agegi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eote mowooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ica ane alitigi ЙЎМ¶agegi nigicota naЙЎМ¶aca lakata nige limedi motaЙЎМ¶ani.  
\v 20 IgaataЙЎМ¶a nige limedi motaЙЎМ¶anitiwaji, ЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶a aicoЙЎМ¶otedigi makaamitaЙЎМ¶a, pida icoЙЎМ¶otedigi mijotaЙЎМ¶a Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane ЗӨadiodi anini makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji. 
\p  
\v 21 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko icota moyajigo epaa nioxoadipi monigodi, codaa eniododipi oyajigo lionigipi, odaa nionigipi ja lakapetedi eliododipi, odaa joЙЎМ¶owo monigodi.  
\v 22 LeeЙЎМ¶odi maniwiticitiwaji, inatawece oko icota moyelataЙЎМ¶adomi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a ika me niotici, codaa me daЙЎМ¶a ika me idinakato, biЙЎМ¶ida lewiЙЎМ¶a ane diЙЎМ¶ica liniogo.  
\v 23 NigetiЙЎМ¶adiatenitibece anigani nigotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ialeticogi manitaЙЎМ¶a eledi nigotaЙЎМ¶a. EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi, midioka limedi mani eledi nigotaЙЎМ¶a anei makati mawii niЙЎМ¶ida ibakedi nigepaaЙЎМ¶icota me idopitijo, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi. 
\p  
\v 24 AЙЎМ¶ica niiЙЎМ¶axinigi ane naЙЎМ¶axateloco niiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi daЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi. Codaa aЙЎМ¶ica niotagi ane naЙЎМ¶axateloco niotagodi daЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi.  
\v 25 Enice niЙЎМ¶ina niiЙЎМ¶axinigi leeditibige me ninitibece niЙЎМ¶ina mododigo digo mijotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo niiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina niotagi leeditibige maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ninitibece niЙЎМ¶ina mododigo digo mijotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagodi. Nigoditalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa ane nebi diimigi me Belzebu (ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi SatanГЎs), odaa eledi owote liboonaЙЎМ¶atedi ane daЙЎМ¶axa me beyagi niЙЎМ¶idi loiigi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ane nebi diimigi. 
\s1 NiЙЎМ¶ica anepaЙЎМ¶a leeditibige me idoiiЙЎМ¶a 
\r (Lucas 12.2-7) 
\p  
\v 26 JinaЙЎМ¶adoiitiogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko. IgaataЙЎМ¶a inoatawece ane dinapoЙЎМ¶oditedini icota moyowiegi, codaa inoatawece anoyowiegitelogo, icota moyowooЙЎМ¶odi.  
\v 27 NiЙЎМ¶inoa anejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina me enoale, eloЙЎМ¶otitiogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko me noko. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina anajipaata ane dinaЙЎМ¶aditi, eloЙЎМ¶oti anei eliodi oko moyakadi mowajipata.  
\v 28 JinaЙЎМ¶adoiita niЙЎМ¶ina anoyakadi mowo anodigo ЙЎМ¶adolaadi, leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶ica loniciwaЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶oyeloadi ЙЎМ¶adiwigo. Pida adoiitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anepaЙЎМ¶a yakadi me yaaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶adewiЙЎМ¶a minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe.  
\v 29 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko adakake loojedi moyaa iniwataale ilaaЙЎМ¶axodawaanaЙЎМ¶a, loojedi onaniteci beexo. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina ilaaЙЎМ¶agi inoka enitinigi iiЙЎМ¶o, nige yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane ЗӨadiodi.  
\v 30 Codaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yowooЙЎМ¶odi ane liwokodi ЙЎМ¶adamodi aneitigi ЙЎМ¶adacilo.  
\v 31 Enice jinaЙЎМ¶adoii! IgaataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mida ЙЎМ¶aniwalГі caticedi niЙЎМ¶inoa ilaaЙЎМ¶axodi. 
\s1 Ica oko anida aneetege Cristo icaaЙЎМ¶ica ane daЙЎМ¶a onigecaЙЎМ¶atema 
\r (Lucas 12.8-9) 
\p  
\v 32 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane dineloЙЎМ¶odi lodoe niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko mida aneetigi, odaa Ee aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jeloЙЎМ¶oditalo Eiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi mida anejitege.  
\v 33 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina anee me diЙЎМ¶ica aneetigi lodoe niЙЎМ¶ina oko, odaa Ee eledi eji me diЙЎМ¶ica anejitege lodoe Eiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi. 
\s1 Oko dawalacetiwage leeЙЎМ¶odi Jesus 
\r (Lucas 12.51-53; 14.26-27) 
\p  
\v 34 JinaЙЎМ¶aleetibige daЙЎМ¶a janagi digoina iiЙЎМ¶o daЙЎМ¶a jao me ilaЙЎМ¶atiwage inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina oko. Ajanagi daЙЎМ¶a jao me ilaЙЎМ¶atiwage, pida janagi micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane nadeegi lodaajo, odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko idiokiditiwage, pida dawalacetiwage.  
\v 35 LeeЙЎМ¶odi janagi me jao niЙЎМ¶ina nionigi me lakapetegi eliodi, niona lakapete eliodo, codaa me niiЙЎМ¶ate lakapete loxiiЙЎМ¶ate.  
\v 36 Odaa dinaxakawepodi niЙЎМ¶idi oko, idaaЙЎМ¶ida me domaЙЎМ¶a dinoiigiwepodi. 
\s1 Leeditibige me jemaanaЙЎМ¶a Jesus caticedi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko 
\p  
\v 37 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane yemaa eliodi codaa me eliodo caticedi me idemaa, niЙЎМ¶ini oko ayakadi diЙЎМ¶ida aneetigi, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane yemaa lionigi codaa me liona caticedi me idemaa, niЙЎМ¶ini ayakadi diЙЎМ¶ica aneetigi.  
\v 38 Inoka yakadi mida aneetigi niЙЎМ¶ina baanaЙЎМ¶a igo me dawikode nigepaa yeleo leeЙЎМ¶odi me niotibici.  
\v 39 NiЙЎМ¶ina aninoka doletibige me dowediteloco epaa lewiЙЎМ¶a, codaa epaa dinowedi adinigaanyetece lewiЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane domaЙЎМ¶a yajigote. NiЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atema epaa lakataЙЎМ¶a, pida ja igo me yeleotomi, joaniЙЎМ¶iniaa dinigaanyetece lewiЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yajigo. 
\s1 Ica laЙЎМ¶ajegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yajigo 
\r (Marcos 9.41) 
\p  
\v 40 NiЙЎМ¶ina anele me dibataЙЎМ¶agitiwaji, odaa aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ele me dibatigi. NiЙЎМ¶ina anele me dibatigi, odaa ele me dibatege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane idimonya.  
\v 41 NiЙЎМ¶ina anele me dibatege niЙЎМ¶ina ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji leeЙЎМ¶odi ane libakegitema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ini oko dibatege icaaЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ica laЙЎМ¶ajegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ina ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane dibatege niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ini oko dibatege icaaЙЎМ¶ica naЙЎМ¶ajegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ina ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji.  
\v 42 Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane yacipeЙЎМ¶eta ninyoЙЎМ¶odi ane diwete anigepidiЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ina anoniotici ane daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, pida leeЙЎМ¶odi me iiЙЎМ¶exegi, ajawienatakanaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ini oko me dinigaanyetece naЙЎМ¶ajegi anele ane yajigote AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ 
\c 11  
\s1 Jesus iniaa JoГЈo Batista 
\p  
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a ika me niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo dooze anodiotibece, odaa ja noditedice, jiЙЎМ¶igo diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a codaa me yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece ЙЎМ¶obodicetedi anele midiwataЙЎМ¶a nigotadi niЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi. 
\s1 Icoa liiЙЎМ¶exedi JoГЈo Batista igotibeci oige Jesus 
\r (Lucas 7.18-35) 
\p  
\v 2 JoГЈo Batista idei niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi. NaЙЎМ¶a dibodicetibige niЙЎМ¶icoa ane loenataka Cristo, odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶e itoataale niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibeci moige Jesus.  
\v 3 NoЙЎМ¶ototalo Jesus, moditalo, вҖңManigakamaЙЎМ¶akaami ica anenagi ЙЎМ¶odewikatidi, oЙЎМ¶oa domigalee jaliiЙЎМ¶atege eledi?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 4 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a igidi, meetediogi, вҖңOpilitijotiwaji, eloЙЎМ¶otita JoГЈo anajipaata, codaa eloЙЎМ¶otita yoenataka baanaЙЎМ¶a anati.  
\v 5 NaЙЎМ¶a yatetacibigiwaji ЙЎМ¶oladi, alejaadotedi jeЙЎМ¶ewaligi, dawace-loolatedi ja nicilaЙЎМ¶a, aticilonadi ja najipaaЙЎМ¶a, Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ja newiЙЎМ¶atace, codaa nibodicetedi anele ane icoЙЎМ¶otedibigimece miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji joЙЎМ¶oyeloЙЎМ¶oditiogi madewetedi.  
\v 6 Nige daЙЎМ¶a ikani madinakatoni, odaa niЙЎМ¶ida makaami jaЙЎМ¶aniniitibecitiwaji.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 7 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a noditicoaci niЙЎМ¶ijoa liiЙЎМ¶exedi JoГЈo, odaa Jesus ja yalaЙЎМ¶ate JoГЈo, meetediogi niЙЎМ¶ica oko, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶emiitiwaji akapetege JoГЈo midi nipodigi ane yadilo ane diЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi, amiini ica anemii awinitiwaji? EjideЙЎМ¶emiitiwaji mawini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa aЙЎМ¶amaleЙЎМ¶egi ane diЙЎМ¶ica baЙЎМ¶a lowoogo, micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina naanyogo ane igiketibece niocodi.  
\v 8 Enice, amiini ica anemii awinitiwaji? EjideЙЎМ¶emiitiwaji mawini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa liico, ane dinixotinigilo nowoodi libinienaЙЎМ¶a ane dakake loojedi. NiЙЎМ¶ina oko anodinixotinigilo nowoodi libinienaЙЎМ¶a ane dakake loojedi odiЙЎМ¶eladetigilo diimaЙЎМ¶a nelecoli, liЙЎМ¶eladi ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 9 Enice, amiini ica anemii awinitiwaji? Ejime emii mawinitiwaji anigepidiЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, niЙЎМ¶ijo anemii awinitiwaji daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi caticedi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 10 IgaataЙЎМ¶a lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jotigide naЙЎМ¶akaa yalaЙЎМ¶ata JoГЈo, mee, вҖҳDigawini! Ida iiЙЎМ¶exegi, ane datematika maleediЙЎМ¶icatibige diЙЎМ¶icoo. YoetaЙЎМ¶adomi ЙЎМ¶anaigi.вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 11 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. JoГЈo Batista daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi, caticedi inatawece oko aninaa codaa natigide. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶ena oko ane diЙЎМ¶ica naЙЎМ¶atetigi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ini oko daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi caticedi JoГЈo.  
\v 12 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa nokododi me yatematitedibece JoГЈo latematiko, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina noko, niЙЎМ¶ina oko nawikodeeЙЎМ¶a, leeЙЎМ¶odi moikatece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko loidenaЙЎМ¶a odoletibige modinigaanyetece domoЙЎМ¶owotibige me daЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶oika AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali.  
\v 13 Pida maleediЙЎМ¶icatibige me yatemati JoГЈo latematigo, ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, oyalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me doletedibige me iiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶enali.  
\v 14 Odaa nigemaanitiwaji me iwaЙЎМ¶ati anoyatemati, JoГЈo jiЙЎМ¶iniaaЙЎМ¶ini niЙЎМ¶ijo Elias ane leeditibige me dopitijo.  
\v 15 Nigemaani majipaatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a, enice atacoli! 
\p  
\v 16 AmigetiЙЎМ¶ini ica ane jiciaceeketege niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi ane newiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi? Liciagi nigaanigipawaanigi ane nicotiniwace dinalokowepodi. Odaa ini lapo ane dapaaweta eledi, meeta,  
\v 17 вҖҳJa jatenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji nateneЙЎМ¶egi nadoneЙЎМ¶egi jatiiЙЎМ¶a natena, pida aЙЎМ¶emaanitiwaji manibaile. Codaa ja jatenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji natenaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi lajo monaligitini Г©meЙЎМ¶egi, pida aЙЎМ¶emaanitiwaji manoeni oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a akaami agecaЙЎМ¶alodipi.вҖҷ  
\v 18 Jiciaceeketege nigaanigipawaanigi leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nimonya JoГЈo, odaa aЙЎМ¶igo nalokeco daЙЎМ¶a yeligo niweenigi anele, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a wacipeta viinyo. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi joЙЎМ¶odi, вҖҳNiЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa dakatiogi niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi.вҖҷ  
\v 19 Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a idimonya Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, odaa baЙЎМ¶a jiitiogi nalokeco, codaa me jeligo niweenigi anele, jacipe viinyo. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi modi, вҖҳDigawini! NiЙЎМ¶iniwa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa olade, codaa me acipeЙЎМ¶egi, lokaaЙЎМ¶edi niЙЎМ¶ina anodibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi, codaa me niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶axa me abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.вҖҷ Pida oko anida lixakedi ane icoЙЎМ¶otibigimece miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ina oko idioka limedi meo ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icota me iloikatidi noiigi ane doЙЎМ¶oika mowo ane beyagi 
\r (Lucas 10.13-15) 
\p  
\v 20 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etediniwace ЙЎМ¶onitiadi inoa lotaЙЎМ¶atediogi niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotadi anei meote owidi ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko aЙЎМ¶odinilaatece libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco.  
\v 21 Meetediogi Jesus, вҖңNagoodi akaamitiwaji, niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Corazim! Codaa nagoodi akaamitiwaji, niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Betsaida! IgaataЙЎМ¶a ijoa jaote owidi ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi anoikee loniciwaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji catiwedi ЙЎМ¶anigotaditiwaji, pida idokee aЙЎМ¶ikanitiwaji mawii ane beyagi ane daЙЎМ¶a yemaateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida daЙЎМ¶a jaote niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide midiwa nigotadi Tiro aniaa Sidom, aneitice niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi ane daЙЎМ¶axa me abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, toЙЎМ¶oika mowo ane beyagi, codaa toЙЎМ¶odinixotinigi jaacogo, codaa toЙЎМ¶oyati lojienigi lacilodi moikee me agecaЙЎМ¶alodipi leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco anowote.  
\v 22 Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, niЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, odaa daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶adiloikatititetiwaji caticedi niЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotadi Tiro aniaa Sidom.  
\v 23 Akaami, niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Cafarnaum. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji adoЙЎМ¶etetedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adadeegitedibigimece ditibigimedi aneite. Pida diiЙЎМ¶enatakatedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji metiЙЎМ¶adokolenitiogi minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe. IgaataЙЎМ¶a jeЙЎМ¶eliodi me jaote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi anoikee loniciwaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida idokee aЙЎМ¶ikanitiwaji mawii ane beyagi ane daЙЎМ¶a yemaateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. DaЙЎМ¶a jaote niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide catiwedi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Sodoma, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi toЙЎМ¶oika mowo ane beyagi, codaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji agotaЙЎМ¶a yaaЙЎМ¶adi naЙЎМ¶ajo nigotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa taЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ani codaa ina noko.  
\v 24 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, niЙЎМ¶ica noko nige iloikatidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji oko leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, odaa daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶adiloikatititetiwaji caticedi niЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Sodoma.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus noЙЎМ¶a ligecaЙЎМ¶aloЙЎМ¶o laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane diitalo 
\r (Lucas 10.21-22) 
\p  
\v 25 NaЙЎМ¶ajo lakata, Jesus meete AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, вҖңEiodi, ane Niotagodi ditibigimedi, codaa me iiЙЎМ¶o. IniotagodetaЙЎМ¶awa leeЙЎМ¶odi maЙЎМ¶atiti anodaa diitigilo yotaЙЎМ¶atiogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anodiletibige diЙЎМ¶inoa lixaketedi codaa doЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi inoatawece. Pida biЙЎМ¶ikeenitiogi ane diitigilo yotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane deЙЎМ¶ewi ina ica lixakedi, micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina nigaanigawaanigi analeedaЙЎМ¶a diwaxinaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 26 JoЙЎМ¶etetaЙЎМ¶awa Eiodi, leeЙЎМ¶odi jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ida niЙЎМ¶ica anemaani mawii.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 27 Jesus meetediogi, вҖңEiodi ja yajigote ibaaЙЎМ¶adi inoatawece. AЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, iniokiniwateda Eiodi me idowooЙЎМ¶odi. Codaa aЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi Eiodi, emokee ane Ee Lionigi, inaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane jao monadi Eiodi. 
\p  
\v 28 Anagi meetaЙЎМ¶a akaamitawecetiwaji baanaЙЎМ¶a anigaaxetema ЙЎМ¶adewiЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi me micataЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶oyaЙЎМ¶atitiwaji noyaЙЎМ¶aka ane iwaaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa jao manipenitema ЙЎМ¶adawikodico.  
\v 29 MicataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ewalaile me yoyaЙЎМ¶adi lotoinaЙЎМ¶atijegi aneo me yakadi me ilakidetice niotagodi me diba, odaa idaaЙЎМ¶eni oleetibige madadiwaЙЎМ¶atitiwaji codaa adiniiЙЎМ¶axinitece iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco, igaataЙЎМ¶a Ee okaaЙЎМ¶egi codaa aЙЎМ¶ee anaЙЎМ¶axakeneЙЎМ¶egi, odaa jaЙЎМ¶akatitiwaji ЙЎМ¶anipenaЙЎМ¶adi anele.  
\v 30 IgaataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adotoinaЙЎМ¶atijegi ane jajigotaЙЎМ¶awa aЙЎМ¶adibeyacaЙЎМ¶ati, codaa ЙЎМ¶adoyaЙЎМ¶agi ane jajigotaЙЎМ¶awa aiwaaЙЎМ¶adi.вҖқ 
\c 12  
\s1 Jesus ane ЗӨoniotagodi baaniЙЎМ¶iniaa niiЙЎМ¶etedoЙЎМ¶owa ane jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina me saabado (noko anodeemitetibige judeutedi leeЙЎМ¶odi niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi) 
\r (Marcos 2.23-28; Lucas 6.1-5) 
\p  
\v 1 Odaa naЙЎМ¶a saabado, Jesus ja yakagiditedeloco ica nixoЙЎМ¶otagi ane dinanateloco leyeema. NiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece ijo mijoataЙЎМ¶a, ja nigodi nigigi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶onotegi ligegi leyeema oyeligo lolagi.  
\v 2 Pida ijoa icoa fariseutedi anonadi noЙЎМ¶onotegi ligecidi leyeema. NoЙЎМ¶onadi, odaa moditalo Jesus, вҖңDigawini! NiЙЎМ¶idi anodiotibigaЙЎМ¶adici joЙЎМ¶owo ane yolitoЙЎМ¶odomi ЙЎМ¶onajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi niЙЎМ¶ina me saabado.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 3 Odaa Jesus ja igiditediogi, mee, вҖңAjawienataka niЙЎМ¶ica malomeЙЎМ¶eniteloco ane loenatagi Davi niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, Davi icaaЙЎМ¶icoa lokaaЙЎМ¶etedi nigodi nigigi.  
\v 4 Davi naЙЎМ¶a dakatiwece liЙЎМ¶eladi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa ja yeligo niЙЎМ¶ijoa paontedi baanaЙЎМ¶a oibootalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ligiiwepodi lokaaЙЎМ¶etedi. Pida ЙЎМ¶onajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶e me diЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me yeligo niЙЎМ¶ijoa paontedi. Ijokijoa sacerdotitedi moyakadi moyeligo niЙЎМ¶ijoa paontedi.  
\v 5 Eleditace, midiwa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, idi liwai ane iditini MoisГ©s, iwoteloco sacerdotitedi me yakadi mowo libakedi niЙЎМ¶ina me saabado, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee, aЙЎМ¶oyotete niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi ane ЙЎМ¶odoli me jibaaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina me saabado, pida anilaagetedipi. Odaa ajawienataka neЙЎМ¶eliodi malomeЙЎМ¶enitibigelogo niЙЎМ¶idiwa notaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 6 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji digoina ЙЎМ¶adiwigotigi ini oko ane daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi caticedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi.  
\v 7 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a mee, вҖҳJemaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko moiwikode eledi oko, pida ajemaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko moyeloadi eijeeЙЎМ¶agi monibootiwa.вҖҷ DoЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji ane diitigilo niЙЎМ¶inoa notaЙЎМ¶a, agotaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶alaagetedipi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane diЙЎМ¶ica leemidi.  
\v 8 IgaataЙЎМ¶a Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, ida inaЙЎМ¶atetigi me idalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ica ane jakataЙЎМ¶a me jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina me saabado.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me saabado 
\r (Marcos 3.1-6; Lucas 6.6-11) 
\p  
\v 9 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a noditedice niЙЎМ¶ijo aneite, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo manitaЙЎМ¶a liiakanaЙЎМ¶axi judeutedi.  
\v 10 Odaa ini ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa beyagi libaaЙЎМ¶adi, alejaado. Pida idi niЙЎМ¶ijoa neloЙЎМ¶ododipi Jesus odoletibige me nilaagedi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi moige, moditalo, вҖңIjo ЙЎМ¶onajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi, domige ЙЎМ¶odika me jicilatitaЙЎМ¶a eelotaginaЙЎМ¶a ina me saabado?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 11 Odaa ja igidi Jesus, meetediogi, вҖңDiЙЎМ¶ini niЙЎМ¶ina akaamitiwaji anokanitece niwaxacoco, oditaЙЎМ¶a daxaboketinece begi niЙЎМ¶ina me saabado, odaa domigetaЙЎМ¶a dinoniciwaЙЎМ¶aditibece me noЙЎМ¶atice niwaxacoco midataЙЎМ¶a begi.  
\v 12 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina oko baЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mida niwalГі caticedi waxacoco. Odaa jaЙЎМ¶anatitiwaji ЙЎМ¶onajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi me daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odoli me jaoЙЎМ¶a anele niЙЎМ¶ina me saabado.вҖқ  
\v 13 Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eete niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa alejaado, вҖңIxokenitice ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶adi!вҖқ Odaa ja ixoketice libaaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa ja icГӯ libaaЙЎМ¶adi, ja liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo caticedi.  
\v 14 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi ja noditicoaci, odaa ja dinatecoЙЎМ¶otee odinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etigi nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi moyeloadi Jesus. 
\s1 Ica liotagi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iolatedice 
\p  
\v 15 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a yowooЙЎМ¶odi modoletibige moyeloadi, odaa ja noditedicogi aneite. Eliodi oko odiotece, codaa nicilatiditedi ijotawece neelotaginadi anoyadeegitalo.  
\v 16 Pida najoitediniwace me diЙЎМ¶ica anoyeloЙЎМ¶odita.  
\v 17 Odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa neЙЎМ¶eote micotece niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a IsaГӯas, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, me yalaЙЎМ¶atalo Jesus, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee, 
\q1  
\v 18 вҖңDigawini! 
\q1 Etiniwa Iotagi, 
\q1 ane jiolatedice. 
\q1 Jemaa, codaa eliodi meote me idinitibeci. 
\q1 Jixotiogilo Iwigo. 
\q1 Odaa ja yatematitediogi niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi niЙЎМ¶ina ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, 
\q1 codaa me eetetece micota me jiwi anejigotiogi niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi 
\q1 leeЙЎМ¶odi loenataka. 
\q1  
\v 19 NiЙЎМ¶iniwa Iotagi adinotigimadetetege oko, 
\q1 oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yapaawe oko. 
\q1 AdinigetaЙЎМ¶atee me dotaЙЎМ¶a aneitice me yatecoЙЎМ¶o oko minoa nigotadi. 
\q1  
\v 20 Doweditedeloco oko ane deЙЎМ¶eliodi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, 
\q1 ane liciagi naЙЎМ¶ana niale libiwe ane dinoke, 
\q1 codaa ayaaЙЎМ¶adi eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, 
\q1 niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane liciagi nadegogo anokexaa doЙЎМ¶ocilaЙЎМ¶ade. 
\q1 Eote niЙЎМ¶ida libakedi 
\q1 nigepaa iЙЎМ¶eke inoatawece ane beyagi. 
\q1  
\v 21 Odaa inatawece ane noiigi onibeotege meote me newiЙЎМ¶atace.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus iniaa Belzebu 
\r (Marcos 3.20-30; Lucas 11.14-23) 
\p  
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi joЙЎМ¶onadeegitalo Jesus ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane dakatiogi niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi aneo me ЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶a codaa mewaloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa Jesus ja icilatidi, ja yakadi me dotaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me yatetacibece.  
\v 23 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi joЙЎМ¶oyopo, odaa modi, вҖңManigidaaЙЎМ¶idoa icoa anida aneetetege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЙЎМ¶odaxawa?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 24 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi noЙЎМ¶owajipatalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditiogi, вҖңYakadi me iticoitedice niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi leeЙЎМ¶odi Belzebu yajigotalo loniciwaЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 25 Jesus yowooЙЎМ¶oditediwe lowoogo, odaa meetediogi, вҖңNigidi noiigi ane dawalacetiwage, odaa dinideleЙЎМ¶e, niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi icota me dinaaЙЎМ¶adi. Codaa nigidi niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a, oЙЎМ¶oa domige dinoiigiwepodi, ane dawalacetiwage, codaa dinideleЙЎМ¶e, icota mepaa dinaaЙЎМ¶adi.  
\v 26 Odaa niЙЎМ¶inoa ane liotaka SatanГЎs nigoiticoitedice eletidi liotaka SatanГЎs, odaa ja dawalacetiwage, odaa icota me ma loniciwaЙЎМ¶a SatanГЎs.  
\v 27 Menitiwaji me jiticoitedice niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi Belzebu, ane SatanГЎs, me najigotiwa yoniciwaЙЎМ¶a. Enice ame yajigotiogi anodiotibigaЙЎМ¶adici loniciwaЙЎМ¶a moiticoitice niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi? Odaa niЙЎМ¶idi anodiotibigaЙЎМ¶adici oikee makamaЙЎМ¶a adininaalenitiwaji.  
\v 28 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina me jiticoitice niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi, jatika loniciwaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo. Odaa joaniЙЎМ¶idaa me jikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji naЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko ЙЎМ¶adiwigotigitiwaji. 
\p  
\v 29 Digowoo niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa loniciweЙЎМ¶enigi. AЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me dakatiwece liЙЎМ¶eladi, oditaЙЎМ¶a dolicetalo ane nepilidi nige daЙЎМ¶a odoejegi me oigoetini. Idokida nige oigoetini niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa loniciweЙЎМ¶enigi odaa boЙЎМ¶oyakadi moyadeegi ane nepilidi.  
\v 30 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶a dibatigi, odaa yakapetegi. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a idaxawa me nadeegitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji oko, odaa niЙЎМ¶ini oko inibeyacaЙЎМ¶atagodi, codaa eo oko mepaanaЙЎМ¶a leegitalo moyototedice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 31 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi mejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice inoatawece ane latopaco libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco oko, codaa niЙЎМ¶inoa lotaЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi modotaЙЎМ¶atibige. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baadaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice niЙЎМ¶ina oko modotaЙЎМ¶atibige Liwigo.  
\v 32 Codaa baЙЎМ¶a yakadi me ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice niЙЎМ¶ina oko modotaЙЎМ¶atibigiji, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baadaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice niЙЎМ¶ina oko me beyagi modotaЙЎМ¶atibige Liwigo, aixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice niЙЎМ¶ina natigide, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi. 
\s1 JowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a niale leeЙЎМ¶odi ela 
\r (Lucas 6.43-45) 
\p  
\v 33 NaЙЎМ¶ana niale nigele, odaa elali eletidi ele, pida nige deЙЎМ¶ele naЙЎМ¶ada niale, odaa elali idaaЙЎМ¶ee beyagi. JakataЙЎМ¶a me jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a niale leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa elali ane yajigo.  
\v 34 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji ЙЎМ¶adiciagi laketedi ane diniweneene. Akaami abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶atetiwaji, odaa aЙЎМ¶akati me ЙЎМ¶adalaki anele. IgaataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odotaЙЎМ¶a ane icoЙЎМ¶otiwece ЙЎМ¶onioladi, icoЙЎМ¶otiwece ЙЎМ¶odaaleЙЎМ¶ena.  
\v 35 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko anele, nolee laaleЙЎМ¶ena niЙЎМ¶inoa anele, codaa lotaЙЎМ¶a inokinoa anele. NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane beyagi laaleЙЎМ¶ena, odaa yalaЙЎМ¶ata inokina ane beyagi. 
\p  
\v 36 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige iwi anigote me iloikatidi oko leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, odaa laagetedipi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anoyalaЙЎМ¶a inokina ane ibeyacaЙЎМ¶adi lewiЙЎМ¶a eledi oko. Codaa leeditibige moyeloЙЎМ¶oditalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane leeЙЎМ¶odi modi niЙЎМ¶ijoa notaЙЎМ¶a ane beyagi.  
\v 37 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eetedaЙЎМ¶aloco makaami niЙЎМ¶ica oko anele nige ЙЎМ¶adalakita inokina anele, pida nige inoka ЙЎМ¶adalakita ane beyagi motaЙЎМ¶ani, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eetedaЙЎМ¶aloco makaami oko ane beyagi, odaa ja ЙЎМ¶adiloikatiti.вҖқ 
\s1 Judeutedi odipokotalo Jesus meote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi me ikee mewi me niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji 
\r (Marcos 8.11-12; Lucas 11.29-32) 
\p  
\v 38 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi onidiwa onateciЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, icaaЙЎМ¶icoa fariseutedi igotibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa moditalo, вҖңNiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, jemaanaЙЎМ¶a mawii ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi bidige anikeenitoЙЎМ¶owa mewi me AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶eni, codaa me yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶adoniciwaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 39 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a igidi, meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina noiigi aninaa niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi abeyaceЙЎМ¶egipi, codaa me aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Oyemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi ane ikee me najigotediwa yoniciwaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me idiiЙЎМ¶e me jao ibakedi. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶eote eledi ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi anakati manatitiwaji. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide akaa ikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me idiiЙЎМ¶e leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo ninyaagi Jonas, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 40 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jonas me idei catiwedi le noЙЎМ¶ojegi nelegi, ane yalitini, odaa idiaaЙЎМ¶i le itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi, itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida enoaleli. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶eji Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, etidaligiti itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi, itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida enoaleli.  
\v 41 NiЙЎМ¶ica noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige iwi anigote me iloikatidi oko leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, niЙЎМ¶ijo oko ane niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a NГӯnive nige dabiditiniwace me newiЙЎМ¶atace, odaa jaЙЎМ¶akaami nilaagetedipi, leeЙЎМ¶odi mepaЙЎМ¶a odinilaatece libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶owajipatalo lotaЙЎМ¶a Jonas. Jemaa mejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, niЙЎМ¶ida me Ee daЙЎМ¶axa me Ee ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi caticedi Jonas, pida idokee aЙЎМ¶adinilaanitece ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶eco niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a ajipaatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 42 Codaa niЙЎМ¶ica noko naЙЎМ¶ajo iniona, ane icoЙЎМ¶oticogi natinediteloco, nige yewiЙЎМ¶atace, odaa jaЙЎМ¶akaami laagetedipitetiwaji, igaataЙЎМ¶a baЙЎМ¶a leegitece me diniwiaje migo wajipatalo liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco SalomГЈo, niЙЎМ¶ijo anowidi lixaketedi. Odaa digawini! Ee, ane daЙЎМ¶axa me Ee ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi caticedi SalomГЈo, ite Ee digoina makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji. Pida aЙЎМ¶emaanitiwaji majipaatalo iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco. 
\s1 AnodaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ina oko noЙЎМ¶opitaceloco niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi 
\r (Lucas 11.24-26) 
\p  
\v 43-44 NiЙЎМ¶ina niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi me noditicogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igoteloco nipodaЙЎМ¶a ane yadilo codaa me daxixe, doletibige ane lotokaЙЎМ¶adi. Pida nige diЙЎМ¶ica yakadi lotokaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa mee me dotaЙЎМ¶a, вҖҳEjime jopitacicogi iЙЎМ¶eladi ane jicoЙЎМ¶oticogi.вҖҷ Nigopitio, odaa jiЙЎМ¶icota liЙЎМ¶eladi me diЙЎМ¶ica ane itidi, yapidi, codaa me ilaaЙЎМ¶atini.  
\v 45 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotiogi eletidi seete niwicidi ane daЙЎМ¶axa me abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a modiЙЎМ¶eladetigi niЙЎМ¶ini oko. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ini oko jeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi caticedi niЙЎМ¶ijo anee jotigide. Odaa icota midaaЙЎМ¶ee, niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi ane abeyaceЙЎМ¶egipi aninaa niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi.вҖқ 
\s1 Ica loiigiwepodi Jesus 
\r (Marcos 3.31-35; Lucas 8.19-21) 
\p  
\v 46 EЙЎМ¶idaa diiticogi Jesus me notaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etediniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi, odaa naЙЎМ¶ajo eliodo, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo nioxoadipi joЙЎМ¶ototicogi aneite. Odaa idiaaЙЎМ¶iticoaci we niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi aneitedice Jesus, odoletibige moyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e.  
\v 47 Odaa ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa meetalo Jesus, вҖңЗӨadiodo, ЙЎМ¶anioxoadipi etidi we. DomoЙЎМ¶oyemaa metiЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 48 Odaa Jesus naЙЎМ¶a igidi niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane ibodicaxi, meeteta, вҖңAmaajo aca eiodo? Codaa amiidi ica inioxoadipi?вҖқ  
\v 49 Odaa ja dikeenatakatediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, mee, вҖңDigawini! NaЙЎМ¶ani beЙЎМ¶eiodo, codaa niЙЎМ¶idi beЙЎМ¶ewi me inioxoadipi!  
\v 50 IgaataЙЎМ¶a inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina anowo ane yemaa Eiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi, joaniЙЎМ¶inaa beЙЎМ¶ewi me inioxoadipi, iniwaalepodi, codaa me eiodo.вҖқ 
\c 13  
\s1 Jesus yatemati natematigo ane iciaceeketege niЙЎМ¶ina anetanaЙЎМ¶a 
\r (Marcos 4.1-9; Lucas 8.4-8) 
\p  
\v 1 IjaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo noko Jesus ja noditedice niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo liniogotibece niweiigi GalilГ©ia. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaa nicote me iiЙЎМ¶axi ijo noiigi-nelegi.  
\v 2 Eliodi oko anototalo, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyawiile. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi naЙЎМ¶a waxoditedinigi ajo etogawaana, odaa ja nicotedinigi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi baЙЎМ¶a dabiditiniwace liniogotibece ninyoЙЎМ¶odi.  
\v 3 Odaa Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶axi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi. NaЙЎМ¶a niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace, yatemati owidi natematiko anida ane iciaceeketetege. Odaa mee me datematika, вҖңIca ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa onigo lixoЙЎМ¶otagi etanaЙЎМ¶a, odaa yadeegi nolacidi.  
\v 4 NaЙЎМ¶a yaladitedibece niЙЎМ¶ijoa nolacidi meyatedini, onicoa lolacidi aneniteloco liniogotibece naigi. Odaa ilaaЙЎМ¶axodi joЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶oja.  
\v 5 Icoa eletidi lolacidi boЙЎМ¶oneniteloco wetiadawaanaЙЎМ¶a, ane deЙЎМ¶ewi mica iiЙЎМ¶o. NiЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi yediiЙЎМ¶a me nokoloЙЎМ¶o leeЙЎМ¶odi iiЙЎМ¶o aleegitinece.  
\v 6 Pida naЙЎМ¶a dapicoЙЎМ¶o aligeЙЎМ¶e, odaa ja yalegi nawodigijedi, odaa ja yadilo leeЙЎМ¶odi aleegitinece litodi.  
\v 7 Odaa icoa eletidi lolacidi boЙЎМ¶oneniteloco ipelakijadi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ipelaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶a ili, odaa ja yapoЙЎМ¶oditedini niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodigijedi.  
\v 8 Pida eletidi lolacidi boЙЎМ¶oneniteloco iiЙЎМ¶o anele. Odaa baЙЎМ¶a ili codaa etaye, yajigo owidi ligecidi. Idatecibece libatadi yajigo onaniteci taalia ligecidi, idaaЙЎМ¶eledi baЙЎМ¶a yajigo seseenta, idatibece baЙЎМ¶a triinta.  
\v 9 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane wajipatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a, leeditibige me watacotece.вҖқ 
\s1 Ane leeЙЎМ¶odi Jesus me yatemati natematiko anida ane iciaceeketetege 
\r (Marcos 4.10-12; Lucas 8.9-10) 
\p  
\v 10 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus joЙЎМ¶ototalo, odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo, вҖңIgaamee ina mabakeni natematigo anida ane iciaceekenitege, ina matematikanitema ina oko?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 11 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meetediogi, вҖңAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baЙЎМ¶a yemaa me ikeetedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji ane nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko, ane diЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi anodaaЙЎМ¶ee. Odaa baadaЙЎМ¶a ikeetediogi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko.  
\v 12 Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eneЙЎМ¶egi ikeete niЙЎМ¶ina oko baanaЙЎМ¶a oyowooЙЎМ¶odi anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali. Codaa noЙЎМ¶a lixakedi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane daЙЎМ¶a yemaa me yowooЙЎМ¶odi anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko, icaaЙЎМ¶ica nige domiЙЎМ¶iniawaanigi niЙЎМ¶ini oko lixakedi.  
\v 13 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi mepaЙЎМ¶a jibake natematiko anida ane jiciaceeketege niЙЎМ¶ina me jatematikatiogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko. Odaa etidadi pida aЙЎМ¶etidowooЙЎМ¶odi. Codaa owajipatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a, pida aЙЎМ¶odibatege, codaa aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi ane diitigilo.  
\v 14 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ida anee joЙЎМ¶owo micotece niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a IsaГӯas, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a iditini ane ligegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, neЙЎМ¶ee, 
\q1 вҖҳIcota majipaatatiwaji, 
\q1 pida aЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti ane diitigi. 
\q1 Icota mawinitiwaji, 
\q1 pida aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a anatitiwaji. 
\q1  
\v 15 LeeЙЎМ¶odi oyakakaЙЎМ¶adi laaleЙЎМ¶enali, 
\q1 codaa adinajipake, 
\q1 codaa adoletibigiwaji. 
\q1 DaЙЎМ¶aleetiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi, 
\q1 toЙЎМ¶oyakadi monadi, 
\q1 codaa mowajipatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a, 
\q1 codaa toЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi ane diitigilo, 
\q1 codaa toЙЎМ¶odopitiwa oditaЙЎМ¶a jinicilatiditiniwaci.вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 16 Pida aniniitibecetiwaji leeЙЎМ¶odi akati manati, codaa majipaatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 17 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. Eliodi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji codaa eliodi oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji domoЙЎМ¶oyemaa monadi niЙЎМ¶inoa analeeЙЎМ¶anati, pida aЙЎМ¶onadi, codaa domoЙЎМ¶oyemaa mowajipatalo niЙЎМ¶inoa yotaЙЎМ¶a anajipaatalo, pida aЙЎМ¶owajipatalo. 
\s1 Jesus yeloЙЎМ¶odi anodaa diitigi natematigigi niЙЎМ¶ijo anetanaЙЎМ¶a 
\r (Marcos 4.13-20; Lucas 8.11-15) 
\p  
\v 18 Natigide anajipaatiwaji, codaa adiniiЙЎМ¶axinitece anodaa diitigi natematigigi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko anetanaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 19 NiЙЎМ¶ina anowajipata natematigo ane yalaЙЎМ¶ata anodaaЙЎМ¶ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶ena oko, pida aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi ane diitigilo, niЙЎМ¶ina oko liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi anenitedini naigi liniogotibece. LeeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa neЙЎМ¶enagi, odaa ja noЙЎМ¶atedice lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane ideite catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena digo mijoataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa ilaaЙЎМ¶axodi monoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi midi naigi.  
\v 20 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi anenitedini midiwataЙЎМ¶a wetiadawaanaЙЎМ¶a baЙЎМ¶a liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane wajipatalo natematiko, odaa dibatege, codaa me ninitibigiwaji.  
\v 21 Pida liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi anenitedini midiwataЙЎМ¶a wetiadawaanaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶a nokoloЙЎМ¶o aleegitinece litodi, jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane deЙЎМ¶ewi monakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa aleegi jeЙЎМ¶eyamaЙЎМ¶aticoace niЙЎМ¶ina menagi lawikodico, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina moiatetibeci.  
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi anenitedini miditaЙЎМ¶a ipelakijadi, liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anowajipata natematigo, pida owidi inoa ligecaЙЎМ¶aleЙЎМ¶etedi leeЙЎМ¶odi ane yopotibige, odaa odoletibige mowidi niliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi, odaa epaa dininaale. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶alee ewianaЙЎМ¶a oyowo natematigo, odaa natematigo aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a iigi ane lakataЙЎМ¶a me yewiЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 23 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi anenitedini miditaЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶o anele, beЙЎМ¶etaye, idatecibece libatadi yajigo onaniteci taalia ligecidi, codaa idatecibece yajigo seseenta ligecidi, idaaЙЎМ¶eledi yajigo triinta ligecidi. NiЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anowajipata natematigo, odaa oyowooЙЎМ¶odi ane diitigi. Odaa natematigo ja iigi lewiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko eo mowo anele.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus yatemati latematigo ane iciaceeketetege nadegogo ane diniweneene 
\p  
\v 24 Jesus yatematitediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi eledi natematigo anida ane iciaceeketetege, meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e oko laaleЙЎМ¶ena, liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa aneyatini nolacidi anele miditaЙЎМ¶a lixoЙЎМ¶otagi.  
\v 25 Ica enoale naЙЎМ¶a niotaЙЎМ¶a liotaka, odaa jeЙЎМ¶enagi niЙЎМ¶ica laxakawa. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ini laxakawa ja yokoletedice eletidi lolacidi liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ijo leyeema. NiЙЎМ¶icoa lolacidi one diniweneene, codaa one latopiwa leyeema. Odaa joЙЎМ¶opi niЙЎМ¶ijo laxakawa.  
\v 26 NaЙЎМ¶a ili niЙЎМ¶ijo leyeema, odaa ja yeloЙЎМ¶o ligecidi. Odaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yeloЙЎМ¶o niЙЎМ¶ijo nadegogo ane diniweneene.  
\v 27 Odaa liimetedi niЙЎМ¶ijo bajendeoodi jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci midataЙЎМ¶a, odaa modita, вҖҳЗӨonecalailegi, niЙЎМ¶ida makaami geme anitedi lolacidi anele. Enice, igame icoЙЎМ¶oticogi ina nadegogo ane diniweneene?вҖҷ  
\v 28 Odaa ja igidi, meetiogi, вҖҳYaxakawa libakedi.вҖҷ Odaa liimetedi joЙЎМ¶oige, modita, вҖҳEmaani me inawacenaЙЎМ¶a ina nadegogo ane diniweneene?вҖҷ  
\v 29 Odaa ja igidi, meetiogi, вҖҳOЙЎМ¶oa! IgaataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a anawaceni niЙЎМ¶ida nadegogo, doidetibige maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anawaceni leyeema libatadi.  
\v 30 Dioki leyeema epaaЙЎМ¶awatege nadegogo me ili nigepaaЙЎМ¶icota limedi me inopilaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶atio. NiЙЎМ¶ica noko, ejitiogi anonakagidi leyeema, вҖңOdoejegi manawacenitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina nadegogo ane diniweneene, codaa awiitibige ligoxe, odaa okolenitiogi noledi. NigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a aladieni leyeema, odaa baЙЎМ¶a anopilaЙЎМ¶atitiwece diimigi aneitice me jotete yawodigijedi.вҖқ вҖҷвҖқ 
\s1 Natematigigi lolagi aca вҖңmostaadaвҖқ icaaЙЎМ¶ica ane yabooЙЎМ¶odi leyeema 
\r (Marcos 4.30-32, 33-34; Lucas 13.18-19, 20-21) 
\p  
\v 31 Jesus yatematitediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi eledi natematigo anida ane iciaceeketetege, meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e oko laaleЙЎМ¶enali, liciagi naЙЎМ¶ana lolacawaana вҖҳmostaadaвҖҷ ane dibata ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eyateloco lixoЙЎМ¶otagi.  
\v 32 NaЙЎМ¶ani lolagi daЙЎМ¶axa me lionawaana liwigotigi inoatawece eletidi ane niale lolacidi. Pida nige ili, odaa yayoketacedice inoatawece ane ЙЎМ¶odawodigijedi, codaa ili nigepaa icota me niale nelegi. Codaa ilaaЙЎМ¶axodi owote libatoli midoataЙЎМ¶a libiwedi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 33 Odaa Jesus ja yatematitediogi eledi natematigo, meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e oko laaleЙЎМ¶enali, liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina ane yabooЙЎМ¶odi leyeema anoibake iwaalepodi. Nige yawanaЙЎМ¶aditege itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida baxia leyeema, odaa niЙЎМ¶ica labookojegi jeЙЎМ¶eo me ili, dabo initawece niЙЎМ¶ini leyeema.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 34 Jesus idioka limedi me yeloЙЎМ¶odi natematiko anida ane iciaceeketetege niЙЎМ¶ina me iiЙЎМ¶axi niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi. NiЙЎМ¶ina me niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace, aЙЎМ¶ica daaditaЙЎМ¶a ibaketeda natematigo anida ane iciaceeketetege.  
\v 35 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus me datematika, eote micotece lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide neЙЎМ¶ee, 
\q1 вҖңJatemati natematigo anida ane jiciaceeketege, 
\q1 niЙЎМ¶ina me jatematikatema. 
\q1 Codaa jeloЙЎМ¶oditiogi niЙЎМ¶ina ane diЙЎМ¶ica moyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo maleekoka yoeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus yeloЙЎМ¶odi anodaa diitigi niЙЎМ¶ijo natematigigi nadegogo ane diniweneene 
\p  
\v 36 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a ibode niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo minitaЙЎМ¶a ica diimigi. NaЙЎМ¶a dakatedio, niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶odipegitalo, odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo, вҖңAneloЙЎМ¶otitoЙЎМ¶owa ane diitigi niЙЎМ¶ijo natematigigi nadegogo ane diniweneene.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 37 Odaa ja igidi Jesus, meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijo aneyatedini lolacidi anele jeЙЎМ¶emeЙЎМ¶ee, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi.  
\v 38 NiЙЎМ¶ijo nixoЙЎМ¶otagi baЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o anejonaЙЎМ¶ateloco. NiЙЎМ¶ijoa lolacidi anele baЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko anida aneetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, leeЙЎМ¶odi me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo nadegogo ane diniweneene baЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko anida aneetege ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa, ane abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi.  
\v 39 NiЙЎМ¶ijo aneyatini nadegogo ane diniweneene baЙЎМ¶a diaabo, ane ЙЎМ¶odaxakawa. NiЙЎМ¶ijo noko me dinopilaЙЎМ¶aditedio nawodigijedi baЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica noko nigicota liniogo niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anonioda leyeema baЙЎМ¶a aanjotedi.  
\v 40 MijoataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa niimetedi anonawace nadegogo ane diniweneene, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyalegi mini noledi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee nigicota me ma niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o.  
\v 41 Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, jiniiЙЎМ¶e iniaanjotedi anodibatomi moiomaЙЎМ¶adi oko anowo ane beyagi, codaa anowo eledi oko minoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Odaa iniaanjotedi joЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶aticoace niЙЎМ¶idi oko liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶idi eledi oko anepiЙЎМ¶ida anejitege.  
\v 42 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyokoletiwece niЙЎМ¶idi oko catiwedi noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶itice oko me noenaЙЎМ¶ateloco, codaa oyacigice lowe leeЙЎМ¶odi lawikodico.  
\v 43 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji anida anejitege baЙЎМ¶a dataletibigiwaji lodoe AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ane Eliodi, liciagi aligeЙЎМ¶e me datale. NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane wajipatalo yotaЙЎМ¶a, leeditibige me watacotece! 
\s1 Jesus yatemati natematigo ane iciaceeketetege aca nalicexe acaaЙЎМ¶aca wetiЙЎМ¶a ane diniwaloe 
\p  
\v 44 NiЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ina oko laaleЙЎМ¶enali, liciagi naЙЎМ¶ana nalicexe aneiteloco nipodigi. Odaa ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa jona yakadi, pida one naligitacini. Odaa eliodi me ninitibece, codaa jeЙЎМ¶eyaa icoatawece ane nepilidi, niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi joЙЎМ¶opitacijo migo me dinoojeteta niЙЎМ¶ijo nipodigi eotibige me nebi naЙЎМ¶ajo nalicexe. 
\p  
\v 45 Eleditace niЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e oko laaleЙЎМ¶enali, liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina anoojetekegi ane doletibige me dinoojeteta wetiЙЎМ¶a ane diniwaloe.  
\v 46 Odaa naЙЎМ¶ani lakate wetiЙЎМ¶a aneliodi niwalГі, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo meyaa ijoatawece ane nepilidi. Odaa ja dinoojeteta naЙЎМ¶aca wetiЙЎМ¶a ane diniwaloe. 
\s1 Natematigigi neladi lajo modibatalo noЙЎМ¶ojedi 
\p  
\v 47 NiЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e oko laaleЙЎМ¶enali, liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina neladi anoyokoletinigi weiigi. NiЙЎМ¶ina neladi dibatalo inoatawece ane latopaco noЙЎМ¶ojedi.  
\v 48 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina neladi naЙЎМ¶a nolee noЙЎМ¶ojedi, niЙЎМ¶ina nomiigomigipi oixigiticogi daato, odaa nicotiniwace moiomaЙЎМ¶adi noЙЎМ¶ojedi. NiЙЎМ¶inoa noЙЎМ¶ojedi anele boЙЎМ¶oyexaЙЎМ¶atinigi naЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi, pida niЙЎМ¶inoa noЙЎМ¶ojedi ane deЙЎМ¶eleteda me jelicaЙЎМ¶a boЙЎМ¶oyaladi.  
\v 49 NiЙЎМ¶ica noko nigicota liniogo niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee. Aanjotedi enagitibeci, moiolaticoace oko, odaa onoЙЎМ¶atedice niЙЎМ¶inoa oko abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ina oko anepaЙЎМ¶a iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji.  
\v 50 Odaa oyokoletiogi niЙЎМ¶idi oko abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a catiwedi noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe. Aneitice oko me noenaЙЎМ¶ateloco, codaa oyacigice lowe leeЙЎМ¶odi lawikodico.вҖқ 
\s1 NiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco geladi idiaa icoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco laxokodi 
\p  
\v 51 Jesus igetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, meetediogi, вҖңMigowooЙЎМ¶otitecetiwaji ijoatawece ijoa yatematiko?вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңJowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a, ЗӨoniotagodiвҖқ.  
\v 52 Odaa meetediogi, вҖңEnice digawini! Inatawece niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, niЙЎМ¶ina naЙЎМ¶a ikatece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶ena, ja liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina eniodi anani lotetenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi aneyate niЙЎМ¶inoa nepilidi ane diniwaloe, odaa yakadi me diba niЙЎМ¶ina ane gela, oЙЎМ¶oa, domige niЙЎМ¶ina baanaЙЎМ¶a oxiiЙЎМ¶odi, me yajigotiogi lionigipi. JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ijo niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a yakadi me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece niЙЎМ¶ina niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi gela, codaa me niЙЎМ¶ina oxiiЙЎМ¶odi niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi.вҖқ 
\s1 NiЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi nigotaЙЎМ¶a NazarГ© aЙЎМ¶onakato Jesus 
\r (Marcos 6.1-6; Lucas 4.16-30) 
\p  
\v 53 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a ika me yatemati niЙЎМ¶ijoa latematiko aninoa ane iciaceeketege, odaa ja noditedice niЙЎМ¶ijo aneite.  
\v 54 Odaa joЙЎМ¶opitedicogi manitaЙЎМ¶a epaa nigotaЙЎМ¶a. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a mani niiakanaЙЎМ¶axi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anowajipatalo joЙЎМ¶oyopo leeЙЎМ¶odi liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi. Odaa ja dinigetiwage, modi, вҖңIgame yakadite icoa lixaketedi? Codaa igame icoЙЎМ¶otigi loniciwaЙЎМ¶a meote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi?  
\v 55 NiЙЎМ¶idoa lionigi niЙЎМ¶ijoda gapinteelegi. Codaa naЙЎМ¶ajoda eliodo ЙЎМ¶odowooЙЎМ¶ota, Maria. Codaa Tiago, JosГ©, SimГЈo ijaa Judas nioxoadipi.  
\v 56 Codaa me niwaalepodi inaa liЙЎМ¶eladi digoina NazarГ©. Enice, igamigodaaЙЎМ¶ee ica me yakadi me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a, codaa meote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi?вҖқ  
\v 57 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica mowote. Pida Jesus meetediogi, вҖңIdioka limedi moiweniЙЎМ¶ide niЙЎМ¶ina ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida aniokani epaa nigotaЙЎМ¶a codaa me liЙЎМ¶eladi, baadoЙЎМ¶oiweniЙЎМ¶ide.вҖқ  
\v 58 Odaa Jesus onateciЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi aneote manitaЙЎМ¶a epaa nigotaЙЎМ¶a, leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi aЙЎМ¶onakato. 
\c 14  
\s1 LemeЙЎМ¶egi JoГЈo Batista 
\r (Marcos 6.14-29; Lucas 9.7-9) 
\p  
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa nokododi Herodes, ninionigi-eliodi nipodigi GalilГ©ia, ja dibodicetibige Jesus.  
\v 2 Odaa meetiogi liotagipi, вҖңEjime niЙЎМ¶idaa JoГЈo Batista, ejinaЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace me idei aneiticoace Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. Odaa leeЙЎМ¶odi naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace, odaa jiЙЎМ¶ida loniciwaЙЎМ¶a meote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 3 Herodes eote niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi jiЙЎМ¶ijaa diiЙЎМ¶enatakata moniwilo JoГЈo, moigoe libaaЙЎМ¶atedi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oixotiwece niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi. IdiЙЎМ¶igota JoГЈo leeЙЎМ¶ote Herodias ane lodawa Filipe nioxoa Herodes. (Herodias ja lodawa Herodes ane niniwoodi.)  
\v 4 JoГЈo ijo meeta Herodes, вҖңЗӨoniiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi yolitaЙЎМ¶adomi me ЙЎМ¶adodawa naЙЎМ¶ani lodawa ЙЎМ¶anioxoa.вҖқ  
\v 5 Odaa Herodes ja domaЙЎМ¶a yemaa me yeloadi JoГЈo, pida doitiogi niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi, leeЙЎМ¶odi oyowooЙЎМ¶odi JoГЈo miniЙЎМ¶ina ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. 
\p  
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶icota ica lanikegi Herodes, odaa ja nalooЙЎМ¶o. Aca liona Herodias ja dinibaile lodoe iditawece nodenigipi, odaa Herodes eliodi me ninitibece.  
\v 7 Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eo ligegitege naЙЎМ¶ajo awicije meo noЙЎМ¶eedi okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ane dipokotibige. 
\p  
\v 8 NaЙЎМ¶ajo eliodo ja yeloЙЎМ¶odita ica ane lipoketegita Herodes. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo naЙЎМ¶ajo awicije minitaЙЎМ¶a Herodes, odaa meeta, вҖңJemaa me anajicitiwa lacilo JoГЈo Batista exakitinigi ЙЎМ¶inogo niЙЎМ¶ina natigide.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 9 Odaa Herodes, inionigi-eliodi, jaЙЎМ¶agecaЙЎМ¶alo. Pida jeЙЎМ¶eo niЙЎМ¶ijo ligegi ane daЙЎМ¶a yakadi me inoke lodoe niЙЎМ¶ijo lodenigipi me lalokegi lanikegi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi meo niЙЎМ¶ijo ane lipoketegi naЙЎМ¶ajo awicije.  
\v 10 Odaa ja diiЙЎМ¶enatakata moyakagiditice JoГЈo lacilo manitaЙЎМ¶a niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi.  
\v 11 Odaa joЙЎМ¶onadeegi lacilo JoГЈo oyexaЙЎМ¶atinigi ЙЎМ¶inogo, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyajigota naЙЎМ¶ajo awicije, odaa ja yadeegita eliodo niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶inogo.  
\v 12 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibeci JoГЈo jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegi lolaadi monaligitini. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci oyatematitalo Jesus. 
\s1 Jesus niodeЙЎМ¶etedini noiigi-nelegi 
\r (Marcos 6.30-44; Lucas 9.10-17; JoГЈo 6.1-14) 
\p  
\v 13 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a dibodicetedibige ane ninyaagi JoГЈo, odaa ja noditedice niЙЎМ¶ijo aneite, waxoditedinigi niwatece, igo mokijoatece miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi ane diЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi. Pida ijo noiigi-nelegi joЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi ane diitedicogi, odaa ja noditicoaci nigotadi, jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci onewaligitibigiwaji moigaalatece Jesus.  
\v 14 IgaanaЙЎМ¶a waxoditedice niwatece, odaa ja nadi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi. Odaa eliodi me iwikodetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi, odaa ja nicilatiditediniwace neelotaginadi. 
\p  
\v 15 NaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶ocidi, niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus joЙЎМ¶odiitalo, odaa moditalo, вҖңJa ЙЎМ¶ocidi, codaa aЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi niЙЎМ¶ina nipodigi anejonaЙЎМ¶a. IiЙЎМ¶eni niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi mopitibeci, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a igotibeci minoataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoa nigotadawaanaЙЎМ¶a modinoojetetigi anoyeligo.вҖқ  
\v 16 Pida Jesus naЙЎМ¶a igidi, meetediogi, вҖңAleeditibige doЙЎМ¶opitibeci. AkamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji ajicitiogi anoyeligo!вҖқ  
\v 17 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңIdiwa mina ciinco paontedi, idiaa itiwataale noЙЎМ¶ojedi, pida aЙЎМ¶abo!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 18 Odaa jeЙЎМ¶ee Jesus, вҖңAnadeegitediwa niЙЎМ¶icoa paontedi idiaaЙЎМ¶idioda icoa noЙЎМ¶ojedi!вҖқ  
\v 19 Odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi monicoteloco nadegocawaanigi. Odaa Jesus ja dibate niЙЎМ¶ijoa ciinco paontedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa itiwataale noЙЎМ¶ojedi. Odaa naЙЎМ¶a iwitedibigimece ditibigimedi, odaa ja diniotagodete AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. NaЙЎМ¶a ninoketedini paontedi, odaa ja yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece monediatiniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi.  
\v 20 Odaa ijotawece niodaЙЎМ¶a, codaa me nitiminaЙЎМ¶a. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oniodatece liwailidi ane iiЙЎМ¶otedice. Odaa joЙЎМ¶onoleenaЙЎМ¶adi dooze etacanitedi.  
\v 21 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noko ejinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a ijoa ciinco miili ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane niodaЙЎМ¶a, pida baadoЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi ane liwokodi iwaalepodi inaa nigaanigipawaanigi ane niodaЙЎМ¶a. 
\s1 Jesus ewaligitedeloco ditibigimedi ninyoЙЎМ¶odi 
\r (Marcos 6.45-52; JoГЈo 6.15-21) 
\p  
\v 22 AЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece mowaxoditinigi niwatece, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci daato weiigi, idaa Jesus baЙЎМ¶a nenyaЙЎМ¶atedi ibode niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi.  
\v 23 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi naЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶e mopitibeci niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi, Jesus ja dalaЙЎМ¶atetedibigimece aca wetiЙЎМ¶a migo yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mokiniwatece. EЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶ite neЙЎМ¶enoale.  
\v 24 NaЙЎМ¶aca lakata naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece ja leegita me yototice liniogotibece weiigi. Odaa ebekadi ja igike naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece, codaa naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece ja dakapetege niwocotaЙЎМ¶a. 
\p  
\v 25 AniЙЎМ¶icatibige daЙЎМ¶a yeloЙЎМ¶otibige, Jesus ja iwidatediogi, jeЙЎМ¶ewaligitedeloco ditibigimedi ninyoЙЎМ¶odi.  
\v 26 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece noЙЎМ¶onadi Jesus mewaligitedeloco ninyoЙЎМ¶odi, odaa eliodi me nawelatibigiwaji, odaa modi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina niwigo!вҖқ. Odaa ja nacaagaЙЎМ¶ateloco codaa doitibigiwaji. 
\p  
\v 27 Pida aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi Jesus meetediogi, вҖңAnipeneЙЎМ¶eni ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena! JeЙЎМ¶emeЙЎМ¶ee. JinaЙЎМ¶adoiitiwaji!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 28 Odaa Pedro meetalo, вҖңЗӨoniotagodi, nigewi naЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶akaami, enice adiiЙЎМ¶eni maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jawaligiteloco ninyoЙЎМ¶odi mejigo jakapetaЙЎМ¶agi.вҖқ  
\v 29 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eeteta, вҖңAnagi!вҖқ Odaa Pedro ja waxoditice naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece, jeЙЎМ¶ewaligiteloco ninyoЙЎМ¶odi migo midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus.  
\v 30 Pida naЙЎМ¶a nadi niocodi me yoniciwadi, odaa ja doi, ja domaЙЎМ¶a domololetini. Odaa ja dapaawe, mee, вҖңIniotagodi, jiniЙЎМ¶ikani deЙЎМ¶ee oceЙЎМ¶egi!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 31 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi Jesus ja ixoketedice libaaЙЎМ¶adi me nolitedini Pedro, odaa meeteta, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ida makaami aЙЎМ¶eliodi ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi! Igaamee ina madawieni?вҖқ \fig |src="cn01722B.tif" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Mateus 14.31" \fig* 
\v 32 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶owaxoditinigi naЙЎМ¶ajo niwatece, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niocodi ja notokoti.  
\v 33 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ideiticoace catinedi niwatece, joЙЎМ¶odiitalo Jesus modoЙЎМ¶etetalo, moditalo, вҖңDicewi makaami Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji!вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi eelotaginadi midi nipodigi GenesarГ© 
\r (Marcos 6.53-56) 
\p  
\v 34 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a diЙЎМ¶etacicoace niЙЎМ¶ijo weiigi, odaa joЙЎМ¶otota nipodigi GenesarГ©.  
\v 35 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi joЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶oditege Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶owo libodigi iditawece oko monadeegi neelotaginadi midiwataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa nipodaЙЎМ¶a anodipegitege. Odaa joЙЎМ¶onadeegitalo ijotawece ane eelotaginadi.  
\v 36 Odaa joЙЎМ¶odipokotalo mokexaa odibateloco liniogo nijayogo. Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo anodibateloco nijayogo ja nicilaЙЎМ¶a. 
\c 15  
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶ate icoa jotigide lakataЙЎМ¶a judeutedi 
\r (Marcos 7.1-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci icoa fariseutedi icaaЙЎМ¶ica anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, oicoЙЎМ¶oticogi JerusalГ©m. Igotibeci modinotigimadetege Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo,  
\v 2 вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi ina anodiotibigaЙЎМ¶adici me doЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco ЙЎМ¶odaamipi? IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶oiwilegi libaaЙЎМ¶atedi niЙЎМ¶ina me niodaЙЎМ¶a, anetiЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶axitece ЙЎМ¶odaamipi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 3 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a igidi meetediogi, вҖңEnice, igaamee ina me daЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a otetenitatiwaji liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji? IgaataЙЎМ¶a inoka iwitecetiwaji anakamaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi ane dakapetege liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 4 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji diiЙЎМ¶enataka, niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶ee, вҖҳEemiteetibige ЙЎМ¶adiodi, codaa me ЙЎМ¶adiodo.вҖҷ codaa mee, вҖҳLeeditibige moyeloadi niЙЎМ¶ina ane beyagi me dotaЙЎМ¶atibige eliodi, codaa me eliodo.вҖҷ  
\v 5 Pida akamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji baЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶axini niЙЎМ¶ina analeeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a domiЙЎМ¶ida nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me yaxawa eliodi codaa me eliodo, leeЙЎМ¶odi jaЙЎМ¶awii me lakatigi, odaa moditiogi eliododipi, вҖҳJa jajigotalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina ane inepilidi ane domaЙЎМ¶a jajigotedaЙЎМ¶awaвҖҷ,  
\v 6 LeeЙЎМ¶odi menitiogi me daЙЎМ¶alee leeditibige me deemitetibige codaa me yaxawa niЙЎМ¶ina eliododipi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ida aneni aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶otetenitiwaji ane iiЙЎМ¶etedaЙЎМ¶awa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ina me iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anitece ane ЙЎМ¶adakatigitiwaji.  
\v 7 Onawiitiwaji makaami oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a. Codaa IsaГӯas niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eetece niЙЎМ¶ina anewi, niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yalaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶awatiwaji.  
\v 8 YalaЙЎМ¶ata niЙЎМ¶ica ane ligegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, neЙЎМ¶ee, 
\q1 вҖҳNiЙЎМ¶idi noiigi odoЙЎМ¶etetiwa me notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a. 
\q1 Pida catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena aЙЎМ¶oyemaa metidowooЙЎМ¶odi. 
\q1  
\v 9 AЙЎМ¶ica niwalГі niЙЎМ¶ina modoЙЎМ¶etetiwa, 
\q1 leeЙЎМ¶odi odiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece inokinoa epaa lakataЙЎМ¶a, 
\q1 odaa aЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece ane jiiЙЎМ¶enatakata.вҖҷвҖқ 
\s1 Jesus diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atetece niЙЎМ¶ica aneo me napioi laaleЙЎМ¶ena oko 
\r (Marcos 7.14-23) 
\p  
\v 10 Jesus eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi modipegitalo, odaa meetediogi, вҖңAjipaa amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a mowooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji!  
\v 11 NiЙЎМ¶ina ane napioyaЙЎМ¶adi laaleЙЎМ¶ena oko aЙЎМ¶iniЙЎМ¶ina ane dakatiwece nioladi. Pida ane napioyaЙЎМ¶adi laaleЙЎМ¶ena oko baЙЎМ¶a ane icoЙЎМ¶otiwece nioladi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 12 Odaa joЙЎМ¶ototalo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus, odaa moditalo, вҖңAЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti niЙЎМ¶idi fariseutedi me neliЙЎМ¶ideeЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶a?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 13 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meetediogi, вҖңEiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi icota me nawace inoatawece nawodigijedi ane deЙЎМ¶eyatedini.  
\v 14 Enice jinaЙЎМ¶a agecaЙЎМ¶aleЙЎМ¶eni niЙЎМ¶idiwa fariseutedi! IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idi liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina anonibatege ЙЎМ¶oladi, pida idiaaЙЎМ¶idi aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶oladi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶a nige nibatege eledi ЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶a, odaa iditawece enitiniwace mida begi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 15 Odaa Pedro jeЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңEnice, aneloЙЎМ¶otitoЙЎМ¶owa ane diitigi niЙЎМ¶ijo natematigo anida ane iciaceekenitege.вҖқ  
\v 16 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji adaЙЎМ¶axa minoa ЙЎМ¶adixaketedi caticedi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko!  
\v 17 AЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji? NiЙЎМ¶ina ane dakatiwece nioladi oko, dakatiwece liwokomaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja noditicogi lolaadi.  
\v 18 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina ane noditicogi nioladi oko icoЙЎМ¶otiwece laaleЙЎМ¶ena. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane noditicogi catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena beЙЎМ¶eo me napioi laaleЙЎМ¶ena.  
\v 19 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko yowo niЙЎМ¶ina ane beyagi catiwedi laaleЙЎМ¶ena, odaa ja yeloadi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko, codaa loomatewa lodawa eledi oko, codaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane loomatewa ane daЙЎМ¶a lodawa, codaa dolice, codaa aneo liwitakeco, codaa ane beyagi me dotaЙЎМ¶atibige eledi oko.  
\v 20 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko nige yowo meo niЙЎМ¶ina ane beyagi, odaa laaleЙЎМ¶ena niЙЎМ¶ini oko ja napioi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina oko nige daЙЎМ¶a iwilegiteda libaaЙЎМ¶atedi anoiiЙЎМ¶axitece me lakatigi, baadaЙЎМ¶a napioyaЙЎМ¶adi laaleЙЎМ¶ena.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi liona aca iwaalo ane diЙЎМ¶ica aneetege noiigi judeu 
\r (Marcos 7.24-30) 
\p  
\v 21 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a noditedicogi niЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo ica nipodigi anipegitege nigotadi Tiro aniaa Sidom.  
\v 22 Odaa ani aca iwaalo cananГ©ia niЙЎМ¶eladimatigi niЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ipegitalo Jesus, ja dapaawe, mee, вҖңIniwa-aagodi, anida ane-eenitege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi, adiwikodeni! Niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi dakatiogi i-oona, odaa eliodi me dawikode.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 23 Pida Jesus aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a igidi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶ototalo, odaa joЙЎМ¶odipokotalo, moditalo, вҖңIiЙЎМ¶eni naЙЎМ¶ada iwaalo mopi, igaataЙЎМ¶a niotibigoЙЎМ¶odici codaa ja ЙЎМ¶odatitata niЙЎМ¶ina me dapaawetibece.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 24 Jesus meeteta naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo, вҖңAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji idiiЙЎМ¶etediogi loiigi Israel ane liciagi niЙЎМ¶inoa waxacocoli ane nabalaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 25 Odaa naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo ja diitalo, odaa ja yamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi lodoe Jesus, odaa meetalo, вҖңIniwa-aagodi, adaxawani!вҖқ  
\v 26 Odaa Jesus meeteta, вҖңAdiitigi niЙЎМ¶ina me jibanoonaЙЎМ¶atece liweenigi nigaanigawaanigi, oditaЙЎМ¶a jokolenaЙЎМ¶atiogi necexodi.вҖқ  
\v 27 Odaa ja igidi naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo, meetalo, вҖңEwi, Iniwa-aagodi! Pida codaa me necexodawaanaЙЎМ¶a oyeligo latijedi niwe-eenigi ane icoЙЎМ¶otibigimece nameeja niwikateenoЙЎМ¶odi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 28 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meeteta, вҖңIwaalo, niЙЎМ¶ida makaami eliodi ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi. NiЙЎМ¶ida anemaani ja jao.вҖқ Odaa acaaЙЎМ¶aca naЙЎМ¶aca lakata naЙЎМ¶ajo liona ja icГӯ. 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi eliodi eelotaginadi 
\p  
\v 29 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a noditedicogi niЙЎМ¶ijo aneite, odaa joЙЎМ¶opitacedicogi lipecaЙЎМ¶adi niweiigi GalilГ©ia. Odaa ja dalaЙЎМ¶atetedibigimece ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja nicotedini.  
\v 30 Odaa eliodi oko joЙЎМ¶odiitalo, oyadeegi aЙЎМ¶atiloЙЎМ¶oladi, alejaadotedi, ЙЎМ¶oladi, ina ewaloЙЎМ¶onadi, codaa mowidi eletidi eelotaginadi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶oyadeegiticogi lodoe Jesus, odaa ijotawece ja nicilatiditediniwace.  
\v 31 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi eliodi moyopo noЙЎМ¶onadi naЙЎМ¶a notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa ewaloЙЎМ¶onadi, alejaadotedi naЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a nicilaЙЎМ¶a, ane doЙЎМ¶oyakadi mewaligitibigiwaji neЙЎМ¶ewaligitibigiwaji, codaa me ЙЎМ¶oladi yatetibigiwaji. Odaa joЙЎМ¶odoЙЎМ¶etetibigimece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, NoenoЙЎМ¶odi loiigi Israel. 
\s1 Jesus niodeЙЎМ¶etedini cwaatolo miili ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi 
\r (Marcos 8.1-10) 
\p  
\v 32 Jesus eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa meetediogi, вҖңEliodi me jiwikode niЙЎМ¶ina oko, igaataЙЎМ¶a jeЙЎМ¶eote itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi mina meetaЙЎМ¶a, odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica gaantokaaЙЎМ¶idi anoyeligo. Ajemaa daЙЎМ¶a jiiЙЎМ¶etibigiwaji mopitibeci daaditiЙЎМ¶icata ane jajigotiogi me jiniodeЙЎМ¶etiniwace, igaataЙЎМ¶a doidetibige diЙЎМ¶ica ane noЙЎМ¶omiwaditiniwace leeЙЎМ¶odi nabocaЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶opiticogi liЙЎМ¶elatedi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 33 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oige Jesus, moditalo, вҖңIgametaЙЎМ¶a jakataЙЎМ¶a ica niweenigi nelegi me jiniodeЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atiniwace iditawece niЙЎМ¶idi oko digoina minataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina nipodigi ane diЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 34 Odaa ja nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңIgame liwokodi ЙЎМ¶anipaontedi anidiwa?вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңIdiwa seete paontedi idiaaЙЎМ¶idiwa noЙЎМ¶ojedawaanaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 35 Odaa Jesus ja iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi monicotinigiiЙЎМ¶o.  
\v 36 Odaa ja dibate niЙЎМ¶ijoa seete paontedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa noЙЎМ¶ojedawaanaЙЎМ¶a, naЙЎМ¶a diniotagodetedibigimece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa ja ninoketedini, odaa ja yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece monediatiniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi.  
\v 37 Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi niodaЙЎМ¶a, neЙЎМ¶epaa nitiminaЙЎМ¶a. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶onioda niЙЎМ¶ijoa liwailidi ane iiЙЎМ¶otedice, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyetigilo seete etacanitedi nelecoli.  
\v 38 NiЙЎМ¶ica noko ejinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a cwaatolo miili ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane niodaЙЎМ¶a, we iwaalepodi, inaa nigaanigipawaanigi anaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niodaЙЎМ¶a, pida baadoЙЎМ¶onilaaЙЎМ¶aditibigiwaji. 
\p  
\v 39 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus ja imonya niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi mopitibeci, odaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a waxoditedinigi niwatece, jiЙЎМ¶igo midiwa nipodaЙЎМ¶a MagadГЈ. 
\c 16  
\s1 Icoa lacilodi judeutedi domoЙЎМ¶oyemaa Jesus meote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi ane ikee me liiЙЎМ¶exegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji 
\r (Marcos 8.11-13; Lucas 12.54-56) 
\p  
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa saduceutedi joЙЎМ¶ototalo Jesus. Odineetalo, domoЙЎМ¶owo moyakadi gaantiЙЎМ¶idi ane niwokotedini, odaa ja domaЙЎМ¶a nilaagedi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi modipokotalo meote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi ane ikee me liiЙЎМ¶exegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 2 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina naЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶ocidi me ixagodi loolatedi, odaa menitiwaji, вҖҳNatiinigoi adatiode, leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶ocidi diticetinece.вҖҷ  
\v 3 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina nigoi me ixagoditege codaa me nexocaЙЎМ¶a ditibigimedi, odaa menitiwaji, вҖҳDatiode, leeЙЎМ¶odi loolatedi ixagodi me nabidi.вҖҷ Odaa boЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji domige datiode, oЙЎМ¶oa domige adatiode, niЙЎМ¶ina mawinitibigimecetiwaji ditibigimedi. Pida baadoЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ica ane diitigi niЙЎМ¶ina manati ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi ane jaote.  
\v 4 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko aninaa niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a codaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶onakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aЙЎМ¶eote eledi ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi ane ikeetiogi me idiiЙЎМ¶e. JeЙЎМ¶eote niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶edi ane ikee me idiiЙЎМ¶e, niЙЎМ¶ijo me ideyate Jonas catiwedi le niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶ojegi nelegi itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi.вҖқ Odaa Jesus ja yototedicoace, joЙЎМ¶opi. 
\s1 Ica nabookojedi fariseutedi ijaa saduceutedi 
\r (Marcos 8.14-21) 
\p  
\v 5 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a diiЙЎМ¶etita daato weiigi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, oyaagiditece doЙЎМ¶oyadeegi paontedi.  
\v 6 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңAtacolitiwaji codaa anidakita nabookojedi fariseutedi inaa saduceutedi!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 7 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶odinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etigi niЙЎМ¶ida aneete, modi, вҖңEote niЙЎМ¶ida ligegi leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶icoa me inadeegaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶onipaontedi.вҖқ  
\v 8 Pida Jesus ja yowooЙЎМ¶odi ane lotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңIgaamee ina madinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶enitigitiwaji me diЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶anipaon? Ame iwaЙЎМ¶atitetiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji!  
\v 9 AnoЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji? NaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adaagititibige ijoa ciinco paontedi ane jatikatalo me jiniodeЙЎМ¶etiniwace ciinco miili ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa etacanitedi ane nolee niЙЎМ¶ijoa liwailidi ane iiЙЎМ¶otedice?  
\v 10 Codaa naЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adaagititibigetiwaji ijoa seete paontedi ane jatikatalo me jiniodeЙЎМ¶etiniwace cwaatolo miili ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa etacanitedi nelecoli ane nolee niЙЎМ¶ijoa liwailidi ane iiЙЎМ¶otedice?  
\v 11 AЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji me daЙЎМ¶a idalaЙЎМ¶ata paon niЙЎМ¶ijo me ЙЎМ¶adajacaЙЎМ¶atitiwaji manidakita nabookojedi fariseutedi idiaa saduceutedi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 12 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi Jesus me daЙЎМ¶a yalaЙЎМ¶ate modinidakata paon labookojedi, pida modinidakata liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco fariseutedi ijaa saduceutedi. 
\s1 Pedro mee Jesus niЙЎМ¶iniaaЙЎМ¶iniwa NiЙЎМ¶icoa ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote me ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶atace 
\r (Marcos 8.27-30; Lucas 9.18-21) 
\p  
\v 13 Jesus igo nipodaЙЎМ¶a anipegitege nigotaЙЎМ¶a, ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңCesarГ©ia Filipe ane dabiteЙЎМ¶etiniвҖқ. JiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶i naЙЎМ¶a nigetediniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, meetediogi, вҖңEe, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, odaa ame Ee modi ina oko?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 14 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңInatecibece modi makaami JoГЈo Batista, codaa inatecibece eledi modi makaami Elias. Codaa ina eledi modi makaami Jeremias, oЙЎМ¶oa, domige anigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 15 Odaa Jesus ja digika, meetediogi, вҖңBiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji, amakati me Ee?вҖқ  
\v 16 SimГЈo Pedro naЙЎМ¶a igidi, meetalo, вҖңJaЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶akaami ane iiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЙЎМ¶odewikatiteЙЎМ¶egi. Akaami Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anidioka limedi me yewiЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 17 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meeteta, вҖңAniniitibeci niЙЎМ¶ida makaami SimГЈo, anakaami lionigi JoГЈo, leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶oko anoikeetaЙЎМ¶awa ane Ee, pida Eiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi ikeetedaЙЎМ¶awa ane Ee.  
\v 18 Natigide jao gela ЙЎМ¶aboonaЙЎМ¶adi akaami Pedro (leeЙЎМ¶odi niitege niЙЎМ¶ina mejinaЙЎМ¶a wetiЙЎМ¶a). Odaa ЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶a me ЙЎМ¶adalakitiwa liciagi naЙЎМ¶ana wetiЙЎМ¶a anodatika moyoe lipodaЙЎМ¶aladi diimigi. Odaa ja jao niЙЎМ¶ina oko anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶a me micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina diimigi ane dabiteЙЎМ¶eteloco niЙЎМ¶ina noenatagodi ditibigimedi wetiЙЎМ¶a ane ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶e. Odaa oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a nГ©maЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica loniciwaЙЎМ¶ateloco niЙЎМ¶idi oko.  
\v 19 Codaa jajigotaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi me iiЙЎМ¶eni niЙЎМ¶ina oko anida anejitege, micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko anida lakabakenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶adi ane dowediteloco diimigi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ica anoliitege digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yolitetege. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ica anikani mowo niЙЎМ¶ina oko digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ika.вҖқ  
\v 20 Odaa Jesus ja dipokotediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece me doЙЎМ¶oyeloЙЎМ¶oditiogi niЙЎМ¶ina oko me NiЙЎМ¶ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a. 
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶ate me yeleo pida yewiЙЎМ¶atace nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi 
\r (Marcos 8.31вҖ“9.1; Lucas 9.22-27) 
\p  
\v 21 Odaa joaniЙЎМ¶ijaaЙЎМ¶ijotigi niЙЎМ¶ijo noko Jesus jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eyatedigi me yeloЙЎМ¶oditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece me leeditibige migo manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, codaa me leeditibige meliodi me dawikode libaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶icoa laxokodi lacilodi noiigi judeutedi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s. Codaa me leeditibige me yeleo, pida nige ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi, odaa ja yewiЙЎМ¶atace.  
\v 22 Odaa Pedro ja yadeegitedice Jesus me yapeteЙЎМ¶e, meetalo, вҖңAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶adiwikodeni, odaa aika daЙЎМ¶awikodee, ЗӨoniotagodi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 23 Odaa Jesus ja niwiteta Pedro, odaa meete, вҖңOtonitice yodoe, SatanГЎs! DomaЙЎМ¶a adibeyacaЙЎМ¶ati macataЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ana wetiЙЎМ¶a ane itinece naigi ane ixipe oko, leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶adowoocaЙЎМ¶awa niЙЎМ¶ina oko, pida aЙЎМ¶adowoocaЙЎМ¶awa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 24 Odaa Jesus meetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, вҖңNigica ane yemaa me niotici, leeditibige me daЙЎМ¶adiaa iniokini me dinowo, codaa leeditibige me igotema me diniwikodetibece, codaa me dawikode nigepaa yeleo, odaa ja niotici.  
\v 25 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane yemaa minoka yewiЙЎМ¶ateloco niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, aЙЎМ¶ica lewiЙЎМ¶a ane diЙЎМ¶ica liniogo, pida niЙЎМ¶ina baanaЙЎМ¶a igo me yeleotomi, niЙЎМ¶ini oko baanaЙЎМ¶a ida lewiЙЎМ¶a ane diЙЎМ¶ica liniogo.  
\v 26 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko nige yakadi inoatawece ane yopotibige digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, pida odaa liwigo baЙЎМ¶a ika me yeleo, niЙЎМ¶ini oko aЙЎМ¶ica anigetiЙЎМ¶ida nigaanye. IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ica anigetiЙЎМ¶idi liboonigi me dedianaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko oditaЙЎМ¶a eo lewiЙЎМ¶a liwigo.  
\v 27 LeeЙЎМ¶odi Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, idopitijo anigida noko idiaa iniaanjotedi, codaa loniciwaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane Eiodi, idei meetaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa ja jiwi ane loenataka inatawece oko, codaa jajigotiogi niЙЎМ¶ica loojedi ane loenataka ane beyagi, oЙЎМ¶oa, domige anele.  
\v 28 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. Ina oko digoina analee daЙЎМ¶a nigo nigetidadi me janagi me Ee inionigi-eliodi ane iiЙЎМ¶e oko laaleЙЎМ¶enali.вҖқ 
\c 17  
\s1 Jesus diniigi anodaaЙЎМ¶eeteda naЙЎМ¶a dakapetetege MoisГ©s ijaa Elias 
\r (Marcos 9.2-13; Lucas 9.28-36) 
\p  
\v 1 NaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo seis nokododi, Jesus ja yadeegi Pedro, Tiago ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo nioxoa anodita JoГЈo, idiokidi niЙЎМ¶idi itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida anodiotibece me yadeegi. Odaa ja yadeegitedicogi maditaЙЎМ¶a aca wetiЙЎМ¶a ane leegitibigimece, ane diЙЎМ¶ica oko.  
\v 2 Odaa noЙЎМ¶oiwitalo, joЙЎМ¶onadi Jesus me diniigi idoatawece, latobi ja datale macataЙЎМ¶a aligeЙЎМ¶e, lowoodi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yapacaЙЎМ¶a me datale.  
\v 3 CodaaЙЎМ¶ida noЙЎМ¶onadi me dinikee MoisГ©s ijaa Elias, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e Jesus.  
\v 4 Odaa Pedro jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a dotaЙЎМ¶a, meetalo Jesus, вҖңIca mele minaaЙЎМ¶ejonaЙЎМ¶a, ЗӨoniotagodi. Nigemaani, jaote iniwatadiЙЎМ¶ini nopecetiidi, oniniteci ЙЎМ¶anebi, iniaaЙЎМ¶eledi MoisГ©s nebi, iniaaЙЎМ¶eledi baЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a Elias nebi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 5 EЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee Pedro me dotaЙЎМ¶a, ica lolaadi ane datale ja yapoЙЎМ¶oditiniwace Jesus, MoisГ©s ijaa Elias. Odaa joЙЎМ¶owajipata ica notaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi catiwedi lolaadi, anee, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idoa Ionigi yemaanigi, aneliodi meote me idinitibeci. Atacolitecetiwaji niЙЎМ¶inoa lotaЙЎМ¶a!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶owajipata niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo ane dotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja dakagitiniwace oyatedini iiЙЎМ¶o latopidi, leeЙЎМ¶odi eliodi me doitibigiwaji.  
\v 7 Odaa Jesus ja diitediogi, naЙЎМ¶a dibatedeloco, meetediogi, вҖңAdabititiniwacetiwaji, codaa jinaЙЎМ¶adoii!вҖқ  
\v 8 Odaa naЙЎМ¶a noletibigimoace, noЙЎМ¶oiwitalo, aЙЎМ¶ica anigetiЙЎМ¶ijo eledi anonadi, idokidoateda Jesus monadi. 
\p  
\v 9 NaЙЎМ¶a daxoditiniwace naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a, Jesus ja yajoi niЙЎМ¶ijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida anodiotibece, meetediogi, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶a domiЙЎМ¶ica aneloЙЎМ¶ititatiwaji ananati maditaЙЎМ¶a wetiЙЎМ¶a nigepaa idewiЙЎМ¶atace, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 10 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo, вҖңIgaamee ijo anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s modi menagi Elias maleediЙЎМ¶ica meno NiЙЎМ¶icoa ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meo me ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶atace?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 11 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meetediogi, вҖңEwi niЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee Elias menagi maleediЙЎМ¶ica NiЙЎМ¶ijoa ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meo oko me newiЙЎМ¶atace. Elias enagi me ilakidetedice inoatawece.  
\v 12 Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji Elias jiЙЎМ¶ijo menagi, codaa ЙЎМ¶odacilodi aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi, odaa joЙЎМ¶owotema niЙЎМ¶ica anoyemaa modigota. Odaa idaaЙЎМ¶odigotiwa owo me jawikode, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi.вҖқ  
\v 13 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi Jesus me yalaЙЎМ¶ate JoГЈo Batista niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a yalaЙЎМ¶ate Elias. 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi ica lioneeЙЎМ¶a 
\r (Marcos 9.14-29; Lucas 9.37-43) 
\p  
\v 14 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a diitacediogi niЙЎМ¶ica noiigi-nelegi lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi niЙЎМ¶ijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida anodiotibece, odaa ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa jiЙЎМ¶ipegitalo Jesus. NaЙЎМ¶a yamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi lodoe Jesus, odaa meetalo,  
\v 15 вҖңIniotagodi, iwikodeni ionigi! ЗӨatiЙЎМ¶alegi, odaa eliodi me dawikode, elioditibece menitibiga, odaa enitiogi noledi, codaa idatibece daxaboketinigi ninyoЙЎМ¶odi.  
\v 16 Ja inadeegitiogi niЙЎМ¶idi anodiotibigaЙЎМ¶adici, pida joЙЎМ¶oyapi moicilatidi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 17 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңJodaЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ica noiigi ane doЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa akamaЙЎМ¶a adininaalenitiwaji. NiЙЎМ¶ida me Ee aleegi minaaЙЎМ¶ejo makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji, codaa ajakadi deЙЎМ¶eliodi me idinatitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji. Anadeegitiwa niЙЎМ¶ica lioneeЙЎМ¶a!вҖқ  
\v 18 NoЙЎМ¶onadeegitalo, odaa Jesus ja yapeteЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ica niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi, codaa iiЙЎМ¶e me noditice. Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi, niЙЎМ¶ica niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi ja noditice mijotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo lioneeЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja icГӯ. 
\p  
\v 19 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus joЙЎМ¶odiitalo noЙЎМ¶okaaniЙЎМ¶idoatece, odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo, вҖңIgaamee ina daЙЎМ¶a jakataЙЎМ¶a me jiticodaЙЎМ¶atice ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi?вҖқ  
\v 20 Odaa ja igidi Jesus, meetediogi, вҖңAЙЎМ¶akatitiwaji miticoitice niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo ane beyagi leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶eliodi manakatoni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. DoЙЎМ¶okateciЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶atiwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, macataЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ana lolagi вҖҳmostaadaвҖҷ ane daЙЎМ¶axa me lionawaana, taЙЎМ¶akatitiwaji me enita naЙЎМ¶ani wetiЙЎМ¶a, вҖҳOtonitice, emii digoida!вҖҷ Odaa wetiЙЎМ¶a ja alatГӯ. AЙЎМ¶ica ane apini mawii, nige iwaЙЎМ¶ati AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 21 Pida okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niwigo liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo niwigo abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi noditice idokidata nigotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa nige ikanawaanigi maniodi moleetibige meneЙЎМ¶egi otaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶atace ica me yeleo pida yewiЙЎМ¶atace nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi 
\r (Marcos 9.30-32; Lucas 9.43-45) 
\p  
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶ica me yatecoЙЎМ¶o niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece midi nipodigi GalilГ©ia, Jesus meetediogi, вҖңEtidajigota libaaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi.  
\v 23 Odaa etideloadi, pida nige ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi, odaa ja idewiЙЎМ¶atace.вҖқ NiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece eliodi magecaЙЎМ¶alodipi noЙЎМ¶owajipatalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a. 
\s1 Icoa dinyeelo ane leeditibige me dinajigo mini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi 
\p  
\v 24 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece noЙЎМ¶ototicogi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Cafarnaum, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane oniodatema ninyeelo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, joЙЎМ¶otota Pedro, odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, modita, вҖңIdoa ЙЎМ¶aniotagodi domige yajigo dinyeelo ane leeditibige me yajigo minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi?вҖқ  
\v 25 Odaa Pedro ja igidi, meetiogi, вҖңYedia.вҖқ Odaa ja dakatiwece diimigi. Pida aniЙЎМ¶icatibige daЙЎМ¶a dotaЙЎМ¶a Pedro, niЙЎМ¶ijapaЙЎМ¶a odoejegi me dotaЙЎМ¶a Jesus, odaa ja ige, meete, вҖңSimГЈo, amiida ЙЎМ¶adowoogo? EtiЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶e me jajicaЙЎМ¶atiogi dinyeelo niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odaciloditigi niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o. Pida amiijo ica ane dedianaЙЎМ¶a? Domigepaa loiigi nedianaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, oЙЎМ¶oa, domigina anokegipi anoicoЙЎМ¶oticogi eletidi nipodaЙЎМ¶a?вҖқ  
\v 26 Odaa Pedro ja igidi, meetalo, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶inoa icoЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a boЙЎМ¶oyedia.вҖқ Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eete, вҖңOdaa niЙЎМ¶ida moko anoko loiigi ame leeditibige me jedianaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 27 Pida aЙЎМ¶ele daЙЎМ¶a jaoЙЎМ¶a me neliЙЎМ¶ideeЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idi anetiЙЎМ¶odipiciadi. Natigide, emii miditaЙЎМ¶a weiigi, odaa okolenitini ЙЎМ¶adomiigo. Odaa okeni niЙЎМ¶ica odoejegi noЙЎМ¶ojegi ane ixigi ЙЎМ¶adomiigo. Odaa catiwedi nioladi akati beexo. Odaa anadeegi naЙЎМ¶ani beexo, ediani niЙЎМ¶ica ane leeditibige me jedianaЙЎМ¶a mini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi. NaЙЎМ¶ani beexo abotema mediani codaa ane leeditibige maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jedia.вҖқ 
\c 18  
\s1 NiЙЎМ¶ica ane daЙЎМ¶axa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi liwigotigi oko ane iiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji 
\r (Marcos 9.33-37; Lucas 9.46-48) 
\p  
\v 1 Jesus eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeteda me yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e Pedro, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo, вҖңAmiina ica oko ane ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi ina naЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji laaleЙЎМ¶enali ina oko?вҖқ  
\v 2 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶enidite ijo nigaanigawaanigi, jiЙЎМ¶ideyate liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece. \fig |src="cn01772B.tif" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Mateus 18.2" \fig* 
\v 3 Odaa meetediogi, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. Nige daЙЎМ¶a iigitiwaji aneni me ЙЎМ¶adewiki, codaa nige daЙЎМ¶adiniwikodenitibece micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ini nigaanigawaanigi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aiiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enalitiwaji, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica anenitege.  
\v 4 Enice, niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane diniwikodetibece, codaa aneo me liciagi niЙЎМ¶ida nigaanigawaanigi, baaniЙЎМ¶iniaa eneЙЎМ¶egi ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi liwigotigi noiigi anida aneetetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 5 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina anele me dibatege niЙЎМ¶ina nigaanigawaanigi liciagi anejigo me jibatege niЙЎМ¶idoda nigaanigawaanigi, codaa nige dibatege leeЙЎМ¶odi IboonaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ini oko dibatigi. 
\s1 Leeditibige me jikanaЙЎМ¶a ane ЙЎМ¶odibeyacaЙЎМ¶adi me jakaЙЎМ¶atiwece miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji 
\r (Marcos 9.42-48; Lucas 17.1-2) 
\p  
\v 6 Nigica aneo anigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ina nigaanigipawaanigi me ika me idinakato, domaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mele moigoetece lotoinaЙЎМ¶adi naЙЎМ¶ana wetiЙЎМ¶a nelegi, oditaЙЎМ¶a oyokoletinigi akiidi-eliodi moyoceЙЎМ¶atidi, maleedeЙЎМ¶eo niЙЎМ¶ida loenatagi ane beyagi.  
\v 7 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko anida aneetege niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o icota meliodi me nawikodeeЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶inoa loenataka ane beyagi anowo eledi oko moika moyiwaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. NiЙЎМ¶inoa anodineetoЙЎМ¶owa idioka limedi minoa, pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icota meote meliodi me nawikodeeЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko aneo eledi oko moika moyiwaЙЎМ¶adi. 
\p  
\v 8 NiЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶adi, idaa ЙЎМ¶adoЙЎМ¶onagi nigowo mabataa, leeditibige maloikatiti ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶adi, codaa me ЙЎМ¶adoЙЎМ¶onagi micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶akagiti, oditaЙЎМ¶a alati. IgaataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mele mokidatece ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶adi, domigetaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adoЙЎМ¶onagi, pida akati makaatiwece miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa idioka limedi me ЙЎМ¶adewiki. AЙЎМ¶ele diЙЎМ¶idoatawece ЙЎМ¶abaaЙЎМ¶atedi, ЙЎМ¶adoЙЎМ¶onaka, pida etiЙЎМ¶adokolenitiogi noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe.  
\v 9 ЗӨagecooЙЎМ¶e nigeo mabataa, aloikatiti, micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a anoЙЎМ¶aa, odaaЙЎМ¶alati. IgaataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mele makaatiwece miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa idioka limedi me ЙЎМ¶adewiki mokanitece ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶e. AЙЎМ¶ele diЙЎМ¶idiwatawece ЙЎМ¶agecooЙЎМ¶eli, pida etiЙЎМ¶adokolenitiogi noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe. 
\s1 Aca waxacoco ananiadi 
\r (Lucas 15.3-7) 
\p  
\v 10 Anidakitatiwaji adaЙЎМ¶aleetibige daatiЙЎМ¶ica ane jaoЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoda nigaanigipawaanigi. EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶icoa aanjotedi anodowediteloco niЙЎМ¶ina nigaanigipawaanigi idioka limedi midi lodoe Eiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi.  
\v 11 IgaataЙЎМ¶a Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, janagi me jopilaЙЎМ¶aditacalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina aniatagigipi. 
\p  
\v 12 Amiida ica anakatitecetiwaji? DiЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa anidiwa onaniteci taalia niwaxacocoli, oditaЙЎМ¶a jaЙЎМ¶aca aniadi. Odaa amigetiЙЎМ¶ida anee? EjitaЙЎМ¶awa me yoya niЙЎМ¶idiwa noventa-noove waxacocoli madi wetiЙЎМ¶a anei me nadecoЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo doletibige naЙЎМ¶ajo ananiaditibige. \fig |src="BK00005B.TIF" size="span" copy="Horace Knowles revised by Louise Bass В© The British & Foreign Bible Society, 1994." ref="Mateus 18.12" \fig* 
\v 13 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ina nige yakadi, eliodi me ninitibece, leeЙЎМ¶odi me yakadi naЙЎМ¶ajo niwaxacoco, odaa daЙЎМ¶axa me ninitibece, caticedi linikegitema niЙЎМ¶ijoa noventa-noove ane daЙЎМ¶aniaditeda.  
\v 14 JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee ЗӨadioditetiwaji aneite ditibigimedi, ayemaa me aniatagigi anigeteЙЎМ¶epidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ina oko anonakato ane micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina nigaanigawaanigi meyiwaЙЎМ¶adi eliodi. 
\s1 Ica ЙЎМ¶onioxoa ane dibatГЎ 
\p  
\v 15 Nige dibatГЎ ЙЎМ¶anioxoa, eotaЙЎМ¶adomi ane beyagi, emii minitaЙЎМ¶a mokakaamitece, ikeenita ane libatiigi. Nige niwoditaЙЎМ¶adomi, jaЙЎМ¶anigaanyetece ЙЎМ¶anioxoa.  
\v 16 Pida nige daЙЎМ¶a niwoditaЙЎМ¶adomi, odaa adeegi eletidi itoa oЙЎМ¶oa domige itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶adixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶enitiwaji, awii aneeta AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a. IgaataЙЎМ¶a mee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, вҖҳNiЙЎМ¶ina nigica oko ane yeloЙЎМ¶odita eledi oko libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, leeditibige eletidi itoa oЙЎМ¶oa domige itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida oko midokida ane ligegi.вҖҷ  
\v 17 Pida nige daЙЎМ¶a niwoditema niЙЎМ¶idi oko, enice leeditibige eleЙЎМ¶enitiogi niЙЎМ¶idi lapo anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi ЗӨoniotagodi. Odaa nige daЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a wajipatiogi niЙЎМ¶idi lapo anoyiwaЙЎМ¶adi ЗӨoniotagodi, odaa ademii niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶anioxoa micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane deЙЎМ¶eyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa me laxokegi abataЙЎМ¶a, codaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica anenitege. 
\s1 Ica niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi ane yoli, codaa me ika anigica 
\p  
\v 18 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. OkanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica anoliitegetiwaji digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yolitetege. Codaa okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica anikanitiwaji midaЙЎМ¶aee digoina iiЙЎМ¶o, ЗӨadiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ika midaЙЎМ¶aee.  
\v 19 AaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, nigidi iniwataale niЙЎМ¶ina akaamitiwaji digoina iiЙЎМ¶o ane dinilakidetiwage odaa idokida ane lipoketegi niЙЎМ¶ina moyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e Eiodi, odaa Eiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi jeЙЎМ¶eote niЙЎМ¶ica ane lipoketegi.  
\v 20 IgaataЙЎМ¶a diЙЎМ¶idiwa iniwataale, domige iniwatadiЙЎМ¶ini oko ane yatecoЙЎМ¶o moiweniЙЎМ¶ide IboonaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa idejo miditaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\s1 Natematigigi ica niotagi ane daЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice naalewe eledi niotagi 
\p  
\v 21 Odaa Pedro jiЙЎМ¶icotalo Jesus, ja ige, meetalo, вҖңIniotagodi, igame liwokodi me leeditibige me jixomaЙЎМ¶ateetice inioxoa libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco aneotomi? Domige leeditibige nigepaa seete me jixomaЙЎМ¶ateetice libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco inioxoa?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 22 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a igidi, meeteta, вҖңAЙЎМ¶okexaa seete me ixomaЙЎМ¶ateenitice libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco ЙЎМ¶anioxoa aneotaЙЎМ¶adomi. Pida leeditibige midioka limedi me ixomaЙЎМ¶ateenitice libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco ЙЎМ¶anioxoa aneotaЙЎМ¶adomi, aleeditibige daЙЎМ¶a anilaЙЎМ¶ati. 
\p  
\v 23 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e oko laaleЙЎМ¶enali, eote liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina inionigi-eliodi ane lowoogo me ilakidetedini naalewe liotagipi.  
\v 24 NiЙЎМ¶ina naЙЎМ¶a dinilakidetege, jonoЙЎМ¶onadeegita ica liotagi ane dinaalewe deez miili icoa beexotedi oolo.  
\v 25 AЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me yedia niЙЎМ¶ijoa naaleweli anowidi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagodi ja domaЙЎМ¶a diiЙЎМ¶enataka niЙЎМ¶ijo liotagi moyaa dioteci lodawa, lionigipi, moiwotagetibigiwaji, codaa moyaa idiwatawece ane nepilidi me yedianawaanigi naalewe.  
\v 26 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagi ja yamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi lodoe niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagodi, odaa ja dipokota, meeta, вҖҳAliitatiwa, jedianoda idiwatawece ane inaalewetaЙЎМ¶awa anigida noko.вҖҷ  
\v 27 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagodi eliodi me iwikode, odaa ja ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice niЙЎМ¶ijoa naalewe, codaa ikatice mopi. 
\p  
\v 28 Pida ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagi naЙЎМ¶a noditice, odaa ja dakapetege ica eledi liotagi inionigi-eliodi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo eledi niotagi baЙЎМ¶a dinaalewe onexaa onateciЙЎМ¶idiwa beexotedi naaleweta niЙЎМ¶ijo odoejegi niotagi anowidi naalewe. Pida dibatigi lotoinaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa ja iligice, meeta, вҖҳYokaaЙЎМ¶edi adediani niЙЎМ¶ijoa anadinaalewe!вҖҷ  
\v 29 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lokaaЙЎМ¶edi ja yamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi, odaa ja dipokota, meeta, вҖҳAliitatiwa, odaa icota me ЙЎМ¶adediani idiodatawece ane inaalewetaЙЎМ¶awa.вҖҷ  
\v 30 Pida ayemaa me ixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice, odaa ja yadeegi niЙЎМ¶ijo lokaaЙЎМ¶edi mani niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi midiaaЙЎМ¶i nigepaa yediatelogo ane naalewe.  
\v 31 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶onadi eletidi niotaka niЙЎМ¶ida niciagi, eliodi me agecaЙЎМ¶alodipi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci oyeloЙЎМ¶odita niotagodi, inionigi-eliodi.  
\v 32 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagodi jeЙЎМ¶enidita niЙЎМ¶ijo liotagi anowidi naalewe, odaa meeta, вҖҳEjinaЙЎМ¶a akamaЙЎМ¶akaami niЙЎМ¶ica nimeedi ane daЙЎМ¶axa me agopeloagi! Ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa dinyeelo owidi ane adinaaleweeni jixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedice leeЙЎМ¶odi manipokitiwa.  
\v 33 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ida makaami leeditibige me iwikodeni ЙЎМ¶adokaaЙЎМ¶edi, digo anejigotaЙЎМ¶awa me ЙЎМ¶adiwikodeni.вҖҷ  
\v 34 NiЙЎМ¶ijo niotagodi eliodi me yelatema, odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶eticogi niЙЎМ¶ijo limeedi mani niwiloЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶axi moiloikatidi nigepaa yedia icoatawece ane naalewe.  
\v 35 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a igotedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji Eiodi ane ideite ditibigimedi nige deЙЎМ¶ewi mixomaЙЎМ¶ateenitedicetiwaji anowotaЙЎМ¶adomi ane beyagi ЙЎМ¶anioxoadipi.вҖқ 
\c 19  
\s1 Jesus diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atetece lalataЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi wadonadi 
\r (Marcos 10.1-12) 
\p  
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a ika me diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja noditedicogi nipodigi GalilГ©ia, odaa joЙЎМ¶opitacedicogi liwai nipodigi JudГ©ia, daato akiidi JordГЈo.  
\v 2 Eliodi oko anodiotece, odaa nicilatiditedini eelotaginadi. 
\p  
\v 3 Icoa fariseutedi igotibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus modineetalo meote ligegi ane beyagi. Odaa moditalo, вҖңЗӨonajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco domige oika ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me yaladi lodawa mokanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ane leeЙЎМ¶odi?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 4 Odaa Jesus ja igidi, meetediogi, вҖңIca ina daaditiЙЎМ¶ica malomeЙЎМ¶eniteloco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, miditaЙЎМ¶a anee, вҖҳMaleekoka yoeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, odaa ja yoe oko, ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa aniaaЙЎМ¶iwaalo.вҖҷ  
\v 5 Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mee, вҖҳJoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me ikaticoace eliododipi, odaa ja noiigiwa lodawa, odaa niЙЎМ¶idi iniwataale ja micataЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶okinitece oko.вҖҷ  
\v 6 Odaa aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶iniwataale, pida oneniЙЎМ¶initeci. Enice aЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane yakadi me yawalaceticoace niЙЎМ¶ina ane yexocaЙЎМ¶aditediwage AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 7 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi moditalo, вҖңEnice, igame leeЙЎМ¶odi MoisГ©s me iiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me yakadi me iticoitice lodawa nige yajigota naЙЎМ¶ani lodawa notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi ane ikee naЙЎМ¶a yaladi?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 8 Jesus ja igidi, meetediogi, вҖңMoisГ©s ЙЎМ¶adikanitiwaji malati ЙЎМ¶adodawa leeЙЎМ¶odi me dakake ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo maleekoka yoeteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa aniaaЙЎМ¶iwaalo, aniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee.  
\v 9 Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji nigica ane yaladi lodawa, odaa ja lodawa eledi iwaalo, niЙЎМ¶ini ja doЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶ataka. Codaa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane lodawa naЙЎМ¶ana baanaЙЎМ¶a dalataЙЎМ¶a jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶ataka. NiЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa idoka yakadi me yaladi naЙЎМ¶ana lodawa niЙЎМ¶ina nige doЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶ataka naЙЎМ¶ani iwaalo.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 10 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus moditalo, вҖңNige niЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee, dice daЙЎМ¶axa mele niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me daЙЎМ¶a wado.вҖқ  
\v 11 NaЙЎМ¶a igidi Jesus, meetediogi, вҖңAЙЎМ¶inatawece oko oyakadi modibatege niЙЎМ¶ida iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi aneetece nadoneЙЎМ¶egi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ida niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi inokina niЙЎМ¶ina ane yakadi modibatege niЙЎМ¶ida niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi.  
\v 12 IgaataЙЎМ¶a initibece ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa awado leeЙЎМ¶odi ida ane ibeyacaЙЎМ¶adi. Inoatecibece ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi aЙЎМ¶ica lionigi, leeЙЎМ¶odi mina lakatigi. Pida jiЙЎМ¶inatibece eledi aЙЎМ¶ica lionigi leeЙЎМ¶odi me noЙЎМ¶aligijedi. Pida inatecibece eledi mina aЙЎМ¶oyemaa me nadonaЙЎМ¶a oditaЙЎМ¶a eniododipi, leeЙЎМ¶odi moyemaa mowo libakedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, moyatematitibece anodaaЙЎМ¶ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko. Ane yakadi me dibatege niЙЎМ¶ida iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi, ele me dibatege!вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus ibinietediogi ica nigaanigipawaanigi 
\r (Marcos 10.13-16; Lucas 18.15-17) 
\p  
\v 13 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi joЙЎМ¶oyadeegitalo Jesus ica nigaanigipawaanigi me ipeketedeloco libaaЙЎМ¶atedi me dipokotedeloco me ibinietediogi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece oyapeteЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo anonadeegi nigaanigipawaanigi.  
\v 14 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңIkani menagitibeci meetaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶inoda nigaanigipawaanigi, jinoЙЎМ¶oliitege menagitibeci meetaЙЎМ¶a, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane liciagi nigaanigawaanigi me diniwikodetibece.вҖқ  
\v 15 Odaa Jesus ja ipeketedeloco libaaЙЎМ¶atedi niЙЎМ¶ijo nigaanigipawaanigi me dipokotedibigimece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ibinietediogi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi joЙЎМ¶opi. 
\s1 Ica lioneeЙЎМ¶a liico ane domaЙЎМ¶a doletibige lewiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji 
\r (Marcos 10.17-31; Lucas 18.18-30) 
\p  
\v 16 Ica lioneeЙЎМ¶a enotalo Jesus, odaa ja ige, meetalo, вҖңЗӨoniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi anele, amiida ica ane leeditibige me jao, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa yewiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 17 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eete, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi ina menitiwa me Ee ele? Iniokeleteda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida nigemaani mida ЙЎМ¶adewiЙЎМ¶a ane diЙЎМ¶ica liniogo miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, oteteni liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco.вҖқ  
\v 18 NiЙЎМ¶ijo lioneeЙЎМ¶a meetalo, вҖңAmiicoa icoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco ane leeditibige me jotete?вҖқ Odaa meeteta Jesus, вҖңJineЙЎМ¶eloati oko, jinaЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶atakani, jinoЙЎМ¶olice, jinaЙЎМ¶a awitaka deЙЎМ¶eni eledi oko mowo ane beyagi!  
\v 19 Eemiteetibige ЙЎМ¶adiodi, aniaa ЙЎМ¶adiodo, codaa leeditibige memaani eledi oko digo aneni madinemaani.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 20 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lioneeЙЎМ¶a ja igidi, meetalo, вҖңIdioka limedi me jeemitetibige ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. AmaleeЙЎМ¶ida ane leeditibige me jao?вҖқ  
\v 21 Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eeteta Jesus, вҖңNigemaani me diЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶abatiigi, emii, aani idiwatawece ane ЙЎМ¶anepilidi, odaa edianitece ЙЎМ¶aninyeelo niЙЎМ¶inoa madewetedi, amaleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji owidi ЙЎМ¶aniliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi digoida ditibigimedi. OdaaЙЎМ¶anagi, aniwitici!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶ijo lioneeЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶a wajipatalo Jesus lotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶opi, eliodi magecaЙЎМ¶alo, leeЙЎМ¶odi me liico laxokegi, owidi niЙЎМ¶icoa ane nepilidi niliicaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi. 
\p  
\v 23 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. DaЙЎМ¶axa me dakake niЙЎМ¶ina liico me ikatece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶ena.  
\v 24 NiЙЎМ¶ina liico dakaketibige me ikatece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶ena, eneЙЎМ¶egi diЙЎМ¶ica laЙЎМ¶aliigi me jixomaЙЎМ¶atiwece niЙЎМ¶ina gameelo catiwedi niЙЎМ¶ina etakado libegi.вҖқ \fig |src="HK007B.tif" size="span" copy="Horace Knowles revised by Louise Bass В© The British & Foreign Bible Society, 1994." ref="Mateus 19.24" \fig* 
\p  
\v 25 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶owajipatalo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, eliodi moyopo, odaa modi, вҖңEnice, amiijo ica anepaЙЎМ¶a yakadi mida lewiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji?вҖқ  
\v 26 NaЙЎМ¶a iwitediogi Jesus, odaa meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina oko aЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi deЙЎМ¶eo mida lewiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baЙЎМ¶a yakadi meote inoatawece.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 27 Odaa Pedro meetalo, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ida moko ja jikanaЙЎМ¶atedice ijoatawece ane ЙЎМ¶onepilidi, odaa ja jiwaЙЎМ¶atibigaЙЎМ¶adici. Odaa, amigini ica ЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶eedi?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 28 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, icota me jiiЙЎМ¶e inatawece oko jatikata AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji loniciwaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica noko nige yoe gela iiЙЎМ¶o. Nige jiiЙЎМ¶enataka, jajigotaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atetigitiwaji, akaami dooze ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi, ananiwitici. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶iiЙЎМ¶enitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijoa dooze licoЙЎМ¶eco Israel.  
\v 29 Codaa inatawece niЙЎМ¶ina anoyaladi liЙЎМ¶elatedi, nioxoadipi, niwaalepodi, eliodi, eliodo, lodawa, lionigipi, codaa me niiЙЎМ¶otedi, codaa anoyaladi inoatawece, Ee leeЙЎМ¶odi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yajigotediogi caticedi niЙЎМ¶ijoa anoyaladi. Codaa jiЙЎМ¶ida lewiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 30 Codaa eliodi oko niЙЎМ¶ina ane ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egipi niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi, jiЙЎМ¶idiaa onaxaceti liboonaЙЎМ¶adi. Pida eliodi ane diЙЎМ¶ica naЙЎМ¶atetigi niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi, niЙЎМ¶idi baaniЙЎМ¶idiaa leegitibigimece liboonaЙЎМ¶atedi.вҖқ 
\c 20  
\s1 Natematigigi icoa niimetedi anodoweditelogo nawodigijedi uuva 
\p  
\v 1 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e oko laaleЙЎМ¶enali, digawini anodaaЙЎМ¶ee. Onica ica ane nebi icoa nawodigijedi uuva. One opedi me noditice, igo doletibige liimetedi me nibaaЙЎМ¶a midi lixoЙЎМ¶otagi.  
\v 2 Onicoa icoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane dinilakidetege me yedia onaniteci beexo ane loojedi onidateci noko me jibaaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶eticogi midi lixoЙЎМ¶otagi.  
\v 3 NoЙЎМ¶one noove lakata joniЙЎМ¶igotace niЙЎМ¶ica ane lotokaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anodoletibige libakedi. NaЙЎМ¶a nadi icoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane diЙЎМ¶ica libakedi,  
\v 4 odaa meetiogi, вҖҳEmiitiwaji abaa midiwa yawodigijedi uuva, odaa ЙЎМ¶adedianitiwaji ЙЎМ¶adoojedi ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.вҖҷ Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci.  
\v 5 NaЙЎМ¶a yaxoЙЎМ¶o-noko jiЙЎМ¶igotace, codaa naЙЎМ¶a iniwatadaЙЎМ¶ani lakata me ЙЎМ¶ocidi, jiЙЎМ¶igotace, odaa jiЙЎМ¶icotiogi eletidi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anoyemaa me nibaaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶etibigiwaji me nibaaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a nipegi me ciinco lakata, jiЙЎМ¶igotace niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yakadite liimetedi. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶icotiogi eletidi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anidiaaЙЎМ¶iticoace niЙЎМ¶ijo anei. Odaa ja nigetiniwace, meetiogi, вҖҳIgaamee ina minaaЙЎМ¶onitetiwaji idatawece noko me diЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶abakedi?вҖҷ  
\v 7 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, modita, вҖҳInaaЙЎМ¶ejonaЙЎМ¶a digoina leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶ica ane najigotoЙЎМ¶owa ЙЎМ¶obakedi.вҖҷ Odaa meetiogi, вҖҳEmiitiwaji midiwa yawodigijedi, odaa ЙЎМ¶adedianitiwaji ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a me ЙЎМ¶adoojedi.вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 8 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a nexogotini, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane nepilidi niЙЎМ¶ijoa uuva jeЙЎМ¶enidita niЙЎМ¶ijo ane dowediteloco niЙЎМ¶ijoa elanigijedi, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eeta, вҖҳAniditiogi iimetedipi, odaaЙЎМ¶anedianitiniwace. Odoejegi manedianitiniwace niЙЎМ¶ijo anowidijedipi me nibaaЙЎМ¶a, odaa owidijeeni manedianiti niЙЎМ¶ijo anodoejedipi me nibaaЙЎМ¶a.вҖҷ  
\v 9 Ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi ane nibaaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a nipegi me ciinco lakata me ЙЎМ¶ocidi, odibatege onaniteci beexo loojedi me nibaaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 10 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anepaЙЎМ¶a opeditibigiwaji me nibaaЙЎМ¶a odiletibige doЙЎМ¶odibatege caticedi. Pida ijotawece odibatege onaniteci beexo ane ligegitege niЙЎМ¶ijo necalailegi.  
\v 11 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶odibatege ninyeelo, odaa ja notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ateloco oyalomeЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo necalailegi.  
\v 12 Modita, вҖҳNiЙЎМ¶idiwa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi nibaaЙЎМ¶a onexaa onaniteci lakata. Pida oko baЙЎМ¶a jibaaЙЎМ¶a idatawece noko idinatiiЙЎМ¶ata dapicaЙЎМ¶aligeЙЎМ¶e. Pida mediani ЙЎМ¶odiwokodaЙЎМ¶awepodi ane liwokodi ЙЎМ¶oninyeelo.вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 13 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo necalailegi ja igidi, meetiogi, вҖҳYokaaЙЎМ¶etedipi, aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a jaotaЙЎМ¶adomi ane beyagi. Madinilakidenitigi jiЙЎМ¶idaa liwokodi memaani mabaatege onaniteci beexo loojedi onidateci noko mabaa.  
\v 14 Natigide, abaatege ЙЎМ¶aninyeelo odaaЙЎМ¶opiliticogi ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi. EmaЙЎМ¶a jemaa me jajigotiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo owidijegi menotibeci me liwokodaЙЎМ¶awa ane jajigotaЙЎМ¶awa.  
\v 15 Domige jakadi me jao ane jemaa mejigotalo ininyeelo? OЙЎМ¶oa, anoceetema ina eledi oko ane jemaa me ee libinienigitema?вҖҷвҖқ 
\p  
\v 16 Odaa Jesus nigoditedini me dotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңJoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ina anowidijedipi jiЙЎМ¶idiaa odoejegi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ina anodoejedipi jiЙЎМ¶idiaa owidijedipi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eniditediogi eliodi oko, pida onateciЙЎМ¶idi ane iolatedicoace.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶atace me yeleo pida yewiЙЎМ¶atace nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi 
\r (Marcos 10.32-34; Lucas 18.31-34) 
\p  
\v 17 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a dowicetedibigimece nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, noЙЎМ¶atedicoace niЙЎМ¶ijo dooze anodiotibece, odaa eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee mewaligitibigiwaji, neЙЎМ¶eetediogi Jesus,  
\v 18 вҖңDiganajipaatiwatiwaji! Ja jiiЙЎМ¶ata JerusalГ©m. Odaa Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, etidajigotiogi anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s. Odaa modi mone jao ane beyagi, codaa me leeditibige metideloadi.  
\v 19 Codaa metidajigotiogi lacilodi romaanotedi. Odaa metidame, codaa metidalaketibige, codaa etidototeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate. Pida nige ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi me ideleo, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jeЙЎМ¶eote me idewiЙЎМ¶atace.вҖқ 
\s1 Ica lipoketegi eliodo Tiago ijaa JoГЈo 
\r (Marcos 10.35-45) 
\p  
\v 20 Odaa aca lodawa Zebedeu jiЙЎМ¶igo midoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus lixigaЙЎМ¶awadi niЙЎМ¶ijoa itoa lionaЙЎМ¶a, Tiago ijaa JoГЈo. Odaa ja yamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi lodoe Jesus, odaa ja dipokotalo meote niЙЎМ¶ica liwikodenatakaneЙЎМ¶egi. 
\p  
\v 21 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a ige, meeteta, вҖңAmiinoda ica anemaani?вҖқ Odaa ja igidi, meetalo, вҖңAwiita niЙЎМ¶inoda ionigipi me nicote ЙЎМ¶awai, oniniteci ЙЎМ¶aba-aaЙЎМ¶adi, iniaaЙЎМ¶eledi deЙЎМ¶e-eetege ЙЎМ¶animagijegi mikeeni me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, nigo-oota ma-aami inionigi-eliodi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 22 Pida Jesus ja igidi, meetediogi, вҖңAЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ica anipokitibige. Domigakatitiwaji mawikodee digo aneji nige jawikode?вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oniniЙЎМ¶odi, moditalo Jesus, вҖңOko jiboЙЎМ¶atege me jawikodeeЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica aneni mawikodee.вҖқ  
\v 23 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңEwi makati mawikodeetiwaji, niЙЎМ¶ica aneji me jawikode. Pida aЙЎМ¶ica inaЙЎМ¶atetigi daЙЎМ¶a jakadi mejitaЙЎМ¶awa manicootini ibaaЙЎМ¶adi iniaaЙЎМ¶eledi diЙЎМ¶etege inimagijegi. Pida Eiodi ilakidetedini niЙЎМ¶idiwa nimetiidi, baaniЙЎМ¶iniaa yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica ane nicoteloco.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 24 NiЙЎМ¶ijo eledi anodiotibece noЙЎМ¶owajipata ane domoЙЎМ¶oyemaa niЙЎМ¶ijo dinioxomigi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyelatema.  
\v 25 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece menagitibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a, odaa meetediogi, вҖңOwooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji anodaaЙЎМ¶ee niЙЎМ¶ina inionigi-eliodi me dakake ane igotiogi niЙЎМ¶idi loiigi ane iiЙЎМ¶e. Codaa owooЙЎМ¶oti anodaaЙЎМ¶ee moibake naЙЎМ¶atetigi niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶odacilodipi moiiЙЎМ¶e eledi oko.  
\v 26 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji jinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶awii liciagi anowote niЙЎМ¶ina ane niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina ane yemaa me ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶egi leeditibige me niЙЎМ¶iwatece eledi oko.  
\v 27 Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane yemaa me dibata odoejegi nimedi leeditibige moiwotage niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko.  
\v 28 Awii liciagi Ee. IgaataЙЎМ¶a Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, ajanagi daЙЎМ¶a jiotage oko. Pida janagi me Ee niotagi, codaa me jajigo yewiЙЎМ¶a me loojedi ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me napitaЙЎМ¶adi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco eliodi oko.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus icilatidi itoataale ЙЎМ¶oladi 
\r (Marcos 10.46-52; Lucas 18.35-43) 
\p  
\v 29 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece ja noditicoaci nigotaЙЎМ¶a JericГі. Odaa eliodi ica noiigi anodiotece Jesus.  
\v 30 Onidiwa icoa iniwataale ЙЎМ¶oladi onicotinece naigi liniogotibece. NoЙЎМ¶owajipatibece modi me Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ixomaЙЎМ¶atijo, odaa ja napaawaЙЎМ¶a, modi, вҖңЗӨoniotagodi, anida anenitege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi, ЙЎМ¶odiwikodeneЙЎМ¶egi!вҖқ  
\v 31 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi joЙЎМ¶onapeteЙЎМ¶etiniwace, oiiЙЎМ¶e me notokotiniwace. Pida jeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a dinigetaЙЎМ¶ateetibigiwaji me napaawaЙЎМ¶a, modi, вҖңЗӨoniotagodi, ЙЎМ¶odiwikodeneЙЎМ¶egi, anida anenitege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi!вҖқ  
\v 32 NaЙЎМ¶a dabiditedi Jesus, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eniditediogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oladi. Odaa ja nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңAmiini ica anemaanitiwaji me jaotaЙЎМ¶adomi?вҖқ  
\v 33 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңЗӨoniotagodi, jemaanaЙЎМ¶a mawii me jatenaЙЎМ¶atibece.вҖқ  
\v 34 Jesus iwikodetediogi, naЙЎМ¶a dibatedeloco ligecooЙЎМ¶eli, odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi joЙЎМ¶oyakadi me doletibigiwaji, odaa joЙЎМ¶odiotece. 
\c 21  
\s1 Jesus dakatediwece nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina inionigi-eliodi 
\r (Marcos 11.1-11; Lucas 19.28-40; JoГЈo 12.12-19) 
\p  
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece noЙЎМ¶odipegita nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, joЙЎМ¶otota neЙЎМ¶epaa nigotakawaana BetfagГ©, anipegitege lojotaЙЎМ¶adi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңOliveiraвҖқ. JoaniЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶i Jesus naЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶e itoataale niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece migotibeci odoe.  
\v 2 Meetediogi, вҖңEmiitiwaji manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotakawaana digoida ЙЎМ¶ododoe, odaa maleekokakaatio jaЙЎМ¶aniaa boliico dinigoetini, iniaaЙЎМ¶ini boliicawaanigi manitaЙЎМ¶a. Owileceni, odaa anadeegitediwa!  
\v 3 Odaa nigica ane ЙЎМ¶adige ane leeЙЎМ¶odi mowileceni naЙЎМ¶ani boliico, enitatiwaji, вҖҳЗӨoniotagodi yopotedibige. Aleegi odaa nopilaЙЎМ¶aditedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji.вҖҷвҖқ 
\p  
\v 4 NiЙЎМ¶ida anee eotibige micotece lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶ee, 
\q1  
\v 5 вҖңEnitiogi niЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi JerusalГ©m, 
\q1 вҖҳDigawinitegetiwaji! 
\q1 ЗӨaninionigi-eliodi jeЙЎМ¶enotedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji. 
\q1 OkaaЙЎМ¶egi, 
\q1 codaa waxoditedeloco niЙЎМ¶inoda boliicawaanigi.вҖҷвҖқ 
\p  
\v 6 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo itoataale anodiotibece jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci, odaa joЙЎМ¶owo niЙЎМ¶ijo ane iiЙЎМ¶ete Jesus.  
\v 7 JoЙЎМ¶onadeegi niЙЎМ¶ijo boliicawaanigi ajaaЙЎМ¶ajo eliodo, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyexaЙЎМ¶ateloco nicaapatedi, odaa Jesus ja waxoditedeloco.  
\v 8 Eliodi oko oipecetedice nicaapatedi niЙЎМ¶ijo naigitece, inatecibece boЙЎМ¶onakagidi niale laamotiidi, odaa oilaagaЙЎМ¶aditedinece naigi moiweniЙЎМ¶ide Jesus.  
\v 9 Eliodi oko igotibeci lodoe, codaa eliodi eledi oko boЙЎМ¶odilokotelogo, odaa ijotawece napaawaЙЎМ¶ateloco, modi, 
\b  
\q1 вҖңJemaanaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iweniЙЎМ¶ide NiЙЎМ¶inoa 
\q1 anida aneetetege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi! 
\q1 JemaanaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ibinie NiЙЎМ¶inoa anenagi 
\q1 anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi me LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji! 
\q1 JoЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶atibigimece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 10 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a dakatediwece nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, eliodi niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi itaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji, dinigetiwage, modi, вҖңAmiiniwa icoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa?вҖқ \fig |src="CN01784B.TIF" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Mateus 21.10" \fig* 
\v 11 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi anijo mijoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus joЙЎМ¶oniniЙЎМ¶odi, modi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶iniwa joaniЙЎМ¶iniaaЙЎМ¶iniwa NiЙЎМ¶ina ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko, Jesus, anelatedibige nigotaЙЎМ¶a NazarГ© midi nipodigi GalilГ©ia.вҖқ 
\s1 Ica Jesus loenatagi mini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi 
\r (Marcos 11.15-19; Lucas 19.45-48; JoГЈo 2.13-22) 
\p  
\v 12 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a dakatediwece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, ja niticoitedicoace ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo ane enaanaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo ane oojeteeЙЎМ¶a. Odaa yamaЙЎМ¶atedini nameejatedi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiikoaЙЎМ¶e dinyeelo, codaa me nibaancotedi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyaa yotipitedi.  
\v 13 Odaa meetediogi, вҖңMaditaЙЎМ¶a lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, iwoteloco ane ligegi, niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶ee, вҖҳIdokoyatigi iЙЎМ¶eladi me diimigi anei oko modoЙЎМ¶etetibigimece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖҷ Pida akamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji baЙЎМ¶ademii micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶adi olicaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 14 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi icoa ЙЎМ¶oladi icaaЙЎМ¶icoa alejaadotedi enagitibeci midoa Jesus minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa ja nicilatiditediniwace.  
\v 15 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, eliodi me neliЙЎМ¶ideeЙЎМ¶a, noЙЎМ¶onadi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi Jesus aneote, codaa noЙЎМ¶owajipatiogi nigaanigipawaanigi me napaawaЙЎМ¶ateloco mini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, modi, вҖңJemaanaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iweniЙЎМ¶ide NiЙЎМ¶iniwa anida aneetetege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi!вҖқ  
\v 16 Odaa moditalo Jesus, вҖңIda makaami ajipaata ida ligegi idi nigaanigipawaanigi?вҖқ NaЙЎМ¶a niniЙЎМ¶odi Jesus, meetediogi, вҖңJa jajipatiogi. Pida ajawienataka naЙЎМ¶alomeЙЎМ¶enitelocotiwaji ane diniditeloco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, miditaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo anee, вҖҳAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace lionekadawaanaЙЎМ¶a inaa nigaanigipawaanigi anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me joЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶atibigimece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane eneЙЎМ¶egi ele mejinaЙЎМ¶a me joЙЎМ¶eeЙЎМ¶atibigimece.вҖҷвҖқ  
\v 17 Odaa Jesus ja yototedicoace, ja noditedice JerusalГ©m, jiЙЎМ¶igo nigotakawaana BetГўnia. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaa limedi. 
\s1 Jesus ixoo ajo fiigo libatadi 
\r (Marcos 11.12-14, 20-24) 
\p  
\v 18 NeЙЎМ¶eledi noko me nigoitijo, Jesus joЙЎМ¶opitacedicogi JerusalГ©m, odaa ja nigicile.  
\v 19 NaЙЎМ¶a nadi ajo libatadi вҖңfiigoigoвҖқ liniogotibece naigi, odaa ja diiteta. Pida aЙЎМ¶aca yakadi ela, inokinoa laamotiidi. Odaa meeteta naЙЎМ¶ajo niale, вҖңAЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶akati majici fiigo!вҖқ Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi naЙЎМ¶ajo fiigoigo ja yadilo. 
\p  
\v 20 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶onadi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece niЙЎМ¶ijo niciagi, odaa eliodi moyopo, modi me notaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ica meo me yediiЙЎМ¶a me yadilo naЙЎМ¶ada niale!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 21 Jesus ja niniЙЎМ¶odi, meetediogi, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. Niganakatonitetiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa nige daЙЎМ¶awienatakani, yakadi mawii liciagi niЙЎМ¶ida anejigota naЙЎМ¶ada fiigoigo, codaa yakadi mawii caticeditace ane jao. Yakadi menitatiwaji naЙЎМ¶adi wetiЙЎМ¶a, вҖҳAlatii, emii adinokolenitinigi akiidi-eliodi!вҖҷ Odaa naЙЎМ¶adi wetiЙЎМ¶a jaЙЎМ¶alatГӯ.  
\v 22 Niganakatonitetiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, yakadi mabaategetiwaji okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ica anipokitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni.вҖқ 
\s1 Icoa lacilodi noiigi oigetece Jesus niЙЎМ¶ica ane yajigotalo naЙЎМ¶atetigi 
\r (Marcos 11.27-33; Lucas 20.1-8) 
\p  
\v 23 Jesus joЙЎМ¶opitacedicogi minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa ja niiЙЎМ¶axitediniwace ica noiigi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶a, jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci midoataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa laxokodi lacilodi niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oige Jesus, moditalo, вҖңAmiida ica ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atetigi mawiite inoa ane ЙЎМ¶adoenataka? Amiijo ica ane yajigotaЙЎМ¶awa ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atetigi?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 24 NaЙЎМ¶a niniЙЎМ¶odi Jesus, meetediogi, вҖңEe aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ida igikaneЙЎМ¶egi. Nigadigititiwaji, odaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a jeloЙЎМ¶oditaЙЎМ¶awa ane najigotiwa inaЙЎМ¶atetigi.  
\v 25 Enice, amiijo ica ane yajigota naЙЎМ¶atetigi JoГЈo Batista me nilegetiniwace oko? Mige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, oЙЎМ¶oa, domige oko oyajigota naЙЎМ¶atetigi?вҖқ 
\p Odaa joЙЎМ¶odinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etigi, modi, вҖңNigejinaЙЎМ¶a me AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yajigote naЙЎМ¶atetigi JoГЈo, odaa jeЙЎМ¶eetedoЙЎМ¶owa, вҖҳEnice, igaamee ina me diЙЎМ¶iwaЙЎМ¶atiteda lotaЙЎМ¶a JoГЈo?вҖҷ  
\v 26 Pida deЙЎМ¶ejinaЙЎМ¶a, вҖҳMe ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi oyajigota naЙЎМ¶atetigi JoГЈo.вҖҷ Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi joЙЎМ¶oyelatoЙЎМ¶odomi, igaataЙЎМ¶a oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi me AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niiЙЎМ¶e JoГЈo me nilegetiniwace oko, odaa geme idoiiЙЎМ¶atiogi niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi.вҖқ  
\v 27 NoЙЎМ¶oniniЙЎМ¶odi Jesus, moditalo, вҖңAjowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a ane yajigota naЙЎМ¶atetigi JoГЈo.вҖқ Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңEnice Ee ajeloЙЎМ¶oditaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji ane najigotiwa inaЙЎМ¶atetigi me jaote niЙЎМ¶inoa yoenataka. 
\s1 Natematigigi icoa itoataale nionaЙЎМ¶a 
\p  
\v 28 Pida amiida ica anakatitecetiwaji? Ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa onidiwa iniwataale lionaЙЎМ¶a. One diita niЙЎМ¶ica lionigi boЙЎМ¶oxiiЙЎМ¶odi, odaa oneeta, вҖҳIonigi, niЙЎМ¶ina noko emii abaa midiwa eyanigijedi uuva!вҖҷ  
\v 29 NaЙЎМ¶a igidi, meeta, вҖҳEe aЙЎМ¶ejigo.вҖҷ Pida niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja dinilaatibece, naЙЎМ¶a iigi lowoogo, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo diba.  
\v 30 NiЙЎМ¶ijo eliodi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a diita niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi lionigi, jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶e migo diba. Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eeta eliodi, вҖҳJe iniotagodi! JeЙЎМ¶ejigo.вҖҷ Pida aЙЎМ¶igo.  
\v 31 AmepidiЙЎМ¶ica ijoa lionaЙЎМ¶a eo ane yemaa eliodi?вҖқ Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi noiigi joЙЎМ¶oniniЙЎМ¶odi, moditalo, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ijo lionigi liidaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anewi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji dibatetege codaa me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali niЙЎМ¶ijo anodibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi, inaa ewocomigipi, niЙЎМ¶ina oko anakatitiwaji meliodi me abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, pida AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baadaЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶eteda ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enalitiwaji.  
\v 32 IgaataЙЎМ¶a JoГЈo Batista enagi, odaa ikee niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me ejoЙЎМ¶otalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida niЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji aЙЎМ¶iwaЙЎМ¶ati lotaЙЎМ¶a JoГЈo. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo anodibatibigege ninyeelo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa ewocomigipi boЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji, naЙЎМ¶anati me eniwaЙЎМ¶atakanaЙЎМ¶a codaa modiotece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, idokee aЙЎМ¶adinilaanitibecetiwaji, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a iwaЙЎМ¶ati JoГЈo.вҖқ 
\s1 Natematigigi icoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a 
\r (Marcos 12.1-12; Lucas 20.9-19) 
\p  
\v 33 Jesus eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me dotaЙЎМ¶a, meetediogi, вҖңDigajipaatatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ida eledi natematigo anida ane jiciaceeketege! Onini ica ane nebi icoa iiЙЎМ¶otedi aneyatelogo elanigijedi uuva, odaa ja niotaa. Codaa jonaЙЎМ¶a iwila aca nalice lajo monoЙЎМ¶a uuva liwagedi, codaa dabiteЙЎМ¶etini lipe libeoЙЎМ¶adi ica anoyowie elanigijedi. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja yajigotiogi me niwaiЙЎМ¶awepodi icoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi niЙЎМ¶ijoa elanigijedi. Odaa ja diniwiaje.  
\v 34 NaЙЎМ¶a nipegi monopilaЙЎМ¶aditedio elali, odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶e icoa liotaka, iiЙЎМ¶etiogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi modibatege niЙЎМ¶ica liwai ane nebi.  
\v 35 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi joЙЎМ¶odibatiogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa liotaka. Onica ica ononaxacoЙЎМ¶otibige, ica eledi boЙЎМ¶odaa oyeloadi, ica eledi boЙЎМ¶onexaa onigidatice.  
\v 36 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ica ane nepilidi enanigijedi ja iiЙЎМ¶e eletidi liotaka, pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi owo liciagi anodigotiogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa odoejedipi ane iiЙЎМ¶e.  
\v 37 NoЙЎМ¶owidijegi ja iiЙЎМ¶e ica epaa lionigi, meetibige le, вҖҳEjime odeemitetibige ionigi.вҖҷ  
\v 38 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijoa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi noЙЎМ¶onaditege niЙЎМ¶ijo lionigi, odaa modi me dinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e, вҖҳNiЙЎМ¶ina anenagi niЙЎМ¶ijo lionigi anicota me nepilidi niЙЎМ¶inoa nawodigijedi eliodaЙЎМ¶ajetecidi. Ele me jeloataЙЎМ¶a, odaa niЙЎМ¶inoa nawodigijedi ja ЙЎМ¶onepilidi!вҖҷ  
\v 39 Odaa joЙЎМ¶odibata niЙЎМ¶ijo lionigi ane nepilidi nawodigijedi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegiticogi wetice niЙЎМ¶idiwa nawodigijedi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyeloadi. 
\p  
\v 40 Nige limedi menagi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane nepilidi nawodigijedi, amigida ica anigotiogi idiwa nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi?вҖқ  
\v 41 NoЙЎМ¶oniniЙЎМ¶odi Jesus, moditalo, вҖңEo meliodi me nawikodeeЙЎМ¶a codaa nigodi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. Odaa yadilaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eta lawodigijedi eletidi nawodaЙЎМ¶anadi, anepaЙЎМ¶a oyopilaЙЎМ¶adita niwai anida aneetege nigicota noko monopilaЙЎМ¶aditedio.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 42 Odaa meetediogi Jesus, вҖңAjawienataka naЙЎМ¶alomeЙЎМ¶enitelocotiwaji maditaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi, niЙЎМ¶ijo anee, 
\q1 вҖҳNaЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a ane diЙЎМ¶ica mowo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodabiteЙЎМ¶etini diimigi, 
\q1 naЙЎМ¶ani wetiЙЎМ¶a jiЙЎМ¶icota me naЙЎМ¶aca ane eneЙЎМ¶egi oyopotibige. 
\q1 Pida ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mina igote, 
\q1 codaa jakataЙЎМ¶a mele niЙЎМ¶ida loenatagi.вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 43 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi mejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me daЙЎМ¶adiaa iiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali, pida ja iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali eledi oko anepaЙЎМ¶a oyoe niЙЎМ¶ica ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 44 Nigica oko aneniteloco naЙЎМ¶ani wetiЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja napeegitibige, eote liwailidawaanaЙЎМ¶a. Pida naЙЎМ¶ani wetiЙЎМ¶a niganipaЙЎМ¶a eniteloco oko, iopaaЙЎМ¶adi codaa yeloadi niЙЎМ¶ica oko.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 45 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi noЙЎМ¶owajipatalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa natematiko anida ane iciaceeketege Jesus meyatemati, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶eetediogi Jesus.  
\v 46 Odaa ja domoЙЎМ¶oyemaa moniwilo Jesus, pida aЙЎМ¶ica nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi leeЙЎМ¶odi odoitiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi, igaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi oyakadi Jesus miniЙЎМ¶ina ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko. 
\c 22  
\s1 Natematigigi lalokegi ica nadoneЙЎМ¶egi 
\r (Lucas 14.15-24) 
\p  
\v 1 Jesus yatemati eledi natematigo anida ane iciaceeketetege me dotaЙЎМ¶a lodoe niЙЎМ¶ijo ane niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a, meetediogi,  
\v 2 вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko, jiciaceeketege niЙЎМ¶ina inionigi-eliodi ane ilakidetini nalokegi ladoneЙЎМ¶egi lionigi.  
\v 3 Odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶e liotaka modigotece lodenigipitema lalokegi. Pida anibetibigiwaji, aЙЎМ¶oyemaa migotibeci nalooЙЎМ¶o.  
\v 4 Odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶e eletidi liotaka, meetiogi, вҖҳEnitiogi ЙЎМ¶ododenigipi, вҖңDigawinitiwaji! Nalokegi ja limedi. JoЙЎМ¶onigodi waca-lioneke, inaa ЙЎМ¶odinadi ajakalodi, codaa inoatawece ja igo. Anagitiwaji midi nalooЙЎМ¶o!вҖқ вҖҷ  
\v 5 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo nodenigipi aЙЎМ¶ica mowo, odaa oninitecibeci jiЙЎМ¶igo iwi epaa libakedi. Onica ica anigo nibajeenda, ica eledi biЙЎМ¶igo mani noojetekaxi.  
\v 6 IcaaЙЎМ¶ica eledi nodenigipi baЙЎМ¶a odibatiogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa liotaka, odaa joЙЎМ¶onaxacoЙЎМ¶otiniwace, joЙЎМ¶onigodi.  
\v 7 NiЙЎМ¶ijo inionigi-eliodi naЙЎМ¶a dibodiceta niЙЎМ¶ica niciagi, eliodi me deliЙЎМ¶ide, odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶e niodaЙЎМ¶awadi monigodi niЙЎМ¶ijoa aijekaЙЎМ¶a, codaa moyalegi nigotaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 8 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi meetiogi liotaka, вҖҳLalokegi nadoneЙЎМ¶egi ja igo, pida niЙЎМ¶ijo oko yodenigipi aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶oyakadi menagitibeci, leeЙЎМ¶odi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 9 Odaa natigide, emii iwitece ladicotiidi, odaa anodenitema nalokegi okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica oko anakapetege.вҖҷ  
\v 10 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa liotaka joЙЎМ¶odioteci ladicotiidi, oyatecoЙЎМ¶otee inatawece oko anodakapetege, inatecibece oko libinienigipi, codaa minatecibece baЙЎМ¶a abeyaceЙЎМ¶egipi. Odaa naЙЎМ¶aca nalokaxi ja nolee oko. 
\p  
\v 11 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo inionigi-eliodi naЙЎМ¶a dakatiwece nalokaxi me iwitiogi nodenigipi, odaa ja nadi ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane daЙЎМ¶a dinixotinigilo icoa nowoodi epoka lajo nalokegi.  
\v 12 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo inionigi-eliodi ja ige niЙЎМ¶ijo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, meeta, вҖҳЗӨodokaaЙЎМ¶edi, igame ЙЎМ¶animaweneЙЎМ¶egi manakaatio me diЙЎМ¶icoateda ЙЎМ¶adowoodi anepaa lajo nalokegi?вҖҷ Pida aЙЎМ¶ica aneteЙЎМ¶eyatigi ligegi.  
\v 13 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo inionigi-eliodi meetiogi liotaka, вҖҳAgoeni libaaЙЎМ¶atedi, loЙЎМ¶onaka, odaa okoleniticogi wetice midi nexocaЙЎМ¶a, aneite oko me noenaЙЎМ¶ateloco, codaa moyacigice lowe, leeЙЎМ¶odi lawikodico.вҖҷ  
\v 14 IgaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji eniditediogi eliodi oko, pida onateciЙЎМ¶idi ane iolatedicoace.вҖқ 
\s1 Fariseutedi oige Jesus domige leeditibige moyediatece inionigi-eliodi dinyeelo 
\r (Marcos 12.13-17; Lucas 20.20-26) 
\p  
\v 15 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi ja noditicoaci me diniikoetiwage lowooko domoЙЎМ¶owotibige Jesus meote ligegi ane daЙЎМ¶a diitigi, domoЙЎМ¶owotibige doЙЎМ¶oyakadi me nilaagedi.  
\v 16 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oimonyatalo Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibeci fariseutedi oiwaЙЎМ¶ateetece niЙЎМ¶ijo ane licaajepodi inionigi-eliodi Herodes. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶exedi moditalo Jesus, вҖңNiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a makaami oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, codaa mewi me iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anitece niЙЎМ¶ica AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane yemaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko mowo. Codaa jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a me daЙЎМ¶a aniwinita niЙЎМ¶ina oko migida naЙЎМ¶atetigi, oЙЎМ¶oa domige aЙЎМ¶ica naЙЎМ¶atetigi.  
\v 17 Natigide, enitoЙЎМ¶owa niЙЎМ¶ica anakati. Domige lakapetegi najoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi ЙЎМ¶odoiigi me jedianaЙЎМ¶atece CГ©sar, ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi, niЙЎМ¶icoa dinyeelo ane leeditibige me jedianaЙЎМ¶a? Domige lakapetegi ЙЎМ¶onajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi, oЙЎМ¶oa, adakapetege?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 18 Pida Jesus ja yowooЙЎМ¶oditediwe lowooko ane beyagi, odaa meetediogi, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶oditiwaji madineenitiwa? Akaamitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anokowo meletibigiwaji.  
\v 19 Digawii anadeegitiwatiwaji beexo naЙЎМ¶ana anatikani mediani romaanotedi anetiЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶eni mediani.вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegitalo aca beexo.  
\v 20 Odaa ja nigetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңAme liwigo aniwoteloco ani beexo? Codaa ame liboonaЙЎМ¶adi ane diniditeloco ani beexo?вҖқ  
\v 21 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңCГ©sar, niЙЎМ¶ijo ninionigi-eliodi romaanotedi.вҖқ Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңEnice edianitecetiwaji CГ©sar niЙЎМ¶ica ane nebi, codaa edianitece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ica ane nebi!вҖқ  
\v 22 NoЙЎМ¶owajipatalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a Jesus, eliodi moyopo. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyakamaЙЎМ¶adi, joЙЎМ¶opitibeci. 
\s1 Odigikatigi niЙЎМ¶ica noko nige newiЙЎМ¶atace niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a 
\r (Marcos 12.18-27; Lucas 20.27-40) 
\p  
\v 23 IjaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo noko joЙЎМ¶odiitalo Jesus icoa saduceutedi. NiЙЎМ¶icoa saduceutedi baadoЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶aditeda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji micota me yewikatiditace niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anigida noko.  
\v 24 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oige Jesus, moditalo, вҖңNiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, MoisГ©s diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece nigica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane yeleo, odaa ja nenyaЙЎМ¶aditi lodawa, maleediЙЎМ¶ica lionigitege, odaa nioxoa leeditibige me lodawa naЙЎМ¶ajo wajekalo eotibige mica lionigipi. Odaa diЙЎМ¶icoa lionaЙЎМ¶a micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a lionigipi ijoolatibige nioxoa.  
\v 25 Odaa onica seete dinioxomigipi aninaa liЙЎМ¶eladi digoina. NiЙЎМ¶ica liidaЙЎМ¶a jonaЙЎМ¶a wado. Pida aona niЙЎМ¶ica lionigi naЙЎМ¶a yeleo. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo nioxoa ja lodawa naЙЎМ¶ajo wajekalo.  
\v 26 Pida jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yeleo maleedaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶ica lionigitege. Odaa ica eledi nioxoa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a lodawa naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo. Pida idaaЙЎМ¶ee aniЙЎМ¶ica lionigitege naЙЎМ¶a yeleo. Odaa ijotawece seete dinioxomigipi nigo. Ijotawece nigo maleediЙЎМ¶ica lionigipi.  
\v 27 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yeleo.  
\v 28 Enice, nigicota noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meote me newiЙЎМ¶atace niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, amigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo seete dinioxomigi anepeЙЎМ¶ewi me lodawa naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo? IgaataЙЎМ¶a ijotawece lodawadi naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 29 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a niniЙЎМ¶odi, meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji eliodi mabataa leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a owooЙЎМ¶oti AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji notoetiigi.  
\v 30 IgaataЙЎМ¶a nigeotace AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me newiЙЎМ¶atace niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja liciagi niЙЎМ¶inoa niaanjotedi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. AЙЎМ¶alee nadonaЙЎМ¶a, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a icoa lionaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 31 Pida, niЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji ejiniЙЎМ¶ica malomeЙЎМ¶eniteloco ane ligegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶eetetece me newikatiditacediniwace niЙЎМ¶inoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a. Mee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji,  
\v 32 вҖҳEe NoenoЙЎМ¶odi AbraГЈo, codaa Ee NoenoЙЎМ¶odi Isaque, iniaa JacГі.вҖҷ AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aNoenoЙЎМ¶odi oko Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, pida NoenoЙЎМ¶odi oko ane newiЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ  
\v 33 NiЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi noЙЎМ¶owajipatalo Jesus lotaЙЎМ¶a, eliodi moyopo leeЙЎМ¶odi liiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi. 
\s1 LiiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneneЙЎМ¶egi ida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a 
\r (Marcos 12.28-34; Lucas 10.25-28) 
\p  
\v 34 NiЙЎМ¶ijo fariseutedi noЙЎМ¶odibodicetalo Jesus me yamaketedi saduceutedi. Odaa ja dinatecoЙЎМ¶otee.  
\v 35 Odaa onini mawatiogi ica ane diiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶ijaa dineetalo Jesus, domaЙЎМ¶a dibatalo diЙЎМ¶ica libatiigi me dotaЙЎМ¶a. Ige Jesus, meetalo,  
\v 36 вҖңNiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, amiida ica ЙЎМ¶oniiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi ane daЙЎМ¶axa mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a ane iditini MoisГ©s?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 37 NaЙЎМ¶a niniЙЎМ¶odi Jesus, odaa meete, вҖңвҖҳEmaani ЗӨaniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji manitawece ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena, midatawece niЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶alidekegi, codaa minitawece ЙЎМ¶adowoogo.вҖҷ  
\v 38 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ida odoejegi liiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ida ane daЙЎМ¶axa mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 39 NaЙЎМ¶a lowidi niЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶oniiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi, ida eledi ЙЎМ¶oniiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egi ane daЙЎМ¶axa mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a, liciagi niЙЎМ¶idi odoejegi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo anee, вҖҳLeeditibige memaani okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica oko, digo aneni madinemaani.вҖҷ  
\v 40 Nigoteteni niЙЎМ¶idoa itoataale ЙЎМ¶oniiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco, odaa joЙЎМ¶oteteni ijoatawece eletidi ЙЎМ¶oniiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco ane iditedini MoisГ©s, codaa me niЙЎМ¶idiwa niiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶eco aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oiditedini niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus digikatetece NiЙЎМ¶icoa ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji meo lewiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina oko 
\r (Marcos 12.35-37; Lucas 20.41-44) 
\p  
\v 41 NiЙЎМ¶ijo malee yatecoЙЎМ¶o niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi, odaa Jesus ja nigetediniwace, meetediogi,  
\v 42 вҖңAmiida ica ЙЎМ¶adowoogotece anodaaЙЎМ¶ee NiЙЎМ¶icoa ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me yatamaЙЎМ¶ateetege ЙЎМ¶odoiigi lawikodico? Amiida ica licoЙЎМ¶egi?вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, moditalo, вҖңIda aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi.вҖқ  
\v 43 Jesus ja nigetacediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңEnice, igame leeЙЎМ¶odi ina Davi meeta, вҖҳIniotagodiвҖҷ? Davi mee, вҖҳIniotagodiвҖҷ niЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a dakatiogi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji Liwigo eo me dotaЙЎМ¶a. IgaataЙЎМ¶a Davi mee me dotaЙЎМ¶a, 
\q1  
\v 44 вҖҳAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji InoenoЙЎМ¶odi meete Iniotagodi, 
\q1 вҖңAnicooti iwai ibaaЙЎМ¶adi nigepaaЙЎМ¶icota me jao manigaanyetece ЙЎМ¶aneloЙЎМ¶ododipi.вҖқ вҖҷ 
\m  
\v 45 Davi nigeyatigi me Niotagodi. Enice, igamodaaЙЎМ¶ee NiЙЎМ¶icoa ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anida aneetege licoЙЎМ¶egi Davi?вҖқ (IgaataЙЎМ¶a noiigi judeu aЙЎМ¶ica aneeta lionigi me Niotagodi.)  
\v 46 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica ane yakadi me igidi Jesus. Codaa jiЙЎМ¶ijaaЙЎМ¶ijotigi niЙЎМ¶ijo noko aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica anabo laaleЙЎМ¶ena me ige Jesus me dineetalo. 
\c 23  
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶ate niЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s 
\r (Marcos 12.38-40; Lucas 11.45-53; 20.45-47) 
\p  
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece,  
\v 2 вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece MoisГ©s lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco inaaЙЎМ¶inoa fariseutedi ida naЙЎМ¶atetigi modiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece codaa moyeloЙЎМ¶odi ane diitigilo niЙЎМ¶inoa ane diiЙЎМ¶enatakatalo MoisГ©s mowote.  
\v 3 Enice, okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica anodiiЙЎМ¶enatakata, iwaЙЎМ¶atitiwaji codaa awii. Pida jinaЙЎМ¶awii liciagi ane lakataЙЎМ¶a, igaataЙЎМ¶a odiiЙЎМ¶enatakata moyiwaЙЎМ¶adi ane diiЙЎМ¶enatakata najoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco, pida idiaaЙЎМ¶idi baadoЙЎМ¶oyiwaЙЎМ¶adi.  
\v 4 OdiiЙЎМ¶enatakata mowote niЙЎМ¶inoa ane dakake me jiwaЙЎМ¶atece, micataЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶oyexaЙЎМ¶ateloco lelГЎЙЎМ¶a oko loyaЙЎМ¶agi ane iwaaЙЎМ¶adi, pida aЙЎМ¶oyaxawa moyoyaЙЎМ¶adi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oyadodi!  
\v 5 Inoatawece anowote, owote modinikeenaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etema niЙЎМ¶ina oko. OyexocaЙЎМ¶aditeloco libaaЙЎМ¶adi, codaa me latocolodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶a owotibige niЙЎМ¶ina oko modiletibige deЙЎМ¶eliodi moyotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, codaa oyocaЙЎМ¶atee liniogo niЙЎМ¶inoa nijayogoli owotibige niЙЎМ¶ina oko modiletibige diЙЎМ¶iniЙЎМ¶ina niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi aninoa lixaketedi.  
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶ina me nalooЙЎМ¶o oyemaa monicotelogo niЙЎМ¶icoa ane daЙЎМ¶axa mele nimetiidi, codaa me niЙЎМ¶icoa nibaancotedi ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a midiwataЙЎМ¶a niiakanaЙЎМ¶axiidi.  
\v 7 Oyemaatibige niЙЎМ¶ina oko monicetibigiwaji, codaa lemaanigi niЙЎМ¶ina oko moikee modeemitetibige niЙЎМ¶ina modakapetibigege, codaa oyemaatibige niЙЎМ¶ina oko moditiogi me вҖҳNiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi!вҖҷ.  
\v 8 Pida akaamitiwaji baЙЎМ¶a jinaЙЎМ¶a domiЙЎМ¶ikani doЙЎМ¶oditaЙЎМ¶awa niЙЎМ¶ina oko makaami вҖҳNiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadiвҖҷ, igaataЙЎМ¶a iniwa oniniwatece ЙЎМ¶aniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi ane Cristo. Codaa akaamitawece akaami diniciamico, anakaami dinioxomigipi.  
\v 9 Codaa jinaЙЎМ¶a domiЙЎМ¶ica anenita me ЙЎМ¶adiodi digoina iiЙЎМ¶o. IgaataЙЎМ¶a oniniwatece ЗӨadiodi, ane ideite ditibigimedi.  
\v 10 JiniЙЎМ¶ikani niЙЎМ¶ina oko doЙЎМ¶oditaЙЎМ¶awa, вҖҳIniotagodiвҖҷ, igaataЙЎМ¶a oniniwatece ЗӨaniotagoditiwaji, Cristo ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Codaa jeЙЎМ¶emeЙЎМ¶ee ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 11 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina aneneЙЎМ¶egi ida niwalГі ЙЎМ¶adiwigotigitiwaji, jiЙЎМ¶iniaa ЙЎМ¶aotagi.  
\v 12 Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina anepaa ilecatiditibigimece liboonaЙЎМ¶adi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icota meote me diЙЎМ¶ica jaoЙЎМ¶a. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina ane diniwikodetibece, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icota meote me leegitibigimece liboonaЙЎМ¶adi. 
\s1 Jesus yapeteЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ina anokowo me eletibigiwaji 
\r (Marcos 12.40; Lucas 11.39-42, 47-52; 20.47) 
\p  
\v 13 Nagoodi akaamitiwaji, anakaami niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi ane iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anitece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, codaa akaami anakaami fariseutedi, anokawii makaami eletetiwaji! IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶ikanitiwaji diЙЎМ¶ica oko ane ikee anodaaЙЎМ¶ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶ena. Codaa akamaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji aЙЎМ¶emaani AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji daЙЎМ¶a iiЙЎМ¶e ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali, codaa aЙЎМ¶ikani niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko moyowooЙЎМ¶odi anodaaЙЎМ¶ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anigote, niЙЎМ¶ina oko anodoletibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali.  
\v 14 Nagoodi akaamitiwaji, anakaami niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi, codaa anakaami fariseutedi, anokawii makaami eletetiwaji! IgaataЙЎМ¶a aniboloiteeni iwaalepodi ane wajekalodipi, odaa abanoonitece niЙЎМ¶inoa liЙЎМ¶elatedi, codaa olicetalo niЙЎМ¶inoa ane nepilidi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ocaЙЎМ¶ateeni motaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, pida mina adinikeenaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЙЎМ¶adiloikatititetiwaji caticedi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi oko ane iloikatidi. 
\p  
\v 15 Nagoodi akaamitiwaji, anakaami niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi codaa anakaami fariseutedi, anokawii makaami eletetiwaji! IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶eetitatiwaji akiititedi-eloodoli, codaa aniwiajeetelogo owidi nipodaЙЎМ¶a moleetibige mawii mini oko ane dioteci ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina mini anakati mawii me diotaЙЎМ¶adici, jiЙЎМ¶icaaЙЎМ¶awiitibigetiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶inida oko caticedi anigotedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe. 
\p  
\v 16 Nagoodi akaamitiwaji! IgaataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiciagitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina oko ЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶a ane domoЙЎМ¶odoletibige moikeeta naigi niЙЎМ¶ina eledi ЙЎМ¶olaЙЎМ¶a. Meni me iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anitiwaji, вҖҳNigica aneo ligegi meo okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica me liboonaЙЎМ¶adi liЙЎМ¶eladi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa aibeyacaЙЎМ¶adi nige deЙЎМ¶eote niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ligegi. Pida nige ligegi meo okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica me liboonaЙЎМ¶adi nioolo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa baЙЎМ¶a leeditibige meo ane ligegi.вҖҷ  
\v 17 ЗӨadiciagitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina oko yetoledi codaa me ЙЎМ¶oladi! Amiida ica aneneЙЎМ¶egi ida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a, oolo ane idei AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, oЙЎМ¶oa iniaaЙЎМ¶ini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi aneo niЙЎМ¶idiwa oolo anidiwa catiwedi liЙЎМ¶eladi me nepilidi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji?  
\v 18 Codaa eledi meni me iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anitecetiwaji, вҖҳNigica oko aneo ligegi meo okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica me liboonaЙЎМ¶adi nameeja AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina me dotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa baadaЙЎМ¶a ibeyacaЙЎМ¶adi nige deЙЎМ¶eo niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ligegi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina nigeo ligegi me liboonaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijo liboonigi ane idei madi nameeja AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa baЙЎМ¶a leeditibige meo niЙЎМ¶ica ane ligegi.вҖҷ  
\v 19 ЗӨadiciagitiwaji yetoledi inaa ЙЎМ¶oladi! Amiida ica aneneЙЎМ¶egi ida ane jaoЙЎМ¶a, mige ЙЎМ¶oboonigi, oЙЎМ¶oa, domige nameeja aneo me dibatetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶oboonigi?  
\v 20 Enice oko aneo ligegi me liboonaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nameeja niЙЎМ¶ina me dotaЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ini oko aЙЎМ¶idokida me ibake liboonaЙЎМ¶adi nameeja, pida aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ibake liboonaЙЎМ¶adi okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica ane liboonigi madi nameeja.  
\v 21 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko meo ligegi me liboonaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, niЙЎМ¶ina me dotaЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ini oko aЙЎМ¶idokida me ibake liboonaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, pida aaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ibake LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aniniwa catiwedi liЙЎМ¶eladi.  
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko aneo ligegi me liboonaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ica ditibigimedi, niЙЎМ¶ina me dotaЙЎМ¶a, niЙЎМ¶ini oko ewi me ibake liboonaЙЎМ¶adi naЙЎМ¶aca AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nibaanco ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶e, codaa me LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ane nicotedeloco. 
\p  
\v 23 Nagoodi akaamitiwaji anakaami niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶atema lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s codaa anakaami fariseutedi anokawii makaami eletetiwaji! IgaataЙЎМ¶a aboonitalo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane nebi, codaa majici liwai niЙЎМ¶inoa anokateciЙЎМ¶inoa me ЙЎМ¶anidiizimo, niЙЎМ¶inoa niale laamotiidi ane jexakajoЙЎМ¶otinigi niweenigi me lanigi. Pida jiЙЎМ¶ikani me iwitece najoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco aneneЙЎМ¶egi ida ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate midiwa lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s. NiЙЎМ¶idiwa najoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco onikeetoЙЎМ¶owa anodaaЙЎМ¶ejinaЙЎМ¶a me jaoЙЎМ¶a ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, codaa moko eletema eledi oko, codaa onikeetoЙЎМ¶owa me leeditibige mejiwaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida domaЙЎМ¶a leeditibige me iwitecetiwaji niЙЎМ¶inoa najoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco ane daЙЎМ¶axa mida ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate, codaa maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a awiite niЙЎМ¶inoa ane deЙЎМ¶ewi ina mica ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate.  
\v 24 NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji ЙЎМ¶adiciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko ЙЎМ¶oladi anodoletibige moikeetece naigi eletidi ЙЎМ¶oladi. Codaa ЙЎМ¶adiciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane yaago viinyo me noЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶onoodo, pida baЙЎМ¶a yalitini gameelo, igaataЙЎМ¶a adowetiteloco niЙЎМ¶inoa anicinoa ane diЙЎМ¶ica ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate, pida aЙЎМ¶oeni niЙЎМ¶inoa anida ane jaoЙЎМ¶ate ane niiЙЎМ¶etedoЙЎМ¶owa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. 
\p  
\v 25 Nagoodi akaamitiwaji anakaami niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anadi ane iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anitece najoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco, codaa makaami fariseutedi, anokawii makaami eletetiwaji! NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji ica ina daЙЎМ¶a akaami eletetiwaji, ЙЎМ¶ademaanigitiwaji mele me iwileci wetice ЙЎМ¶anigoopa idaa ЙЎМ¶aniginogo, pida micataЙЎМ¶a daaditaЙЎМ¶a iwileci le ЙЎМ¶anigoopa idaa ЙЎМ¶aniginogo. Codaa micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a nolee ЙЎМ¶anigoopa idaa ЙЎМ¶aniginogo niЙЎМ¶ina ane ЙЎМ¶adolicaЙЎМ¶aditiwaji codaa akaami adodigomadadi, leeЙЎМ¶odi aЙЎМ¶akati madinajacaЙЎМ¶ati. Leeditibige maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a iwilecitiwaji catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶ena.  
\v 26 Anakaami fariseutedi, akaami ЙЎМ¶oladi! Odoejeeni miwileci catiwedi akaamitiwaji, micataЙЎМ¶a diЙЎМ¶iwileci le ЙЎМ¶anigoopa codaa me ЙЎМ¶aniginogo, odaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yapidi wetice. 
\p  
\v 27 Nagoodi akaamitiwaji ane iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anitece najoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco, codaa anakaami fariseutedi, anokawii makaami eletetiwaji! ЗӨadiciagitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina Г©meЙЎМ¶egi libegi, ane libinienigi inokina we, leeЙЎМ¶odi onadineЙЎМ¶eta nadinaЙЎМ¶ajegi ane yapacaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idiwa wetiadi. Pida catiwedi niЙЎМ¶ida begi, baЙЎМ¶a nolee ЙЎМ¶obitaka inaa neladaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 28 NiЙЎМ¶ina me ЙЎМ¶adiwineЙЎМ¶egitiwaji ica ina daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adeЙЎМ¶enakitiwaji, pida onawiitetiwaji makaami libinienigipi, codaa ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali nolee niЙЎМ¶ica ane beyagi. 
\p  
\v 29 Nagoodi akaamitiwaji ane iiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶anitece najoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco, codaa anakaami fariseutedi, anokawiitiwaji makaami eletetiwaji! IgaataЙЎМ¶a ipekeniteloco wetiadi libinienaЙЎМ¶a anonaligite niЙЎМ¶ijoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, liotagipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji baanaЙЎМ¶a nigo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece lowooko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Codaa awii ЙЎМ¶adiwilanigitiwaji ocaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a manalakitibige malee newiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide.  
\v 30 Odaa menitiwaji, вҖҳDaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odewiЙЎМ¶a malee newiЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odaamipi, agotaЙЎМ¶a inigotaЙЎМ¶a liotagipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anodigotiogi ЙЎМ¶odaamipi niЙЎМ¶ijo liotagipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖҷ  
\v 31 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ida anenitiwaji jiЙЎМ¶ikeeni mida anenitege licoЙЎМ¶egi niЙЎМ¶ijo anonigodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liotaka.  
\v 32 Odaa jaЙЎМ¶agotitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo nibakedi ane beyagi anoyojogotini ЙЎМ¶adaamipi.  
\v 33 ЗӨadiciagitiwaji niЙЎМ¶inoa laketedi ane diniweneene. NiЙЎМ¶ida makaamitiwaji aЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶animaweneЙЎМ¶egi daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adiwokoni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶odi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco, codaa nige limedi me imonyatedicogi minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane daЙЎМ¶a ipe.  
\v 34 Codaa EmeЙЎМ¶ee jiiЙЎМ¶eticogi makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko, inoa aninoa lixaketedi, inaaЙЎМ¶ina anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece niЙЎМ¶ica ane yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mowo niЙЎМ¶ina oko. Pida ijo ananigotitiwaji, ijo anotonitelocotiwaji nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate manigoti. Ica eledi baЙЎМ¶a analakenitiniwace catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adiiakanaЙЎМ¶axiiditiwaji, codaa me iatenitibece, odaa jaЙЎМ¶awii me daleditibigimoace odeletalo eletidi nigotadi.  
\v 35 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji makaami laagetedipi leeЙЎМ¶odi lemeЙЎМ¶egi ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji anonigodi, odoejegi moyeloadi Abel ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a, lionigi niЙЎМ¶ijo odoejegi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa AdГЈo, neЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶otota moyeloadi Zacarias, lionigi Baraquias, naiigo ЙЎМ¶adoiigitiwaji, anoyeli wetice AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, ipegitege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nameeja.  
\v 36 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji iloikatidi niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi aninaa niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi leeЙЎМ¶odi laijedi. 
\s1 Jesus eliodi me iwikode niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi JerusalГ©m 
\r (Lucas 13.34-35) 
\p  
\v 37 Eliodi me ЙЎМ¶adigecaЙЎМ¶aleЙЎМ¶enitiwaji, anakaami niЙЎМ¶eladimigipitigi JerusalГ©m! LeeЙЎМ¶odi manigotitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko, codaa anigidaatiniwace manigoti niЙЎМ¶ijo ane niiЙЎМ¶etedaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Elioditibece me domaЙЎМ¶a jemaa me ЙЎМ¶adatecoЙЎМ¶oteenitiwaji me idoweditaЙЎМ¶aloco, macataЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ana okoЙЎМ¶okoodi me yatecoЙЎМ¶otee lionaЙЎМ¶a catiwedi labadi, pida aЙЎМ¶emaanitiwaji.  
\v 38 Natigide, liЙЎМ¶eladi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anini makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji icota moyaladi, leeЙЎМ¶odi me diЙЎМ¶icoateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane nebi.  
\v 39 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. Icota me daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica madatitiwaji nigepaaЙЎМ¶icota niЙЎМ¶ica noko nigenitiwaji, вҖҳJemaanaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ibinie NiЙЎМ¶inoa anenagi anida naЙЎМ¶atetigi LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖҷвҖқ 
\c 24  
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶ate micota moyojiketini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi 
\r (Marcos 13.1-2; Lucas 21.5-6) 
\p  
\v 1 Jesus noditedicogi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶opi, niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶odipegitege, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyalaЙЎМ¶ata AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi me nelegi codaa me libinienigi.  
\v 2 Odaa Jesus ja niniЙЎМ¶oditediogi, mee, вҖңJaЙЎМ¶anatitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ini diimigi libinienigi. EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. Icota anigida noko me daЙЎМ¶aca wetiЙЎМ¶a ane yeyaЙЎМ¶ateloco eledi wetiЙЎМ¶a, leeЙЎМ¶odi initawece oyaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ini diimigi.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus yalaЙЎМ¶ate icoa nawikodico anenagi 
\r (Marcos 13.3-13; Lucas 21.8-19) 
\p  
\v 3 Jesus idiaa nicote minitaЙЎМ¶a lojotaЙЎМ¶adi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңLojotaЙЎМ¶adi OliveiraвҖқ. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶oyatecoЙЎМ¶otelogo, odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, oniboloite maleediЙЎМ¶ica eledi oko, moditalo, вҖңIgaatigi ica nigoyojiketini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi? Codaa igamodaaЙЎМ¶ee ica me ikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nigadopilitijo, codaa igaatigi ica nige daa ina iiЙЎМ¶o?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 4 Jesus ja niniЙЎМ¶odi, meetediogi, вҖңAdinowetitiwaji adiЙЎМ¶ica ane ЙЎМ¶adinaaleni.  
\v 5 IgaataЙЎМ¶a eliodi oko enagitibeci, odaa oibake IboonaЙЎМ¶adi, codaa modi, вҖҳJeЙЎМ¶emeЙЎМ¶ee ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me jiЙЎМ¶eke inatawece ЙЎМ¶odaxakawepodi.вҖҷ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oninaaletiniwace eliodi oko.  
\v 6 Codaa jinaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶owikomataatiwaji nigajipaata layaco witidi, codaa nigabodicetibige noiigi me nidelaЙЎМ¶a. IgaataЙЎМ¶a leeditibige minoa nidelakadi. Pida anaЙЎМ¶a ipegiteloco liniogo niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o.  
\v 7 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi dinideleЙЎМ¶etiwage, codaa niЙЎМ¶inoa inionaЙЎМ¶a-eloodoli dinideleЙЎМ¶etiwage. Odaa eliodi mina nigigi, codaa me neelotika ane waxodi, codaa datalale iiЙЎМ¶o, aЙЎМ¶icaadeЙЎМ¶ite.  
\v 8 Inoatawece niЙЎМ¶inoa nawikodico liciaco odoejedi lileenaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egi iwaalo me dinigaje. 
\p  
\v 9 NigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶aneloЙЎМ¶ododipi etiЙЎМ¶adiwilotiwaji, odaa etiЙЎМ¶adajicitiogi ane niiЙЎМ¶enatakanaЙЎМ¶a metiЙЎМ¶adiloikatiti codaa metiЙЎМ¶adeloati. Codaa inatawece noiigi akaami neleЙЎМ¶etedipi leeЙЎМ¶odi maniwiticitiwaji.  
\v 10 Odaa eliodi oko eyamaЙЎМ¶atice eliwaЙЎМ¶atakaneЙЎМ¶egi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyajigo niЙЎМ¶ina anepaЙЎМ¶alee etidadiwaЙЎМ¶ati, oyajigotiogi neloЙЎМ¶ododipi, odaa neleЙЎМ¶etedipi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoniotici.  
\v 11 Codaa eliodi awitakaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anicota menotibeci, odaa modi moyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko, odaa joЙЎМ¶oninaaletiniwace eliodi oko.  
\v 12 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko jeЙЎМ¶epaa noЙЎМ¶owo niЙЎМ¶inoa ane beyagi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ina oko aЙЎМ¶alee dinemaa.  
\v 13 Pida niЙЎМ¶ina ane dinatitalo inoatawece ane lawikodico, codaa ane daЙЎМ¶a ika me idadiwaЙЎМ¶adi, joaniЙЎМ¶iniaa biЙЎМ¶ida lewiЙЎМ¶a ane diЙЎМ¶ica liniogo meetaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 14 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegitedibece nibodicetedi anele anoditece niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali oko, codaa oyatematitedibece niЙЎМ¶inoa nibodicetedi anele. Oyatematitiogi inoatawece nipodaЙЎМ¶a, oyeloЙЎМ¶oditiogi noiigi me yemaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iiЙЎМ¶e laaleЙЎМ¶enali. Odaa jeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a icota liniogo niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o. 
\s1 Ica nawikodigi nelegi 
\r (Marcos 13.14-23; Lucas 21.20-24) 
\p  
\v 15-16 Daniel, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, mee moyojogotini ica niwigo ane ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi liwilanigi minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi. (NiЙЎМ¶ina ane yalomeЙЎМ¶eteloco niЙЎМ¶inoa notaЙЎМ¶a leeditibige me yowooЙЎМ¶odi ane diitigilo.) Enice, nigicota manati niЙЎМ¶ida niwigo minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, niЙЎМ¶ina oko aneitelogo nipodaЙЎМ¶a JudГ©ia, leeditibige me daleditibige, odeletibigimece wetiadi.  
\v 17 Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane anipetini ditibigimedi liЙЎМ¶eladi, leeditibige me diЙЎМ¶igo dakatiwece liЙЎМ¶eladi me dibatalo ane nepilidi, pida leeditibige me dinagetice melodi.  
\v 18 Codaa niЙЎМ¶ina ane ideitice lixoЙЎМ¶otagi, aЙЎМ¶ele daЙЎМ¶a dopitijo me dibata nibalito.  
\v 19 Nagoodoli niЙЎМ¶ina iwaalepodi ipilaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a codaa niЙЎМ¶ina baЙЎМ¶alee oilipeЙЎМ¶e lionigi nigicotalo niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi ane doide!  
\v 20 Ipokitalotiwaji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me daЙЎМ¶adaletitibige me limedi niwetaЙЎМ¶a, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina saabado.  
\v 21 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica nawikodigi anenagi eliodi me ЙЎМ¶onitiЙЎМ¶a. AniЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico liciaco niЙЎМ¶icoa anenagi, niЙЎМ¶ijo maleekoka dinoe niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o. Codaa aЙЎМ¶icota micoa eletidi nawikodico liciaco niЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico.  
\v 22 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji noxopanatidi nokododi niЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico. DaaditaЙЎМ¶a noxopanatiditeda niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi, agotiЙЎМ¶ica ane dinatitalo niЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico. Pida leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi oko ane iolatedicoace me nepilidi, AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji noxopanatidi niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi niЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico. 
\p  
\v 23 Nigica aneetaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji, вҖҳDigawini, etidoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶odacilo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane niiЙЎМ¶e me iЙЎМ¶eke ЙЎМ¶odaxakawepodi!вҖҷ, oЙЎМ¶oa, domigetaЙЎМ¶a eetaЙЎМ¶awa, вҖҳEtidoa digoida!вҖҷ Pida jinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a iwaЙЎМ¶ati.  
\v 24 IgaataЙЎМ¶a icota mowidi anodinanatigi me ЙЎМ¶odacilodi, codaa icota meliodi anodi miniЙЎМ¶ina anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko, pida niwitakaЙЎМ¶a. Codaa owote ЙЎМ¶odoxiceЙЎМ¶etedi anoikee loniciwaЙЎМ¶a, odoletibige moninaaletiniwace niЙЎМ¶ina oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iolatedicoace me nepilidi, odineetiogi doЙЎМ¶oyakadi moninaaletiniwace.  
\v 25 Atacolitiwaji! IgaataЙЎМ¶a jao ЙЎМ¶abodigi maleediЙЎМ¶icotalo niЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico. 
\p  
\v 26 NiЙЎМ¶ina nigodi, вҖҳDigawinitiwaji! NiЙЎМ¶ijoa ane niiЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji etidoa midi nipodigi ane yadilo ane diЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶eladimigipi.вҖҷ JinaЙЎМ¶a domeЙЎМ¶emii! OЙЎМ¶oa, domigetaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina nigodi, вҖҳEtiniwa dinaЙЎМ¶aditedini digoina liЙЎМ¶eladiвҖҷ, jinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶a iwaЙЎМ¶atitiwaji.  
\v 27 IgaataЙЎМ¶a Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, nigicota me idinikee, micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina nalebepaЙЎМ¶a ane Гӯdi digoida ditibigimedi, dalebepe digoida nigoi nigepaa ane diiticogi aligeЙЎМ¶e me dalimeti.  
\v 28 IgaataЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶a ane diЙЎМ¶etigi anigidi Г©meЙЎМ¶egi, leeЙЎМ¶odi opoedi. 
\s1 Lanokegi Jesus, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane icoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi 
\r (Marcos 13.24-27; Lucas 21.25-28) 
\p  
\v 29 Nige leecawaanigi me ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo niЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico, odaa aligeЙЎМ¶e ipe, codaa epenai aЙЎМ¶alee datale. Yotetitedi enitedini, icoЙЎМ¶otedibigimece ditibigimedi, odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja itineЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ica loniciwaЙЎМ¶a ditibigimedi.  
\v 30 Odaa AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ikee ganigica digoida ditibigimedi, ane ikee naЙЎМ¶a limedi me dinikee niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЗӨoneleegiwa ane icoЙЎМ¶otedibigimece ditibigimedi. Odaa inatawece oko niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o doitibigiwaji, codaa agecaЙЎМ¶alodipi nigonadi niЙЎМ¶ica ane ikee AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji digoida ditibigimedi. Codaa inatawece oko onadi niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЗӨoneleegiwa ane icoЙЎМ¶otedibigimece ditibigimedi nige limedi menagi, niotedinece lolaadi. Nigenagi, nadeegi epaa loniciwaЙЎМ¶a, codaa datale liciagi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 31 Odaa ja iiЙЎМ¶e niaanjotedi, odaa inatawece oko owajipata layaageЙЎМ¶egi aca goloneeta. Odaa aanjotedi joЙЎМ¶odigoteloco inoatawece ane liwailidi iiЙЎМ¶o, oyatecoЙЎМ¶otee inatawece oko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iolatedicoace me nepilidi, anilaagiteloco inatawece iiЙЎМ¶o. 
\s1 Ica ane ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶axitece fiigoigo 
\r (Marcos 13.28-31; Lucas 21.29-33) 
\p  
\v 32 Atacolitece ane ЙЎМ¶odiiЙЎМ¶axitece libatadi fiigo. NiЙЎМ¶ina naЙЎМ¶a dione libiwedi, ina laamotiidi naЙЎМ¶a nokoloЙЎМ¶o, odaa joЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji naЙЎМ¶a nipegi me dioneteloco nipodigi.  
\v 33 JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee niganatitiwaji micota niЙЎМ¶ida anejita, odaa joЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti me daЙЎМ¶alee eliodi ЙЎМ¶animedi, odaa jeЙЎМ¶enagi niЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico.  
\v 34 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ica oko ane newiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶icoa nokododi oixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedijo icoatawece niЙЎМ¶icoa nawikodico anenagi.  
\v 35 Ditibigimedi codaa me iiЙЎМ¶o icota me ma, pida yotaЙЎМ¶a biЙЎМ¶idioka limedi midiwa, codaa icota micotece ane igegi. 
\s1 Ica noko nige dopitedijo Jesus 
\r (Marcos 13.32-37; Lucas 17.26-30, 34-36) 
\p  
\v 36 AЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica noko oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶aca lakata nige janagitace. OteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a aanjotedi digoida ditibigimedi aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi, oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a Ee, Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Pida iniokiniwateda AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane Eiodi baЙЎМ¶a yowooЙЎМ¶odi.  
\v 37 Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, nige janagi, anee me newiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica oko liciagi niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide niЙЎМ¶ica oko malee yewiЙЎМ¶a NoГ©.  
\v 38 IgaataЙЎМ¶a maleediЙЎМ¶ica abooЙЎМ¶o-ninyoЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica oko niodaЙЎМ¶a, nacipaЙЎМ¶a, nadonaЙЎМ¶a, codaa moyajigo lionigipi moyadoneЙЎМ¶e neЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶icota noko niЙЎМ¶ijo NoГ© naЙЎМ¶a dakatiwece etogo-nelegi.  
\v 39 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo oko aЙЎМ¶oyowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica anicota me ninyaagi, neЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶icota menagi abooЙЎМ¶o-ninyoЙЎМ¶odi, odaa ijotawece oceЙЎМ¶egipi. JiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee lakataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ica oko nige nipegi me idopitijo, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi.  
\v 40 NiЙЎМ¶ica noko iniwataale ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi odibateloco nipodigi. Odaa aanjotedi onidateci oyadeegi, ideЙЎМ¶eledi baЙЎМ¶a nenyaЙЎМ¶ati.  
\v 41 Iniwataale iwaalepodi oyojogo leyeema. Odaa aanjotedi oyadeegi onaniteci, pida aniaaЙЎМ¶eledi baЙЎМ¶a nenyaЙЎМ¶atini. 
\p  
\v 42 Enice adinenyaЙЎМ¶atitiwaji! IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti niЙЎМ¶ica noko nigeno ЗӨaniotagodi.  
\v 43 AjawienatakanaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane nebi diimigi daЙЎМ¶a yowooЙЎМ¶odi noko micotio oliceЙЎМ¶egi, daЙЎМ¶a yowooЙЎМ¶odi taЙЎМ¶a dinowedi agotaЙЎМ¶a ika oliceЙЎМ¶egi me yawime nibaloote me dakatio.  
\v 44 Enice adinenyaЙЎМ¶atitiwaji! IgaataЙЎМ¶a Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, janagi niЙЎМ¶ica noko maleedaЙЎМ¶anibeoonitege me janagi. 
\s1 Ica nimeedi aneo ane iiЙЎМ¶eta necalailegi icaaЙЎМ¶ica eledi ane deЙЎМ¶eo 
\r (Lucas 12.41-48) 
\p  
\v 45 Odaa ica niotagi aninoa lixaketedi, anoyakadi monakato, joaniЙЎМ¶ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yajigota niotagodi me dowediteloco eletidi liotaka. Yajigotiogi anoyeligo niЙЎМ¶idiwa eletidi niimetedi ditibigimedi lakata.  
\v 46 NiЙЎМ¶ijo niotagi eliodi me ninitibece nigenota necalailegi leeЙЎМ¶odi meo ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 47 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ini niotagodi icota me yajigota niЙЎМ¶ijo limeedi me doweditelogo idiwatawece ane nepilidi.  
\v 48 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo nimeedi anoyajigota me nowienaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a niginiЙЎМ¶ina ane beyagi, odaa meetibige le, вҖҳIniotagodi leegi nige dopitijo.вҖҷ  
\v 49 OditaЙЎМ¶a nalaketiniwace lokaaЙЎМ¶etedi me niba, ligiiwepodi codaa lacipaЙЎМ¶awepodi niЙЎМ¶inoa acipaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 50 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ini niotagodi dopitijo niЙЎМ¶ica noko maleedaЙЎМ¶a nibeotege, codaa me naЙЎМ¶aca lakata me daЙЎМ¶a eetibige niЙЎМ¶ijo liotagi.  
\v 51 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagodi niwiigitibige, odaa eote lawikodigi liciagi lawikodigi niЙЎМ¶ina anokowo me libinienigipi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ica oko nacaagaЙЎМ¶ateloco codaa moyacigice lowe leeЙЎМ¶odi lawikodico. 
\c 25  
\s1 Jesus yatemati natematigigi ica deez awicijipi 
\p  
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ica noko nige janagi me jiiЙЎМ¶e inoatawece, digawini ane jiciaceeketege. Jiciaceeketege deez awicijipi ane nodenigipi migotibeci ica lalokegi nadoneЙЎМ¶egi, noЙЎМ¶odibatalo loledaЙЎМ¶axiidi, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci odakapetege niЙЎМ¶ijo ane wado.  
\v 2 Ciinco niЙЎМ¶idi awicijipi yetoledi, pida icoa eletidi ciinco baЙЎМ¶a niwaxinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶icoa yetoledi oyadeegi loledaЙЎМ¶axiidi, pida aЙЎМ¶oyadeegi lajidi.  
\v 4 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo awicijipi ane niwaxinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a boЙЎМ¶oyadeegi loledaЙЎМ¶axiidi me nolee codaa ida najidi ane iiЙЎМ¶otice.  
\v 5 NiЙЎМ¶ijo ane wado naЙЎМ¶a dinopaЙЎМ¶adi meno, odaa ijotawece nibaciЙЎМ¶ateloco, odaa ja niotaЙЎМ¶a. 
\p  
\v 6 NaЙЎМ¶a liwigo-enoale jiЙЎМ¶ida ica ane dapaawe, onee, вҖҳDigawinitege! NiЙЎМ¶ijo ane wado jeЙЎМ¶eno, anagi akapetetegetiwaji!вҖҷ  
\v 7 Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo awicijipi ja niwoditibigiwaji, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyalegi loledaЙЎМ¶axiidi.  
\v 8 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo awicijipi yetoledi moditiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane niwaxinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, вҖҳЗӨodedianeЙЎМ¶egodi okateciЙЎМ¶ida ЙЎМ¶anajidi, igaataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶odoledaЙЎМ¶axiidi ja dineliotedini.вҖҷ  
\v 9 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo awicijipi ane niwaxinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a joЙЎМ¶oniniЙЎМ¶odi, moditiogi, вҖҳAЙЎМ¶ica ЙЎМ¶onimaweneЙЎМ¶egi! AЙЎМ¶eliodi ЙЎМ¶onajidi, aЙЎМ¶abo-oo me joweenaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji. Emiitiwaji manitaЙЎМ¶a oojetekaxi, anoojeteeta ЙЎМ¶anajidi!вҖҷ  
\v 10 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo awicijipi yetoledi jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci odinoojetetigi najidi. Odaa aniЙЎМ¶ica me dopitijo, neЙЎМ¶eno niЙЎМ¶ijo ane wado. NiЙЎМ¶ijo awicijipi ane niwaxinaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a baanaЙЎМ¶a nigomaЙЎМ¶a, odaa joЙЎМ¶odiotiwece niЙЎМ¶ijo ane wado midi lalokegi nadoneЙЎМ¶egi. Odaa epoagi ja dinoxoco. 
\p  
\v 11 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi jeЙЎМ¶enotibeci niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi awicijipi, odaa ja napaawaЙЎМ¶ateloco, modi, вҖҳЗӨoniwa-aagodi! ЗӨoniwa-aagodi! OmokenitoЙЎМ¶odomi epoagi!вҖҷ  
\v 12 Pida naЙЎМ¶a niniЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane wado, meetiogi, вҖҳEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ida mee aЙЎМ¶akaami yowooЙЎМ¶otagipi.вҖҷвҖқ 
\p  
\v 13 Odaa meetediogi Jesus, вҖңEnice adinowetitiwaji! IgaataЙЎМ¶a aЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ica noko oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶aca lakata nige idopitijo Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi.вҖқ 
\s1 Natematigigi icoa itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida niimetedi 
\r (Lucas 19.11-27) 
\p  
\v 14 Odaa Jesus eЙЎМ¶idaa diitigi me dotaЙЎМ¶a, meetediogi, вҖңDigawini ane jiciaceeketege nige janagi me jiiЙЎМ¶e inoatawece. Jiciaceeketege ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane diniwiajeticogi ditigedi. Odaa maleedaЙЎМ¶a noditice, jeЙЎМ¶eniditiogi liimetedi, odaa ja yajigotiogi modoweditelogo ane nepilidi.  
\v 15 Ica odoejegi yajigota ciinco jaaco nolee beexotedi oolo, ica eledi baЙЎМ¶a yajigota itoataale jaaco nolee beexotedi oolo, ica eledi baЙЎМ¶a yajigota onadateci jaaco. Eote niЙЎМ¶ida anigotiogi leeЙЎМ¶odi yowooЙЎМ¶odi onidateci limeedi ida epaa lixakedi adiniciamico. Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja diniwiaje.  
\v 16 AЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane dibatege ciinco jaacotedi ja ibake niЙЎМ¶ijoa dinyeelo meo nigaanye. Odaa ja dinigaanyetece eletidi ciinco jaacotedi dinyeelo.  
\v 17 NiЙЎМ¶ijo nimeedi ane dibatege itoataale jaacotedi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ibake niЙЎМ¶ijoa dinyeelo, odaa ja dinigaanyetece eletidi itoataale jaaco nolee beexotedi oolo.  
\v 18 Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo ane dibatege onadateci jaaco baЙЎМ¶a naligitini, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶igota naЙЎМ¶ajo jaaco ane nolee beexotedi oolo, jiЙЎМ¶idaa nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me yaЙЎМ¶aditedini me yotete ninyeelo necalailegi. 
\p  
\v 19 IgaanaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo owidi nokododi, niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagodi niЙЎМ¶ijoa niimetedi ja dopitijo, odaa ja ilakidetedini naalewe.  
\v 20 NiЙЎМ¶ijo nimeedi ane dibatege ciinco jaaco beexo niЙЎМ¶icotio, ja yopilaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijoa dinyeelo ane dibatege, codaa iwaЙЎМ¶ateetece eletidi ciinco jaacotedi ane dinigaanyetece. Odaa mee, вҖҳIniotagodi, geme anajicitediwa ciinco jaaco nolee beexotedi oolo. Odaa inigaanyetece eletidi ciinco jaacotedi dinyeelo. Digawini, etinoa idiwatawece!вҖҷ  
\v 21 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagodi meeta, вҖҳEliodi mele ЙЎМ¶abakedi! Akaami ЙЎМ¶owotagi anele ane jakataЙЎМ¶a me jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a. JiЙЎМ¶ikeeni me jakadi me ЙЎМ¶adinakatonitema niЙЎМ¶ina anokateciЙЎМ¶ini. Natigide ЙЎМ¶adixomitio madowetiteloco niЙЎМ¶ina aneliodi. Anagi, akaami inikaЙЎМ¶awa!вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 22 NiЙЎМ¶ijo niotagi ane dibatege itoataale jaaco beexotedi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶icotio, odaa mee, вҖҳIniotagodi, geme anajicitediwa itoataale jaaco beexotedi oolo, odaa inigaanyetece eletidi itoataale jaaco dinyeelo. Digawini, etinoa idiwatawece!вҖҷ  
\v 23 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagodi jeЙЎМ¶eeta, вҖҳEliodi mele ЙЎМ¶abakedi! Akaami niotagi anele ane jakataЙЎМ¶a me jinakatonaЙЎМ¶a. JiЙЎМ¶ikeeni me jakadi me ЙЎМ¶adinakatonitema niЙЎМ¶ina anokateciЙЎМ¶ini. Natigide ЙЎМ¶adixomitio me iiЙЎМ¶eni anowidi. Anagi, akaami inikaЙЎМ¶awa!вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 24 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶eno niЙЎМ¶ijo niotagi ane dibatege onadateci jaaco dinyeelo, odaa mee, вҖҳIniotagodi, jowooЙЎМ¶odi makaami ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane dakake laaleЙЎМ¶ena, odaa idoitaЙЎМ¶awa. Anoteci codaa matecoЙЎМ¶oteeni niЙЎМ¶ina ane daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶atanigijegi.  
\v 25 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi me idoi, odaa jeЙЎМ¶ejigo, jaЙЎМ¶aditedini niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶aninyeelo, inaligitedini. Digawini, etinoa ЙЎМ¶aninyeelo!вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 26 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo necalailegi jeЙЎМ¶eeta, вҖҳAkaami niЙЎМ¶ica nimeedi ane beyagi codaa me nigojigo! Menitiwa me ee ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane dakake laaleЙЎМ¶ena, codaa me inopilaЙЎМ¶aditedio ane daЙЎМ¶a yawodigijedi, codaa me jatecoЙЎМ¶otee ane daЙЎМ¶a eyanigijedi.  
\v 27 Odaa akaami daЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ixomitiwece baanco ininyeelo, daЙЎМ¶anagawini jibatege ininyeelo codaa me lionaЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶a idopitijo.вҖҷ  
\v 28 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo necalailegi meetiogi icoa eletidi liotaka, вҖҳAbaatege ninyeelo, odaa ajicita niЙЎМ¶ijo anidiwa deez nijaaco dinyeelo!  
\v 29 IgaataЙЎМ¶a jajigota caticedi niЙЎМ¶ijo anidiwa nepilidi, odaa jeЙЎМ¶epaanaЙЎМ¶a owidi ane nepilidi. Pida niЙЎМ¶ijo ane diЙЎМ¶ica nebi, jibanootece, codaa niЙЎМ¶inoa anokateciЙЎМ¶inoa ane nepilidi eletidi jibanootece.  
\v 30 Natigide okoleniticogi niЙЎМ¶ini niotagi ane diЙЎМ¶ica aneletema digoida wetice midi nexocaЙЎМ¶a ane lawikodadi oko. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶i oko me nacaagaЙЎМ¶ateloco codaa moyacigice lowe leeЙЎМ¶odi lawikodico.вҖҷ 
\s1 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji icota me iwi anigotediogi oko codaa me iloikatidi 
\p  
\v 31 Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, janagi me Ee inionigi-eliodi, ixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi iniaanjotedi. Nige janagi, idicoteloco baanco ЙЎМ¶oneЙЎМ¶e me jiiЙЎМ¶e codaa me jiwi anejigota niЙЎМ¶ina oko leeЙЎМ¶odi loenataka.  
\v 32 Odaa inatawece oko minoataЙЎМ¶a digawinitelogo ane latopaco noiigi yatecoЙЎМ¶o yodoe. Odaa jiolaticoace oko micataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina nowienoЙЎМ¶odi waxacocoli me iomaЙЎМ¶aditege waxacocoli, waxigidatedi.  
\v 33 Odaa idejate niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji ane jiciaceeketege lapo waxacocoli iwai ibaaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ina oko abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ane jiciaceeketege waxigida baЙЎМ¶a ideja inimagijegi.  
\v 34 Odaa Ee, ane Ee inionigi-eliodi, ejitiogi niЙЎМ¶idi ane idei ibaaЙЎМ¶adi, вҖҳAnagitiwaji ane ЙЎМ¶adibinieni Eiodi! Anakaatiobece miniwataЙЎМ¶a Eiodi, miditaЙЎМ¶a ane ilakidetedaЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji maleediЙЎМ¶icatibige me yoe niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o.  
\v 35 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЙЎМ¶adibinienitetiwaji leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo me idigicile, odaa adedianitece ane jeligo. NiЙЎМ¶ijo me ideloadi ecibi, odaa ja adacipeЙЎМ¶eni ninyoЙЎМ¶odi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo me iciagi niЙЎМ¶ina icoЙЎМ¶egi, odaa ele mabaatigitiwaji ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi.  
\v 36 NiЙЎМ¶ijo me daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica yowoodaЙЎМ¶agi, odaa jaЙЎМ¶adinixomeЙЎМ¶eni. NiЙЎМ¶ijo me jeelotika, odaa jaЙЎМ¶anootiwatiwaji madaxawani. Codaa niЙЎМ¶ijo me idiniwilo, odaa jaЙЎМ¶adaliitiwatiwaji.вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 37 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idi oko aneletibigiwaji etidige, moditiwa, вҖҳЗӨoniotagodi, igaatigi ica me ЙЎМ¶adateЙЎМ¶egi manigicile, odaa ja jajicaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶awa anelici, codaa igaatigi ica me ЙЎМ¶adeloati ecibi, odaa ja jajicaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶awa ninyoЙЎМ¶odi?  
\v 38 Igaatigi ica me ЙЎМ¶adateЙЎМ¶egi me ЙЎМ¶adiciagi icoЙЎМ¶egi, odaa ele me jibaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶agi catiwedi ЙЎМ¶odiЙЎМ¶eladi? Codaa igaatigi ica me ЙЎМ¶adateЙЎМ¶egi me diЙЎМ¶icoa ЙЎМ¶adowoodi, odaa ja ЙЎМ¶adinixomeЙЎМ¶eneЙЎМ¶egi?  
\v 39 Codaa igaatigi ica me ЙЎМ¶adateЙЎМ¶egi me eelotikani, odaaЙЎМ¶ejoЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶awa me ЙЎМ¶adaxawaneЙЎМ¶egi? Codaa igaatigi ica me ЙЎМ¶adateЙЎМ¶egi madiniwilo, odaa ja idaliiЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶awa?вҖҷ  
\v 40 Odaa nige jigidi, ejitiogi, вҖҳEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo maxawanitiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo ane daЙЎМ¶axa me iwikodadipi liwigotigi inioxoadipi, micataЙЎМ¶a daanteЙЎМ¶emaЙЎМ¶a aniЙЎМ¶iwaatici.вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 41 Odaa Ee, ane Ee inionigi-eliodi, ejitiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo ane idei iwai inimagijegi, вҖҳAdeteceniticetiwaji, anakaami laagetedipi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji! Emiitiwaji minitaЙЎМ¶a noledi ane yoetetema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji diaabo idiaa niwicidi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a!  
\v 42 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yelatedaЙЎМ¶adomi leeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo me idigicile, aЙЎМ¶anajicitiwa ane jeligo. NiЙЎМ¶ijo me ideloadi ecibi, aЙЎМ¶anajicitiwa ninyoЙЎМ¶odi me jacipe.  
\v 43 NiЙЎМ¶ijo me iciagi niЙЎМ¶ina icoЙЎМ¶egi, aЙЎМ¶ele mabaatigitiwaji catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo me daЙЎМ¶adiaaЙЎМ¶ica yowoodaЙЎМ¶agi, aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a adinixomeЙЎМ¶eni. NiЙЎМ¶ijo me jeelotika codaa niЙЎМ¶ijo me idiniwilo, aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶adaliitiwatiwaji.вҖҷ 
\p  
\v 44 Odaa etidige, moditiwa, вҖҳЗӨoniotagodi, igaatigi naЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adateЙЎМ¶egi manigicile, codaa me ЙЎМ¶adeloati ecibi? Igaatigi ica me ЙЎМ¶adateЙЎМ¶egi me ЙЎМ¶adiciagi icoЙЎМ¶egi, codaa me diЙЎМ¶icoateda ЙЎМ¶adowoodi, oЙЎМ¶oa migetaЙЎМ¶a eelotikani, oЙЎМ¶oa migetaЙЎМ¶a madiniwilo, odaa aЙЎМ¶adaxawaneЙЎМ¶egi?вҖҷ  
\v 45 Odaa ejitiogi, Ee, ane Ee inionigi-eliodi, вҖҳEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo me daЙЎМ¶a axawanitatiwaji niЙЎМ¶ina oko iwikodadipi, odaa micataЙЎМ¶a me daЙЎМ¶a adaxawani.вҖҷ  
\v 46 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idi oko igotibeci miditaЙЎМ¶a ane lawikodadi oko, aneitice nawikodigi ane diЙЎМ¶ica liniogo, leeЙЎМ¶otedi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco. Pida niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane iЙЎМ¶enaЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji biЙЎМ¶idioka limedi me newiЙЎМ¶a miniwataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ 
\c 26  
\s1 Icoa lacilodi noiigi judeu dinilakidetiwage moyeloadi Jesus 
\r (Marcos 14.1-2; Lucas 22.1-2; JoГЈo 11.45-53) 
\p  
\v 1 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a nigotedini Jesus me yalaЙЎМ¶ate idiwatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa niiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco, odaa meetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece,  
\v 2 вҖңJoЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶otitiwaji aniaditibige itoataale nokododi, odaa ja nakatio nalokegi вҖҳPГЎscoaвҖҷ. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶icota metidajigo metidototeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate metideloadi, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 3 Odaa ja yatecoЙЎМ¶o niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, icaaЙЎМ¶icoa laxokodi lacilodi judeutedi. YatecoЙЎМ¶otibigiwaji minitaЙЎМ¶a liЙЎМ¶eladi-nelegi niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi, anodita CaifГЎs.  
\v 4 Odaa joЙЎМ¶odinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etigi ane nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi moniwilo Jesus codaa odinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etigi moyeloadi me diЙЎМ¶ica ane yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi-nelegi.  
\v 5 Pida modi, вҖңAjakataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a jibaЙЎМ¶atalo niЙЎМ¶ina malee nalooЙЎМ¶o ade jaoЙЎМ¶a magecaЙЎМ¶alodipi niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi codaa ade jaoЙЎМ¶a metiЙЎМ¶odideleЙЎМ¶e.вҖқ 
\s1 Aca iwaalo yadotelogo Jesus ica nadokojegi 
\r (Marcos 14.3-9; JoГЈo 12.1-8) 
\p  
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus midiaaЙЎМ¶ite manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotakawaana ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi BetГўnia, liЙЎМ¶eladi SimГЈo ane nikoxeedi me вҖңDawace-lolaadiвҖқ,  
\v 7 jiЙЎМ¶icotalo ajo iwaalo ane yadeegi aca naЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi, wetiЙЎМ¶a anodita вҖңalabastroвҖқ. NaЙЎМ¶ajo naЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi nolee ladokojegi ane dakake loojedi, anoibake moyatita lolaadi Г©meЙЎМ¶egi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo Jesus naЙЎМ¶a dawaketedeloco nameeja maniodi, odaa naЙЎМ¶ajo iwaalo ja yadotedeloco ladokojegi lacilo.  
\v 8 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece noЙЎМ¶onadi, ja neliЙЎМ¶ideeЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja dinige, modi me dinotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶etiwage, вҖңIgaamee ada iwaalo me yaaЙЎМ¶adi ida nadokojegi?  
\v 9 DaЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a eyaa niЙЎМ¶ida nadokojegi me yakakaЙЎМ¶adi loojedi, oditaЙЎМ¶a iboo ninyeelo me yaxawatiogi madewetedipi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 10 Jesus yowooЙЎМ¶oditediwe lowoogo, odaa meetediogi, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi ina malomeЙЎМ¶eni ada iwaalo leeЙЎМ¶odi ida aneo? Eotomi niЙЎМ¶ida ane daЙЎМ¶axa me libinienigi.  
\v 11 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina madewetedipi idioka limedi mina makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji, pida Ee baadiЙЎМ¶idioka limedi minaaЙЎМ¶ejo makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji.  
\v 12 NiЙЎМ¶ijo me yadoteloco yolaadi niЙЎМ¶ijo ladokojegi, ja ideyaЙЎМ¶aditema nigetidaligitini.  
\v 13 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ina oko moyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece nibodicetedi anele okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica aneitice niЙЎМ¶ina iiЙЎМ¶o, oyatemati niЙЎМ¶ina monalaЙЎМ¶atibige niЙЎМ¶ida loenatagi naЙЎМ¶ada iwaalo.вҖқ 
\s1 Judas dinilakidetege niЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi judeutedi neloЙЎМ¶ododipi Jesus 
\r (Marcos 14.10-11; Lucas 22.3-6) 
\p  
\v 14 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi onijoteci niЙЎМ¶ijo dooze anodiotibece, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi Judas Iscariotes, jiЙЎМ¶igo yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi.  
\v 15 Odaa meetiogi, вҖңIgametaЙЎМ¶a liwokodi madedianitiwaji, daЙЎМ¶a jajigotedaЙЎМ¶awa Jesus?вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶onilaЙЎМ¶adi triinta beexotedi, moyedia.  
\v 16 IjaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa nokododi, Judas ja doletibige nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me yajigo Jesus. 
\s1 Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece oyeligo liweenigi PГЎscoa 
\r (Marcos 14.12-21; Lucas 22.7-14, 21-23; JoГЈo 13.21-30) 
\p  
\v 17 NoЙЎМ¶odoejegi noko nalokegi anodita вҖңPaon ane diЙЎМ¶ica labookojegiвҖқ, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus joЙЎМ¶odiitalo, odaa joЙЎМ¶oige, moditalo, вҖңIgamemaani mejonaЙЎМ¶a me joenaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶oweenigi me PГЎscoa?вҖқ  
\v 18 Odaa ja niniЙЎМ¶odi, meetediogi, вҖңEmiitiwaji nigotaЙЎМ¶a, oleetibige jiЙЎМ¶icaa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, odaaЙЎМ¶enita, вҖҳЗӨoniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi mee, вҖңJiЙЎМ¶icota noko AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane nibikotatedomi. Jeligo liweenigi PГЎscoa me igiiwepodi anoniotibici digoina ЙЎМ¶adiЙЎМ¶eladi.вҖқ вҖҷвҖқ  
\v 19 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece joЙЎМ¶owo ane iiЙЎМ¶ete Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyoe liweenigi PГЎscoa. 
\p  
\v 20 IgaanaЙЎМ¶a enoale, Jesus ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece ja nicotiniwace me niodaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 21 EЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me niodaЙЎМ¶a, Jesus neЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. Ini niЙЎМ¶ina akaamitiwaji ane idajigotiogi ineloЙЎМ¶ododipi.вҖқ  
\v 22 Odaa eliodi magecaЙЎМ¶alodipi, odaa oninitecibeci ige, meetalo, вҖңIniotagodi, manige emeЙЎМ¶ee ane ЙЎМ¶adajici?вҖқ  
\v 23 Odaa ja niniЙЎМ¶odi, meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ini ane jibotege me jititinigi liwagedi inipaon, joaniЙЎМ¶iniaa idajigo.  
\v 24 AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi akaa yalaЙЎМ¶ata Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi me ideleo. Pida nagoodi niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane idajigotiogi ineloЙЎМ¶ododipi, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ewi me iloikatidi. DomaЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶axa mele daaditiЙЎМ¶ica menitini niЙЎМ¶ini ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa!вҖқ  
\v 25 Odaa Judas, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yajigo Jesus, jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ige, meetalo, вҖңIniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi, manige emaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adajici?вҖқ Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eeteta, вҖңAdomaЙЎМ¶a leeditibige madigee!вҖқ 
\s1 AnodaaЙЎМ¶ejinaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ЙЎМ¶odalaЙЎМ¶atibige lemeЙЎМ¶egi Jesus 
\r (Marcos 14.22-26; Lucas 22.15-20; 1 CorГӯntios 11.23-25) 
\p  
\v 26 EЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee me niodaЙЎМ¶a, Jesus ja dibate ijo paon, odaa diniotagodetedibigimece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa ja inoke me yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa meetediogi, вҖңAbaatege, odaa elici niЙЎМ¶idi paon! Ane micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a yolaadi.вҖқ  
\v 27 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja dibate ajo goopa ane nolee viinyo, odaa ja diniotagodetedibigimece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa jaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a yajigotediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece naЙЎМ¶ajo goopa, meetediogi, вҖңAcipeta akaamitawecetiwaji!  
\v 28 IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ida viinyo micataЙЎМ¶a daЙЎМ¶a yawodi ane inadooЙЎМ¶odi, jaotibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji mida gela nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi me dinilakidetetege niЙЎМ¶ina oko. Odaa natigide AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji yakadi me iwilegi libeyaceЙЎМ¶eco inatawece oko.  
\v 29 EjitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji anewi. Me daЙЎМ¶adiaa jacipe daЙЎМ¶akaami igiiwepoditece niЙЎМ¶ida viinyo. Pida jacipeta niЙЎМ¶ica gela viinyo makaami igiiwepodi nige jatecoЙЎМ¶ojoЙЎМ¶o miditaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶idi anejonaЙЎМ¶a ane laЙЎМ¶ajegitetema AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji loiigi.вҖқ  
\v 30 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi joЙЎМ¶odigaanaЙЎМ¶atibigimece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci minitaЙЎМ¶a LojotaЙЎМ¶adi Oliveira. 
\s1 Jesus ibodicaxi Pedro 
\r (Marcos 14.27-31; Lucas 22.31-34; JoГЈo 13.36-38) 
\p  
\v 31 Odaa Jesus meetediogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ina enoale akaamitawecetiwaji adalati moka eetece, igaataЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi yalaЙЎМ¶ata ane ligegi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee, вҖҳJeloadi nowienoЙЎМ¶odi waxacocoli, odaa idiwatawece niwaxacocoli ilaagitedibece.вҖҷ  
\v 32 Pida nige idewiЙЎМ¶atace, odaa ejigo idinewade miditaЙЎМ¶a nipodigi GalilГ©ia.вҖқ  
\v 33 Pida Pedro naЙЎМ¶a niniЙЎМ¶odi, meetalo, вҖңIcaaЙЎМ¶ica niginatawece etiЙЎМ¶adalati, pida ee baadaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adalati.вҖқ  
\v 34 Odaa Jesus meeteta, вҖңEjitaЙЎМ¶awa anewi. NiЙЎМ¶ina enoale, aniЙЎМ¶icatibige daЙЎМ¶a anoe okoЙЎМ¶okoodi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ida makaami itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida meni me daЙЎМ¶adowooЙЎМ¶oti.вҖқ  
\v 35 Pedro meetalo, вҖңIcaaЙЎМ¶ica nige leeditibige makaami yemaЙЎМ¶awa, pida baadaЙЎМ¶a adakatiwece yacilo deЙЎМ¶eji me daЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adowooЙЎМ¶oti.вҖқ Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo eledi anodiotibece idaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a oyatigi ligegi. 
\s1 Jesus igo midiwataЙЎМ¶a enanigijedi вҖңoliveiraвҖқ ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi GetsГӘmani 
\r (Marcos 14.32-42; Lucas 22.39-46) 
\p  
\v 36 Odaa Jesus ja lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece midiwataЙЎМ¶a icoa enanigijedi вҖңoliveiraвҖқ anodita GetsГӘmani. Odaa meetediogi, вҖңInaaЙЎМ¶anicootetiwaji digoina. Ejigawaanigi digoida odoe jotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ  
\v 37 Odaa ja yadeegi Pedro me lixigaЙЎМ¶awa ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa itoataale lionaЙЎМ¶a Zebedeu, JoГЈo ijaa Tiago. Odaa eliodi Jesus magecaЙЎМ¶alo, codaa eliodi me doЙЎМ¶owikomata.  
\v 38 Odaa meetediogi, вҖңEliodi me Ee agecaЙЎМ¶alo codaa jeemitetece mica ina daantaЙЎМ¶a doletibige me ideleo. InaaЙЎМ¶onitetiwaji digoina codaa adinowetitiwaji.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 39 Odaa Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igoawaanigi odoe, naЙЎМ¶a yamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi, odaa ja yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, mee, вҖңEiodi, nige yakadi, jiniЙЎМ¶ikani deЙЎМ¶eliodi me jawikode. Pida ajemaa daЙЎМ¶a jao ane emaЙЎМ¶a jemaa, pida jemaa me jao niЙЎМ¶ina anemaani.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 40 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja dopitetege niЙЎМ¶ijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida anodiotibece, odaa jiЙЎМ¶icotediogi me niotaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa meeteta Pedro, вҖңAgodaЙЎМ¶akati doЙЎМ¶okateciЙЎМ¶iniawaanigi maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a adinowetitiwaji?  
\v 41 Adinoweti, codaa otaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, bidige aЙЎМ¶ikani madinakatoni leeЙЎМ¶odi ЙЎМ¶adawikodico. Catiwedi ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali beЙЎМ¶emaani maniwitici, pida ЙЎМ¶adolaadi aЙЎМ¶ica loniciwaЙЎМ¶a otaЙЎМ¶ateciЙЎМ¶ini.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 42 Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igotace yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa mee, вҖңEiodi, nige leeditibige me jixomaЙЎМ¶ateetedijo inoatawece ane yawikodico ane dakake, Ee daЙЎМ¶axa me jemaa mawii anemaani.вҖқ  
\v 43 Odaa ja dopitacetege niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa icotacediogi me niotaЙЎМ¶a, leeЙЎМ¶odi eliodi liotaЙЎМ¶a, odaa aЙЎМ¶oyakadi me noleticoace. 
\p  
\v 44 Odaa ja yoyatace, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotace yotaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶e AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa yopilaЙЎМ¶ateetedeloco ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ligegite AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 45 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi Jesus ja dopitacetege niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece, odaa meetediogi, вҖңEЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶enitiwaji me iote, anigaaxe? Digawini! JiЙЎМ¶icota lakata AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane nibikotatedomi. Natigide, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, jeЙЎМ¶etidajigotiogi libaaЙЎМ¶adi ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi abeyacaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 46 Adabititiniwacetiwaji, jopilaЙЎМ¶a! Digawinitege! JiЙЎМ¶inaa niЙЎМ¶ijo ane idajigotiogi ineloЙЎМ¶ododipi.вҖқ 
\s1 Jesus diniwilo 
\r (Marcos 14.43-50; Lucas 22.47-53; JoГЈo 18.3-11) 
\p  
\v 47 Jesus eЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶eeteda me dotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶icotalo Judas, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane-diotibece Jesus, lokaaЙЎМ¶etedipi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece. Odaa Judas lixigaЙЎМ¶awepodi ijo noiigi-nelegi onadeegi nodaajoli-ocaЙЎМ¶atedi inaa laxacoЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶atedi. NiЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa laxokodi lacilodi judeutedi joaneЙЎМ¶epaaЙЎМ¶oimonya niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi. \fig |src="cn01814B.tif" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Mateus 26.47" \fig* 
\v 48 NiЙЎМ¶ijo ane yajigo Jesus akaa dinilakidetege niЙЎМ¶ica anodaaЙЎМ¶ee me ikee ane diЙЎМ¶etedigi Jesus. Meetiogi, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ica ane inapicoЙЎМ¶o me idecoaditece, jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶idoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa anoleetibigetiwaji. OdaaЙЎМ¶aniwiloteda!вҖқ  
\v 49 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Judas niЙЎМ¶icotiogi, ja dowicetelogo Jesus, odaa meetalo, вҖңEle ЙЎМ¶ocidi, iniiЙЎМ¶axinoЙЎМ¶odi?вҖқ Odaa ja napicoЙЎМ¶o.  
\v 50 NaЙЎМ¶a niniЙЎМ¶odi Jesus, meeteta, вҖңYokaaЙЎМ¶edi, ageniteloco niЙЎМ¶ica ane ЙЎМ¶abakedi managi!вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶ototelogo Jesus, joЙЎМ¶odibatalo moniwilo.  
\v 51 Pida anigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece nixigitice lodaajo-ocaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a, odaa ja yakagidi napaaЙЎМ¶ate ane diЙЎМ¶eticogi libaaЙЎМ¶adi liotagi niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi.  
\v 52 Pida Jesus meeteta, вҖңIxomitinece ЙЎМ¶adodaajo ЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶aaЙЎМ¶axi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ina ane nixigitice lodaajo me didele, aЙЎМ¶oiwoko moyeloadi oyatita nodaajo-ocaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 53 AgodoЙЎМ¶owooЙЎМ¶oti daЙЎМ¶a jemaa me jipokotalo Eiodi, odaa agotaЙЎМ¶a leegi, taЙЎМ¶a niwakatee anigetaЙЎМ¶a liwokodi miili aanjotedi modoweditiloco?  
\v 54 Pida daЙЎМ¶a idoЙЎМ¶atedicogi libaaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ina ineloЙЎМ¶ododipi, agotiЙЎМ¶icotece niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji anoyalaЙЎМ¶atiwa.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 55 Odaa naЙЎМ¶aca lakata, Jesus meetediogi niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi, вҖңIgame leeЙЎМ¶odi manadeegi inoa ЙЎМ¶adodaajoli-ocaЙЎМ¶atedi inaaЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶adaxacoЙЎМ¶onaЙЎМ¶atedi managi adiwilotiwaji? Domige Ee ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ЙЎМ¶onematagodi? NiЙЎМ¶ijoa nokododi eliodi me idejotibige minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, anei me idicotini odaa jiniiЙЎМ¶axitiniwace noiigi-nelegi, pida aЙЎМ¶adiwilotiwaji.  
\v 56 Pida natigide inoatawece niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶adoenatakatiwaji eotibige micotece ane diniditeloco AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶axi moyalaЙЎМ¶atiwa niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko.вҖқ Odaa ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus joЙЎМ¶oyaladi, jiЙЎМ¶ialetibigiwaji. 
\s1 Lacilodi judeutedi oiwi anodigotalo Jesus 
\r (Marcos 14.53-65; Lucas 22.54-55, 63-71; JoГЈo 18.12-14, 19-24) 
\p  
\v 57 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anoniwilo Jesus joЙЎМ¶oyadeegitedicogi minitaЙЎМ¶a diimigi-nelegi liЙЎМ¶eladi CaifГЎs, ane lacilo idiwatawece sacerdotitedi. JiЙЎМ¶idiaa latecaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa laxokodi lacilodi judeutedi.  
\v 58 Pedro diotece Jesus, pida aЙЎМ¶ipegitece. Diotece neЙЎМ¶epaa niogГіteloco liЙЎМ¶eladi lacilo-sacerdotitedi. NaЙЎМ¶a dakatio, odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaa nicotini awatege icoa nowienaЙЎМ¶anadi, yemaa me iwi niЙЎМ¶ica anodigotalo Jesus.  
\v 59 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi judeutedi idiaaЙЎМ¶idiwa icoa lilokaЙЎМ¶awadi iditawece odoletibige me nilaagedi Jesus. Odoletibige oko ane diwitaka anee mica Jesus loenatagi ane beyagi, domoЙЎМ¶owotibige mida ane leeЙЎМ¶odi moyeloadi.  
\v 60 Pida idaaЙЎМ¶ida meliodi oko awitakaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anidiaaЙЎМ¶i miditaЙЎМ¶a, pida aЙЎМ¶ica oteЙЎМ¶exaaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a itoataale oko ane itiwage liwitakeco niЙЎМ¶ina modotaЙЎМ¶atibige Jesus. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi jiЙЎМ¶ijoa itoataale ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anototicogi lodoe.  
\v 61 Odaa modi, вҖңIjo me jajipaaЙЎМ¶atalo mee, вҖҳJakadi me jojiketini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa idabiteЙЎМ¶etacini catiwedi itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi.вҖҷвҖқ 
\p  
\v 62 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi ja dabiditini, odaa ja ige Jesus, meetalo, вҖңIda makaami aЙЎМ¶otaЙЎМ¶ani? NiЙЎМ¶idoa itoataale ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi migoyeloЙЎМ¶odi anewi ina modakapetaЙЎМ¶agi?вҖқ  
\v 63 Pida Jesus aЙЎМ¶ica anigetiЙЎМ¶ida ligegi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi meetalo, вҖңJibake LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶eni me aneloЙЎМ¶otitoЙЎМ¶owa! NaЙЎМ¶akamaЙЎМ¶akaami icoa Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, ane niiЙЎМ¶e me ЙЎМ¶odatamaЙЎМ¶ateetetege ЙЎМ¶odaxakawepodi?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 64 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a niniЙЎМ¶odi, meeteta, вҖңAnaliiki ЙЎМ¶agegi, jeЙЎМ¶emeЙЎМ¶ee. Pida ejitaЙЎМ¶awatiwaji nigidiaaЙЎМ¶idi adati nige idopitijo, Ee, ЗӨoneleegiwa ane jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi. Icota me idicotini liwai libaaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji aneliodi notoetiigi, odaa idaxoditini jicoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi, jiniotinece lolaadi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 65 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi yaawidigidice lowoodi me ikee me yakadi me beyagi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a Jesus. Odaa mee, вҖңBeyagi me dotaЙЎМ¶atedibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, igaataЙЎМ¶a diniciaceeketetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Odaa aЙЎМ¶alee jopooЙЎМ¶atibige eledi oko nakataЙЎМ¶anadi moyeloЙЎМ¶odi minoa loenataka ane beyagi. IgaataЙЎМ¶a jaЙЎМ¶ajipaatalotiwaji lotaЙЎМ¶a me beyagi me dotaЙЎМ¶atedibige AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.  
\v 66 Enige, amiida ica ane iniЙЎМ¶atalo?вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oniniЙЎМ¶odi, modita, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶idoa idokida me nilaagedi, odaa leeditibige me yeleo.вҖқ  
\v 67 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyawaletigi latobi Jesus, codaa onalaketedibige. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anonaxacoЙЎМ¶otedibige moditalo,  
\v 68 вҖңNatigide, niЙЎМ¶ida makaami ane eni me ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji. Nigewi me ЙЎМ¶adiiЙЎМ¶eni AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, aneloЙЎМ¶otitoЙЎМ¶owa niЙЎМ¶ica ane ЙЎМ¶adaxaciЙЎМ¶i!вҖқ 
\s1 Pedro mee me diЙЎМ¶icoateda me yowooЙЎМ¶odi Jesus 
\r (Marcos 14.66-72; Lucas 22.54-62; JoГЈo 18.15-18, 25-27) 
\p  
\v 69 Pedro nicote digoida niogГіteloco liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi. Aca awicije liimete lacilo-sacerdotitedi niЙЎМ¶icota Pedro, odaa meeta, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ida ma-aami icaa ina daЙЎМ¶a ado-ooni mijoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus ane icoЙЎМ¶otedicogi nipodigi GalilГ©ia.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 70 Pida Pedro mee me niwitakegi lodoe iditawece niЙЎМ¶ijo oko, mee me dotaЙЎМ¶a, вҖңAЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶odi ica ane ЙЎМ¶adalakita.вҖқ  
\v 71 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi jiЙЎМ¶igo midataЙЎМ¶a ijo epoagi me jiniiЙЎМ¶atiwece niogГі liЙЎМ¶eladi niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo-sacerdotitedi. Odaa aca eledi awicije niimete meetiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo oko, вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ini aaginaЙЎМ¶a lixigaЙЎМ¶awa Jesus ane icoЙЎМ¶otedicogi nigotaЙЎМ¶a NazarГ©.вҖқ  
\v 72 Odaa Pedro ja diwitakatace mee me daЙЎМ¶a yowooЙЎМ¶oditeda Jesus, odaa mee me dinigetaЙЎМ¶atee, вҖңAЙЎМ¶icoa daЙЎМ¶a jowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 73 AЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi anigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anidiaaЙЎМ¶i, niЙЎМ¶ipegita Pedro, odaa meeta, вҖңIcaa ina daЙЎМ¶akaami anigepidiЙЎМ¶ica niЙЎМ¶ijo ane idei mijoataЙЎМ¶a Jesus, igaataЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶awa niЙЎМ¶ina oko ane icoЙЎМ¶oticogi nipodigi GalilГ©ia.вҖқ  
\v 74 Odaa Pedro jeЙЎМ¶ee me yakadi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me iloikatidi nige diwitaka, odaa jeЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңEwi me diЙЎМ¶icoateda me jowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶idoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa, ajiwitaka!вҖқ Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi, jaЙЎМ¶anoe okoЙЎМ¶okoodi.  
\v 75 Odaa Pedro ja nalaЙЎМ¶atibige niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ligegite Jesus, niЙЎМ¶ijo neЙЎМ¶eete, вҖңAniЙЎМ¶icatibige daЙЎМ¶a anoe okoЙЎМ¶okoodi, odaa itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida meni me daЙЎМ¶a adowooЙЎМ¶oti.вҖқ Odaa ja noditicogi we niogГі niЙЎМ¶ijo diimigi, eliodi magecaЙЎМ¶alo, codaa anoetibece. 
\c 27  
\s1 Oyadeegitedicogi Jesus lodoe Pilatos 
\r (Marcos 15.1-5; Lucas 23.1-5; JoГЈo 18.28-38) 
\p  
\v 1 NaЙЎМ¶a yeloЙЎМ¶otibige, ijotawece anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi, ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa laxokodi lacilodi judeutedi joЙЎМ¶odinilakidetigi niЙЎМ¶ica ane nimaweneЙЎМ¶egi moyeloadi Jesus.  
\v 2 Oigoe libaaЙЎМ¶atedi Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyadeegi, oyajigotalo Pilatos, lacilo romaanotedi ane iiЙЎМ¶e nipodigi JudГ©ia. 
\s1 LemeЙЎМ¶egi Judas 
\r (Atos 1.16-19) 
\p  
\v 3 Judas, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yajigo Jesus miditaЙЎМ¶a neloЙЎМ¶ododipi, nadi naЙЎМ¶a nilaagedi Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi codaa moyemaa moyeloadi, odaa jaЙЎМ¶agecaЙЎМ¶alo, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo miditaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa laxokodi lacilodi judeutedi, odaa ja yopilaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ijoa triinta beexotedi.  
\v 4 Odaa meetiogi, вҖңIca me jao ica ibeyaceЙЎМ¶egi me jajigo ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane diЙЎМ¶ica loenatagi ane beyagi odaa natigide ja leedi moyeloadi.вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, modita, вҖңAЙЎМ¶ica anejinaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶agi. AkamaЙЎМ¶a ЙЎМ¶abeyaceЙЎМ¶egi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 5 Odaa Judas ja yokoletedinigi iiЙЎМ¶o niЙЎМ¶ijoa beexotedi mini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi. NaЙЎМ¶a noditice, odaa jiЙЎМ¶igo dineloadi, diniЙЎМ¶iwoola. 
\p  
\v 6 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi odibatalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa beexotedi, odaa modi, вҖңЗӨonajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco etiЙЎМ¶odoli me jokolenaЙЎМ¶atinigi ЙЎМ¶oniwokodaЙЎМ¶axi, leeЙЎМ¶odi loojedi ЙЎМ¶odawodi.вҖқ  
\v 7 Odaa ja dinilakidetiwage modinoojeteta nipodigi, oibake niЙЎМ¶ijoa dinyeelo. NiЙЎМ¶ica nipodigi liboonaЙЎМ¶adi вҖңNipodigi ica niwilanaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶aвҖқ. NiЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi owo me napiiЙЎМ¶o niЙЎМ¶inoa icoЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 8 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa leeЙЎМ¶odi codaa me niЙЎМ¶inoa nokododi idokoyatigi, вҖңNipodigi ЙЎМ¶odawodiвҖқ. 
\p  
\v 9 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶icotece niЙЎМ¶ijoa lotaЙЎМ¶a Jeremias, niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee, 
\q1 вҖңOdibatalo niЙЎМ¶ijoa triinta beexotedi, 
\q1 ane lica me dinilakidetiwage loiigi Israel me loojedi modinoojetetalo. 
\q1  
\v 10 Oibake niЙЎМ¶idiwa dinyeelo modinoojeteta nipodigi niwilanaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a. 
\q1 JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa ane niiЙЎМ¶etediwa Iniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me jao.вҖқ 
\s1 Pilatos iwi ica anigotalo Jesus 
\r (Marcos 15.2-5; Lucas 23.3-5, 13-25; JoГЈo 18.33-38) 
\p  
\v 11 Jesus idiaa dabidite lodoe Pilatos, niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo romaanotedi ane iiЙЎМ¶e niЙЎМ¶idi nipodigi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo romaanotedi ja ige Jesus, meetalo, вҖңAkaami ninionigi-eliodi judeutedi?вҖқ NaЙЎМ¶a niniЙЎМ¶odi Jesus, meeteta, вҖңJiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee digo analeeЙЎМ¶enita.вҖқ  
\v 12 Pida aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a igiditediogi Jesus, niЙЎМ¶ijo noЙЎМ¶odakapetege niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa laxokodi lacilodi niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi,  
\v 13 Odaa Pilatos jeЙЎМ¶ee, вҖңAЙЎМ¶ajipaatalo inoa ЙЎМ¶anotaЙЎМ¶a? IgaataЙЎМ¶a owidi lotaЙЎМ¶a modakapetaЙЎМ¶agi makaami nilaagedi.вҖқ  
\v 14 Pida Jesus aniniЙЎМ¶odi, otiЙЎМ¶idatece ligegi, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo romaanotedi eliodi me yopo. 
\p  
\v 15 NiЙЎМ¶ina me lalokegi PГЎscoa, niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo romaanotedi ligileЙЎМ¶egi me ikatice okanicodaaЙЎМ¶ica niwilogojegi anodipokota niЙЎМ¶idi noiigi.  
\v 16 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa nokododi onini ica niwilogojegi aniboonaЙЎМ¶ategimadaЙЎМ¶a, liboonaЙЎМ¶adi BarrabГЎs.  
\v 17 NiЙЎМ¶ijo me yatecoЙЎМ¶o niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi, Pilatos ja nigetiniwace, meetiogi, вҖңAmiijo ica anemaani me jikataЙЎМ¶adomitiwaji, BarrabГЎs oЙЎМ¶oa Jesus, niЙЎМ¶idoa anodi me niiЙЎМ¶e ЗӨanoenoЙЎМ¶oditetiwaji?вҖқ  
\v 18 IgaataЙЎМ¶a Pilatos yowooЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi judeutedi moyadeegi Jesus minitaЙЎМ¶a leeЙЎМ¶odi monocetema. 
\p  
\v 19 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Pilatos naЙЎМ¶a nicotini aneitice me iwi anigota niЙЎМ¶ina oko, odaa naЙЎМ¶ajo lodawa ja dajoinaЙЎМ¶ata, meeta, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶awii ane beyagitema niЙЎМ¶idoa aaginaЙЎМ¶a anele. Le-eeЙЎМ¶odi jotigenoale idigee, meliodi me jawikode le-eeЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ica ane ninyaagi niЙЎМ¶idoa aaginaЙЎМ¶a.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 20 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa laxokodi lacilodi judeutedi joЙЎМ¶odinigaanyetece niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi modipokota Pilatos me ikatice BarrabГЎs, pida baЙЎМ¶a diiЙЎМ¶enatakatalo Jesus moyeloadi.  
\v 21 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo romaanotedi nigetiniwace, meetiogi, вҖңApiЙЎМ¶ijo inoa itoataale ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi anemaani me jikaticetiwaji?вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶oigidi, modita, вҖңIkanitice BarrabГЎs!вҖқ  
\v 22 Odaa Pilatos jeЙЎМ¶eetiogi, вҖңEnice, amiida ica anejigotalo Jesus, ane enitalotiwaji me liwaaЙЎМ¶aditedibigaЙЎМ¶aji AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji?вҖқ Odaa ijotawece oigidi, modita, вҖңOtonitedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate meloati!вҖқ  
\v 23 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo romaanotedi ja nigetiniwace, meetiogi, вҖңAmiida ica loenatagi ane beyagi?вҖқ Pida dinigetaЙЎМ¶ateetibigiwaji, modi, вҖңOtonitedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate meloati!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 24 NiЙЎМ¶ijo Pilatos naЙЎМ¶a nadi me daЙЎМ¶a yakadi meo ane domaЙЎМ¶a yemaa, codaa niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi naЙЎМ¶a domaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a odakapetege, odaa ja dibata ninyoЙЎМ¶odi, ja iwilegi libaaЙЎМ¶atedi lodoe niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi-nelegi. Odaa jeЙЎМ¶eetiogi, вҖңAjemaa deЙЎМ¶ee nilaagedi leeЙЎМ¶odi lemeЙЎМ¶egi niЙЎМ¶idoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa anele. Pida akapaЙЎМ¶akaamitiwaji nilaagetedipi.вҖқ  
\v 25 Ijotawece niЙЎМ¶ijo noiigi oigidi, modita, вҖңAnikanitoЙЎМ¶odici yakadi moko nilaagetedipi, codaa me ЙЎМ¶odionigipi leeЙЎМ¶odi lemeЙЎМ¶egi niЙЎМ¶idoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa.вҖқ  
\v 26 Odaa Pilatos ja ikatice BarrabГЎs. Odaa ja diiЙЎМ¶enatakatalo monalaketedibige Jesus, odaa niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja yajigo midiwataЙЎМ¶a niodaЙЎМ¶awadi moyototedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate moyeloadi. 
\s1 IodaЙЎМ¶awadi oyametibigo Jesus 
\r (Marcos 15.16-20; JoГЈo 19.2-3) 
\p  
\v 27 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa niodaЙЎМ¶awadi niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo romaanotedi joЙЎМ¶oyadeegitedicogi Jesus minitaЙЎМ¶a diimigi-nelegi, liЙЎМ¶eladi lacilo romaanotedi. Odaa ja yatecoЙЎМ¶o ijoatawece iodaЙЎМ¶awadi onawiile Jesus.  
\v 28 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi joЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶a Jesus lowoodi, odaa joЙЎМ¶onixomeЙЎМ¶etedinigi aca caapa lixagotoЙЎМ¶ogo.  
\v 29 Codaa joЙЎМ¶owo aca lale, anitawece lalepiЙЎМ¶igo, joЙЎМ¶onixotinece Jesus lacilo. Odaa owo me nolitedini ligiilaЙЎМ¶adi. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi onowo moyamaЙЎМ¶atedini lokotidi lodoe, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyame, modi, вҖңViiva, NiЙЎМ¶idoa one ninionigi-eliodi judeutedi!вҖқ  
\v 30 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyawaletigi latobi, noЙЎМ¶oibanootece niЙЎМ¶ijo ligiilaЙЎМ¶adi, odaa joЙЎМ¶oyaxacoЙЎМ¶otigi lacilo.  
\v 31 NoЙЎМ¶oika moyametibigo Jesus, odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi joЙЎМ¶onoЙЎМ¶a naЙЎМ¶ajo caapa lixagotoЙЎМ¶ogo, odaa joЙЎМ¶onixomeЙЎМ¶etacedinigi niЙЎМ¶ijoa epaa lowoodi. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi joЙЎМ¶oyadeegi Jesus moyototedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate moyeloadi. \fig |src="cn01827B.tif" size="span" copy="В© 1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="Mateus 27.27-31" \fig* 
\s1 Jesus oyototedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate 
\r (Marcos 15.21-32; Lucas 23.26-43; JoГЈo 19.17-27) 
\p  
\v 32 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi anoyadeegi Jesus naЙЎМ¶a noditicoaci nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, joЙЎМ¶odakapetege ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi SimГЈo, ane icoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigotaЙЎМ¶a Cirene. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi joЙЎМ¶oiedeЙЎМ¶etege SimГЈo me yoyaЙЎМ¶adi naЙЎМ¶ajo nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate.  
\v 33 Odaa joЙЎМ¶otota ijo lojotaЙЎМ¶adi ane liboonaЙЎМ¶adi GГіlgota. NiЙЎМ¶ida boonaЙЎМ¶adi amina anejinaЙЎМ¶ata, вҖңЗӨodacilo libitagiвҖқ.  
\v 34 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi domoЙЎМ¶oyacipeЙЎМ¶etalo Jesus viinyo awatege ligiti. Pida naЙЎМ¶a napi, odaa ayemaa me wacipete. 
\p  
\v 35 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi joЙЎМ¶oyototedeloco Jesus nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate, odaa joЙЎМ¶oiwi anepaЙЎМ¶a dinetetece niЙЎМ¶ijoa lowoodi. JoaniЙЎМ¶idaa niЙЎМ¶icotece lotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo ane yeloЙЎМ¶oditedibece AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji lowooko niЙЎМ¶ijo jotigide, niЙЎМ¶ijo mee, вҖңOdinawalacetigi yowoodi, codaa joЙЎМ¶oiwi anepaЙЎМ¶a dinetetece inicaapa.вҖқ  
\v 36 NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ja nicotiniwace moyowie.  
\v 37 Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyototi taaboa-liwai ditibigimedawaanigi lacilo Jesus ane diniditeloco ane leeЙЎМ¶odi moyeloadi. Diniditeloco niЙЎМ¶ica taaboa, 
\b  
\qc \sc вҖңNIЗӨIDOA JESUS, NINIONIGI-ELIODI JUDEUTEDI.вҖқ\sc* 
\m  
\v 38 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi eletidi oyototedi itoataale ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwadi olicaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a, onidateci diЙЎМ¶etege nimagijegi idaaЙЎМ¶eledi diЙЎМ¶etege libaaЙЎМ¶adi Jesus. 
\p  
\v 39 NiЙЎМ¶ina oko ane ixomaЙЎМ¶ateloco aneite Jesus me dinototedi, oyame. NabalenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶a, odaa modi,  
\v 40 вҖңNiЙЎМ¶ida makaami geemeni makati mojikenitini AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi, odaa meni me domaЙЎМ¶a adabiteЙЎМ¶enitacini catiwedi itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi! Axotitice naЙЎМ¶ada nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate! Nigewi makaami Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaaЙЎМ¶axotitice!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 41 NiЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijo anodiiЙЎМ¶axinaЙЎМ¶atece lajoinaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶eco MoisГ©s, ijoa laxokodi lacilodi judeutedi idaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a lamenaЙЎМ¶aneЙЎМ¶egitema Jesus, modi,  
\v 42 вҖңEliodi meetedibece me yakadi meote eledi oko me newiЙЎМ¶atace, pida IdaaЙЎМ¶idoa ayakadi me dinatamaЙЎМ¶ateetetege lemeЙЎМ¶egi! DaantiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶idoa niЙЎМ¶icoa ninionigi-eliodi Israel, taЙЎМ¶a waxoditedice naЙЎМ¶ada licenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate, odaa teЙЎМ¶ejiwaЙЎМ¶ataЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 43 Codaa nakato AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, odaa natigide jiwinaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji nige yemaa me noЙЎМ¶atedice me daЙЎМ¶a yeleoteda. IgaataЙЎМ¶a mee me Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji.вҖқ  
\v 44 NiЙЎМ¶ijoa olicaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a anoyototelogo nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate anodipegitege Jesus, idaЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶aee, oditibigelogo. 
\s1 LemeЙЎМ¶egi Jesus 
\r (Marcos 15.33-41; Lucas 23.44-49; JoГЈo 19.28-30) 
\p  
\v 45 IgaanaЙЎМ¶a yaxoЙЎМ¶o-noko, ja nexocaЙЎМ¶a neЙЎМ¶epaa iniwatadaЙЎМ¶ani lakata me ЙЎМ¶ocidi, odaa inatawece iiЙЎМ¶o nexocaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 46 NaЙЎМ¶a iniwatadaЙЎМ¶ani lakata me ЙЎМ¶ocidi, Jesus ja dinigetaЙЎМ¶atee me dapaawe, mee me dotaЙЎМ¶a, 
\q1 вҖңEli, Eli, lemГЎ sabactani!вҖқ 
\m NiЙЎМ¶idiwa notaЙЎМ¶a amina anejinaЙЎМ¶a, вҖңInoenoЙЎМ¶odi, InoenoЙЎМ¶odi, igame leeЙЎМ¶odi madikanitice?вҖқ 
\p  
\v 47 NiЙЎМ¶ijo oko anowajipatalo lotaЙЎМ¶a Jesus, modi, вҖңDapaawetedigi Elias.вҖқ  
\v 48 Odaa aЙЎМ¶ica daЙЎМ¶a leegi anigepidiЙЎМ¶ijo niЙЎМ¶ijo anowajipatalo ja walokodi, odaa ititinigi lawaadi ica viinyo ane daЙЎМ¶a dakake loojedi. NaЙЎМ¶a igoetece iwoЙЎМ¶o, odaa ja domaЙЎМ¶a ilipeЙЎМ¶etece Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo lawaadi.  
\v 49 Pida ica eledi oko modi, вҖңIkani! JiwinaЙЎМ¶a Elias migenagi noЙЎМ¶atedicogi aneite.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 50 Jesus naЙЎМ¶a dinigetaЙЎМ¶ateetace me dapaawe, odaa ja yeleo. 
\p  
\v 51 Odaa naЙЎМ¶aca lipegeteЙЎМ¶e nelegi ane nanyoti minitaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji liЙЎМ¶eladi ane iomaЙЎМ¶adi niЙЎМ¶ica aneite AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji, naЙЎМ¶aca lipegeteЙЎМ¶e ja daawidigidicetigi liwigotigi icoЙЎМ¶otibigimece ditibigimedi neЙЎМ¶epaa natinedi me daa. Codaa datalale iiЙЎМ¶o, odaa wetiadi dawalace.  
\v 52 Libecoli Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a domoke, odaa eliodi oko baanaЙЎМ¶a nigo anida aneetege AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ja newiЙЎМ¶atace.  
\v 53 Noditicoaci niЙЎМ¶inoa libecoli. NiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace Jesus, niЙЎМ¶ijoa Г©maЙЎМ¶aЙЎМ¶a ane newiЙЎМ¶atace joЙЎМ¶odakatiwece nigotaЙЎМ¶a JerusalГ©m, nigotaЙЎМ¶a AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ane iomaЙЎМ¶aditedice mepoka nebiteda. Odaa joЙЎМ¶odinikeetiogi eliodi oko. 
\p  
\v 54 NiЙЎМ¶ijo jajeentegi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa niodaЙЎМ¶awadi anoyowie Jesus noЙЎМ¶onadi me datalale iiЙЎМ¶o ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa eletidi loanico niЙЎМ¶ijo noko, odaa eliodi me doitibigiwaji, odaa modi, вҖңDicewi, niЙЎМ¶idoa ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa me Lionigi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji!вҖқ 
\p  
\v 55 IdiaaЙЎМ¶i eliodi iwaalepodi aneite Jesus, anoniotece, oicoЙЎМ¶oticogi GalilГ©ia anelioditibece moyaxawa. Pida leegitiogi moiЙЎМ¶oaditalo.  
\v 56 Liwigotigi niЙЎМ¶ijo iwaalepodi ani Maria Madalena, ajo eledi Maria ane eliodo Tiago ijaa JosГ©, ajaaЙЎМ¶ajo eliodo lionigipi Zebedeu. 
\s1 Onaligitedini Jesus 
\r (Marcos 15.42-47; Lucas 23.50-56; JoГЈo 19.38-42) 
\p  
\v 57 NiЙЎМ¶ijo naЙЎМ¶a doletibige me dalimeti aligeЙЎМ¶e, jiЙЎМ¶icotio ica ЙЎМ¶oneleegiwa liico liboonaЙЎМ¶adi JosГ©, ane icoЙЎМ¶oticogi nigotaЙЎМ¶a ArimatГ©ia. InaaЙЎМ¶ina ane-diotibece Jesus.  
\v 58 JosГ© igo minitaЙЎМ¶a Pilatos, dipokota lolaadi Jesus. Odaa Pilatos ja diiЙЎМ¶enataka moyajigota.  
\v 59 Odaa JosГ© ja yadeegi Jesus lolaadi, ilipaditigi niЙЎМ¶elate gela, lipegeteЙЎМ¶e anodita nigitikonaЙЎМ¶adi.  
\v 60 Odaa ja ixotediwece Jesus niЙЎМ¶ijo anepaa domaЙЎМ¶a libegi JosГ© ane nenyaЙЎМ¶adi, lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a, gela moigodi me diiЙЎМ¶enatakata JosГ©. Odaa ja yawililetio wetiЙЎМ¶a nelegi me noxoco lapoagi niЙЎМ¶ijo lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a. Odaa joЙЎМ¶opitio.  
\v 61 Idiaa nenyaЙЎМ¶ate Maria Madalena ajaaЙЎМ¶ajo eledi Maria. Nicotiniwace lodoe niЙЎМ¶ijo lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a. 
\s1 Icoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi anoyowie anonaligite Jesus 
\p  
\v 62 NaЙЎМ¶a saabado, ja ixomaЙЎМ¶atijo onijoteci noko modinenyaЙЎМ¶aditege lalokegi PГЎscoa. NiЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijaaЙЎМ¶ijoa fariseutedi jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci minitaЙЎМ¶a Pilatos.  
\v 63 Odaa modita, вҖңIniotagodi, nalaЙЎМ¶atibigoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ijo malee yewiЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijoa awitakegi, meetedibece, вҖҳNige ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi, odaa ja idewiЙЎМ¶atace.вҖҷ  
\v 64 Odaa iiЙЎМ¶eni iodaЙЎМ¶awadi modowediteloco lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a anoyatice lolaadi nigepaa ixomaЙЎМ¶atedijo itoatadiЙЎМ¶ida nokododi, adoЙЎМ¶odoliceta niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece lolaadi, oditaЙЎМ¶a oditiogi niЙЎМ¶ina noiigi, вҖҳJa yewiЙЎМ¶atace!вҖҷ IgaataЙЎМ¶a doЙЎМ¶oyakadi mowo, tiЙЎМ¶ida eledi niwitakegi daЙЎМ¶axa me beyagi caticedi niЙЎМ¶ijo odoejegi niwitakegi mijaaЙЎМ¶ee me yewiЙЎМ¶atace.вҖқ  
\v 65 Odaa Pilatos jeЙЎМ¶eetiogi, вҖңAwii adeegitetiwaji iodaЙЎМ¶awadi. Emii, odaa adowetiteloco libegi, codaa awii niЙЎМ¶ica aneneЙЎМ¶egi akati mele me ЙЎМ¶animaweneЙЎМ¶egi.вҖқ  
\v 66 Odaa jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci, joЙЎМ¶oyatitaЙЎМ¶aditi naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a ane noxoco niЙЎМ¶ijo lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a, owo me diЙЎМ¶icata ane yakadi me itineЙЎМ¶e naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶oyoyate iodaЙЎМ¶awadi me nowienaЙЎМ¶anadi. 
\c 28  
\s1 Jesus yewiЙЎМ¶atace 
\r (Marcos 16.1-10; Lucas 24.1-12; JoГЈo 20.1-10) 
\p  
\v 1 NaЙЎМ¶a ixomaЙЎМ¶atijo saabado, ja yapacaЙЎМ¶atege nigoi me nakatio domiingo, Maria Madalena ajaaЙЎМ¶ajo eledi Maria jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci odalita niЙЎМ¶ijo libegi Jesus.  
\v 2 MaleediЙЎМ¶icotibeci, jonaЙЎМ¶a datalale iiЙЎМ¶o, leeЙЎМ¶odi niaanjo ЗӨoniotagodi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji me dinikatini, odaa ja noЙЎМ¶atice naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a nelegi ane noxoco niЙЎМ¶ijo lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a aneitice lolaadi Jesus, odaa ica aanjo ja nicoteloco naЙЎМ¶ajo wetiЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 3 NiЙЎМ¶ijo aanjo datale liciagi nalebepaЙЎМ¶a, icoa lowoodi one daЙЎМ¶axa me yapacaЙЎМ¶a.  
\v 4 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa nowienaЙЎМ¶anadi eliodi me doitibigiwaji, nawigicaЙЎМ¶ateloco, odaa ja liciagi niЙЎМ¶ina oko baanaЙЎМ¶a yeleo. 
\p  
\v 5 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo aanjo meetiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo iwaalepodi, niЙЎМ¶icotiobeci, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶adoii! JowooЙЎМ¶odi managi oleetibige Jesus, niЙЎМ¶ijoa anoyototedeloco nicenaЙЎМ¶anaЙЎМ¶ate moyeloadi.  
\v 6 AЙЎМ¶aleeЙЎМ¶icoa digoina, leeЙЎМ¶odi ja yewiЙЎМ¶atace, jiЙЎМ¶icota niЙЎМ¶ijo ane ligegi. Anagi, awini niЙЎМ¶ijo anoyatedice.  
\v 7 Natigide ЙЎМ¶adediiki memiitiwaji, enitiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece naЙЎМ¶a yewiЙЎМ¶atace, codaa jiЙЎМ¶igo dinewadetedicogi digoida nipodigi GalilГ©ia. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶i manatitetiwaji. Odaa jiЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶ee, jeЙЎМ¶ejitece ijoatawece anetidiiЙЎМ¶e me jeloЙЎМ¶odi.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 8 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo iwaalepodi ja yediiЙЎМ¶atibigiwaji me noditicoaci niЙЎМ¶ijo lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a, eliodi me doitibigiwaji, pida niЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶idi ninitibigiwaji. Waleditibigiwaji migotibeci oibodicaxi niЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece Jesus. 
\p  
\v 9 Odaa naigitece codaa noЙЎМ¶onidoateda Jesus naЙЎМ¶a dakapetetege niЙЎМ¶ijo iwaalepodi, odaa ja nicetediniwace, meetediogi, вҖңInibeotege mele ЙЎМ¶adaaleЙЎМ¶enali!вҖқ Odaa joЙЎМ¶odiitalo, oibedotece loЙЎМ¶onaka, codaa odoЙЎМ¶etetalo.  
\v 10 Odaa Jesus jeЙЎМ¶eetediogi, вҖңJinaЙЎМ¶a adoiitiwaji! Pida emii, odaa enitiogi inioxoadipi migotibeci nipodigi GalilГ©ia. JiЙЎМ¶idiaaЙЎМ¶i metidadi.вҖқ 
\s1 Ica liwitakegi icoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi 
\p  
\v 11 EЙЎМ¶idaa diiticogi mewaligitibigiwaji niЙЎМ¶ijo iwaalepodi, onateciЙЎМ¶ijoa niЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi anoyowie niЙЎМ¶ijo lawimaЙЎМ¶ajegi-wetiЙЎМ¶a joЙЎМ¶opitibeci manitaЙЎМ¶a nigotaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa joЙЎМ¶oyeloЙЎМ¶oditiogi niЙЎМ¶ijo anoiiЙЎМ¶e sacerdotitedi ijoatawece niЙЎМ¶ijoa anonadi.  
\v 12 Odaa niЙЎМ¶idiwa lacilodi joЙЎМ¶odinatecoЙЎМ¶oteetege niЙЎМ¶ijoa laxokodi lacilodi judeutedi, odinilakidetege. Odaa owidi dinyeelo oyajigotiogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi.  
\v 13 Odaa moditiogi, вҖңJemaanaЙЎМ¶a menitiwaji, вҖҳNiЙЎМ¶ijo anodiotibece enagitibeci jotigenoale naЙЎМ¶a jiotaЙЎМ¶a. Odaa joЙЎМ¶odoliceta lolaadi Jesus.вҖҷ  
\v 14 Odaa nige wajipata niЙЎМ¶inoa ЙЎМ¶adotaЙЎМ¶a niЙЎМ¶ijo lacilo romaanotedi, odaa jaoЙЎМ¶a me diletibige me daЙЎМ¶awii ane beyagi, odaa aleeditibige daЙЎМ¶akaami agecaЙЎМ¶alodipitetiwaji.вҖқ 
\p  
\v 15 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijoa iodaЙЎМ¶awadi joЙЎМ¶oyadeegi niЙЎМ¶ijoa dinyeelo owidi, odaa joЙЎМ¶odi niЙЎМ¶ijo nigegi anoiiЙЎМ¶etiogi niЙЎМ¶ijoa lacilodi. Odaa niЙЎМ¶ida niwitakegi jiЙЎМ¶ilaagiteloco iditawece judeutedi codaa niЙЎМ¶ina noko. 
\s1 Jesus dakapetetege niЙЎМ¶ijo oonze anodiotibece odaa ja yajoitetece ane leeditibige mowote 
\r (Marcos 16.14-18; Lucas 24.36-49; JoГЈo 20.19-23; Atos 1.6-8) 
\p  
\v 16 Odaa niЙЎМ¶ijo oonze anodiotibece Jesus jiЙЎМ¶igotibeci nipodigi GalilГ©ia, odaa joЙЎМ¶otota niЙЎМ¶ijo lojotaЙЎМ¶adi aneetediogi Jesus me dakapetetege.  
\v 17 NoЙЎМ¶onadi Jesus, odaa joЙЎМ¶odoЙЎМ¶etetalo. Pida ijoawaanigi onateciЙЎМ¶ijo ane dinawietibigiwaji mewi niЙЎМ¶idaaЙЎМ¶idoa.  
\v 18 Odaa Jesus niЙЎМ¶ipegitediogi, meetediogi, вҖңAneotedoЙЎМ¶oji najigotediwa iiЙЎМ¶enatakaneЙЎМ¶egitema inoatawece, aninoa ditibigimedi codaa minatawece iiЙЎМ¶o.  
\v 19 Natigide, emiitecetiwaji inatawece noiigi, odaa aniiЙЎМ¶axinitiniwace moniotici, codaa anilegenitiniwace niЙЎМ¶ina anetidadiwaЙЎМ¶adi. Abakeni LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji ЗӨodiodi, LiboonaЙЎМ¶adi Lionigi, iniaa Liwigo AneotedoЙЎМ¶oji niЙЎМ¶ina milegenaЙЎМ¶ani.  
\v 20 IiЙЎМ¶axinitece mowo inoatawece ane jiiЙЎМ¶etedaЙЎМ¶awa mawii. Codaa idioka limedi me idejo makaamitaЙЎМ¶atiwaji nigepaa owidijedi nokododi.вҖқ